insert  into `end_chat_speaker`(`speaker_id`,`order_id`,`name_cn`,`name_en`,`title_cn`,`title_en`,`company_cn`,`company_en`,`attend_program`,`avatar_big`,`avatar_small`,`description_cn`,`description_en`) values (1,5,'成尔骏','David Cheng','万达商业地产股份有限公司副总裁，万达酒店及度假村管理有限公司总裁','Vice President of Dalian Wanda Commercial Properties Co., Ltd. and President of Wanda Hotels and Resorts Co., Ltd.','','','','public/2013/07/DavidCheng1453913.png','public/2013/07/DavidCheng1453913_small.png','成尔骏，万达商业地产股份有限公司副总裁，兼万达酒店及度假村管理有限公司总裁。曾服务于金茂集团，主要负责集团酒店业务板块的管理，在业内率先建立并完善了酒店资产管理系统，并曾多次被评为中国酒店行业领袖人物。<br>成尔骏先生于2012年初加入万达集团，出任万达商业地产股份有限公司副总裁兼万达酒店及度假村管理有限公司总裁。在他的倡导下，公司立志成为国际领先的中国豪华酒店管理集团，是一个集酒店业主，经营与销售功能为一体的综合性酒店管理公司。他带领团队先后创立了三个万达的自主酒店品牌，完善了各项品牌标准，创建了公司的全球分销渠道，建立了自有的全球销售办公室。与此同时，在公司成立的第一年，除了履行业主的角色对旗下委托五大国际酒店管理集团管理的34家，数十个品牌的豪华酒店进行综合管控之外，麾下自主品牌酒店不仅实现了按期顺利开业，更是取得了良好的酒店业绩。短短两年，万达酒店及度假村收到业界广泛关注。在接下来的3至5年中，万达酒店及度假村会以年均开业20家豪华酒店的速度，扩大市场影响和巩固业内的地位及声誉，继续完善及提升万达自有酒店品牌的国际化形象，&nbsp;并将在全球门户城市投资，建设和管理万达品牌酒店，将万达酒店及度假村管理有限公司塑造成为真正的拥有国际品牌的跨国酒店管理集团。<br>成尔骏先生乐于和业内同行分享行业经验和心得，并先后在国内知名的报刊杂志上发表过一系列专业文章，包括《国际豪华品牌酒店确立竞争优势之道》、《国际品牌酒店核心竞争力》、《国际品牌酒店以人为本的实践》等。','Mr.&nbsp;David&nbsp;Cheng&nbsp;is&nbsp;now&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President&nbsp;of&nbsp;Dalian&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Commercial&nbsp;Properties&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;and&nbsp;President&nbsp;of&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;Before&nbsp;his&nbsp;career&nbsp;with&nbsp;Wanda,&nbsp;he&nbsp;was&nbsp;in&nbsp;charge&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;business&nbsp;of&nbsp;China&nbsp;Jin&nbsp;Mao&nbsp;Group&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;and&nbsp;pioneered&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;assets&nbsp;management&nbsp;in&nbsp;China.<br>Mr.&nbsp;Cheng&nbsp;joined&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Group&nbsp;in&nbsp;2012&nbsp;and&nbsp;was&nbsp;appointed&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President&nbsp;of&nbsp;Dalian&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Commercial&nbsp;Properties&nbsp;and&nbsp;President&nbsp;of&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;Resorts.&nbsp;It&nbsp;was&nbsp;on&nbsp;his&nbsp;initiative&nbsp;that&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;strives&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;leading&nbsp;global&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;group&nbsp;of&nbsp;China,&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;full&nbsp;business&nbsp;line&nbsp;encompassing&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;development,&nbsp;operations&nbsp;and&nbsp;sales.&nbsp;He&nbsp;led&nbsp;a&nbsp;team&nbsp;and&nbsp;together&nbsp;they&nbsp;created&nbsp;three&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Brands.&nbsp;He&nbsp;established&nbsp;a&nbsp;global&nbsp;distribution&nbsp;channel&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;company&nbsp;and&nbsp;set&nbsp;up&nbsp;its&nbsp;own&nbsp;regional&nbsp;sales&nbsp;office.&nbsp;With&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Cheng’s&nbsp;efforts,&nbsp;the&nbsp;company&nbsp;made&nbsp;a&nbsp;shining&nbsp;debut&nbsp;in&nbsp;2012.&nbsp;In&nbsp;addition&nbsp;to&nbsp;overall&nbsp;management&nbsp;and&nbsp;control&nbsp;of&nbsp;34&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;of&nbsp;different&nbsp;international&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;brands,&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;year&nbsp;after&nbsp;its&nbsp;founding&nbsp;saw&nbsp;successful&nbsp;opening&nbsp;and&nbsp;thriving&nbsp;business&nbsp;of&nbsp;owned&nbsp;managed&nbsp;hotels.&nbsp;Within&nbsp;two&nbsp;years&nbsp;time,&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;has&nbsp;put&nbsp;it&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;limelight&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;public&nbsp;attention.&nbsp;Yet&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;won’t&nbsp;stop&nbsp;its&nbsp;expansion&nbsp;of&nbsp;an&nbsp;average&nbsp;of&nbsp;20&nbsp;new&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;per&nbsp;year&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;coming&nbsp;3&nbsp;to&nbsp;5&nbsp;years,&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;driving&nbsp;ambition&nbsp;to&nbsp;make&nbsp;a&nbsp;louder&nbsp;voice&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;marketplace&nbsp;and&nbsp;pioneer&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;and&nbsp;enhanced&nbsp;international&nbsp;brand&nbsp;image&nbsp;of&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;to&nbsp;make&nbsp;the&nbsp;reputed&nbsp;name&nbsp;impeccable&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;industry.&nbsp;What’s&nbsp;more,&nbsp;through&nbsp;international&nbsp;merger&nbsp;and&nbsp;acquisition&nbsp;to&nbsp;answer&nbsp;the&nbsp;call&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;times,&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;aspires&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;stardom&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;truly&nbsp;multinational&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;group&nbsp;holding&nbsp;international&nbsp;brands.&nbsp;<br>Mr.&nbsp;Cheng&nbsp;is&nbsp;always&nbsp;willing&nbsp;to&nbsp;share&nbsp;his&nbsp;experience&nbsp;and&nbsp;ideas&nbsp;with&nbsp;his&nbsp;peers&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;industry.&nbsp;Published&nbsp;on&nbsp;noted&nbsp;newspapers&nbsp;and&nbsp;magazines&nbsp;home&nbsp;and&nbsp;abroad,&nbsp;his&nbsp;papers&nbsp;and&nbsp;articles&nbsp;on&nbsp;his&nbsp;expertise&nbsp;include&nbsp;The&nbsp;Way&nbsp;to&nbsp;Competitive&nbsp;Edge&nbsp;for&nbsp;International&nbsp;Luxury&nbsp;Brand&nbsp;Hotels,&nbsp;The&nbsp;Core&nbsp;Competitiveness&nbsp;of&nbsp;International&nbsp;Brand&nbsp;Hotels,&nbsp;People-oriented&nbsp;Practice&nbsp;for&nbsp;International&nbsp;Brand&nbsp;Hotels,&nbsp;etc.<br>'),(2,10,'罗伯特•赫克','Robert Hecker','执行董事','Managing Director, Pacific Asia','浩华管理顾问公司','Horwath HTL','','public/2013/07/RobertHecker145.png','public/2013/07/RobertHecker145_small.png','罗伯特•赫克先生负责浩华管理顾问公司在亚太区的运营。浩华管理顾问公司是国富浩华在亚太区专业从&nbsp;事酒店及旅游业的顾问咨询公司，在东京、北京、上海、香港、吉隆坡和雅加达均设有办事机构。自&nbsp;1988年加入浩华以来，罗伯特•赫克先生先后参与了亚太区逾400个项目的规划和分析，拥有大量酒店开发及旅游业发展的广泛背景和专业知识。<br>&nbsp;罗伯特•赫克先生拥有超过35年的工作经验，包括太平洋广场酒店集团于北加利福尼亚州不同酒店的运营工作经验、旧金山Laventhol以及浩华酒店管理顾问公司任职期间对酒店、度假村、游艇、会展中心、会议中心和餐馆进行的市场及财务分析。<br>&nbsp;罗伯特•赫克先生还时常受邀在亚太区酒店领域的研讨会上发表演讲，并在行业刊物上发表了大量研究文章。','Robert&nbsp;oversees&nbsp;the&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;territory&nbsp;of&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;HTL,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;and&nbsp;Leisure&nbsp;consulting&nbsp;specialty&nbsp;group&nbsp;of&nbsp;Crowe&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;International,&nbsp;with&nbsp;offices&nbsp;in&nbsp;Tokyo,&nbsp;Beijing,&nbsp;Shanghai,&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong,&nbsp;Kuala&nbsp;Lumpur,&nbsp;Singapore&nbsp;and&nbsp;Jakarta.&nbsp;With&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;HTL&nbsp;since&nbsp;1988,&nbsp;he&nbsp;has&nbsp;developed&nbsp;an&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;background&nbsp;and&nbsp;expertise&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;region’s&nbsp;developing&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;and&nbsp;tourism&nbsp;industries&nbsp;through&nbsp;his&nbsp;involvement&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;planning&nbsp;and&nbsp;analysis&nbsp;of&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;400&nbsp;projects&nbsp;located&nbsp;throughout&nbsp;the&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Region.<br>&nbsp;Overall,&nbsp;he&nbsp;has&nbsp;over&nbsp;35&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;experience&nbsp;including&nbsp;work&nbsp;in&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;operations&nbsp;with&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;at&nbsp;various&nbsp;properties&nbsp;in&nbsp;northern&nbsp;California&nbsp;and&nbsp;conducting&nbsp;market&nbsp;and&nbsp;financial&nbsp;analyses&nbsp;for&nbsp;hotels,&nbsp;resorts,&nbsp;cruise&nbsp;ships,&nbsp;convention&nbsp;centers,&nbsp;conference&nbsp;centers&nbsp;and&nbsp;restaurants&nbsp;while&nbsp;with&nbsp;Laventhol&nbsp;and&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;in&nbsp;San&nbsp;Francisco.<br>He&nbsp;is&nbsp;also&nbsp;a&nbsp;frequent&nbsp;speaker&nbsp;at&nbsp;industry&nbsp;related&nbsp;conferences&nbsp;around&nbsp;the&nbsp;region&nbsp;and&nbsp;has&nbsp;published&nbsp;numerous&nbsp;research&nbsp;articles&nbsp;in&nbsp;regional&nbsp;industry&nbsp;publications.'),(3,21,'森马仕','Nigel Summers','董事','Director','浩华管理顾问公司','Horwath HTL','','public/2013/08/SummersNigel145.png','public/2013/08/SummersNigel145_small.png','Nigel&nbsp;Summers&nbsp;先生是浩华管理顾问公司资深董事，自1994年加入浩华团队效力至今，参与了浩华在亚太区1,000&nbsp;多个酒店及旅游业项目的顾问服务，这些项目遍及中国、澳大利亚、新加坡、斐济、菲律宾、韩国、北朝鲜、泰国、马来西亚、印尼、越南等10&nbsp;多个国家和地区，具有酒店及旅游业开发领域的丰富经验，尤其在中国市场，Summers&nbsp;先生亲自领导并参与每一个项目，因此对中国市场具有非常独特的见解和认识。此外，他也经常参加酒店及旅游领域著名的国际性论坛或者研讨会，并受邀发表主题演讲。在加入浩华前，Summers&nbsp;先生曾担任澳大利亚Mallesons&nbsp;Stephen&nbsp;Jacques&nbsp;公司商务合同和交易领域律师，之后为Meridien&nbsp;酒店管理集团担任财务分析顾问和总监职务。Summers&nbsp;先生就读于康奈尔大学酒店及旅游业管理MBA，并获得硕士学位。Summers&nbsp;先生亲自监督了所有浩华在中国所执行的项目研究。','Nigel&nbsp;Summers&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;HTL&nbsp;(HHTL).&nbsp;&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Summers&nbsp;is&nbsp;based&nbsp;in&nbsp;HHTL’s&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;office&nbsp;and&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;involved&nbsp;in&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;1,000&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;and&nbsp;tourism&nbsp;projects&nbsp;throughout&nbsp;the&nbsp;region&nbsp;including,&nbsp;China,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Philippines,&nbsp;North&nbsp;and&nbsp;South&nbsp;Korea,&nbsp;Thailand,&nbsp;Malaysia,&nbsp;Indonesia,&nbsp;Vietnam,&nbsp;Cambodia,&nbsp;Brunei,&nbsp;Singapore,&nbsp;Australia&nbsp;and&nbsp;Fiji.&nbsp;He&nbsp;is&nbsp;also&nbsp;a&nbsp;frequent&nbsp;speaker&nbsp;at&nbsp;industry&nbsp;related&nbsp;conferences&nbsp;around&nbsp;the&nbsp;region&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;commentator&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;media.&nbsp;Prior&nbsp;to&nbsp;joining&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;in&nbsp;1994,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Summers&nbsp;worked&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;lawyer&nbsp;specializing&nbsp;in&nbsp;commercial&nbsp;contracts&nbsp;and&nbsp;transactions&nbsp;with&nbsp;Mallesons&nbsp;Stephen&nbsp;Jacques&nbsp;in&nbsp;Melbourne,&nbsp;Australia;&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;financial&nbsp;analyst&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;Meridien&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;London&nbsp;and&nbsp;with&nbsp;Southern&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;in&nbsp;Australia.&nbsp;&nbsp;'),(4,20,'苏仁豪','Soh Leen How','董事','Principal','美国SRSS建筑师事务所','SRSS','','public/2013/08/SohLeenHow145_update.png','public/2013/08/SohLeenHow145_update_small.png','苏仁豪现任美国SRSS建筑师事务所的合伙人，是SRSS在国内的总负责人。<br>苏先生于2003年加入SRSS。是SRSS常驻中国的第一位职员。凭借者SRSS在美洲及亚太地区的优异酒店设计业绩和苏先生的在国内努力开拓、经营“SRSS酒店与旅游”&nbsp;设计服务，SRSS已经树立起顶尖酒店设计的品牌。在苏先生和同事们的努力下，2005年，SRSS在国内迎来了第一家酒店，三亚亚龙湾万豪度假酒店及水疗中心。随后陆续竣工的项目有三亚湾假日酒店，绥芬河世茂假日酒店，上海东方佘山索菲特大酒店，苏州洲际酒店，南昌皇冠假日酒店，常州九洲喜来登,&nbsp;三亚海棠湾喜来登度假酒店及三亚御海棠-豪华精选度假酒店。SRSS全体设计团队也期待着郑州曼哈顿希尔顿，无锡皇冠假日，洛阳希尔顿逸林，郑州站前广场希尔顿逸林及株洲晋合凯悦酒店的竣工。其中，上海东方佘山索菲特大酒及苏州洲际酒店享有奢华酒店的盛名。<br>苏先生向来强调务实，重开发单位的投资效益。秉持高水平的服务态度，力于营造国内外设计单位的工作默契。<br>在酒店专业的学术贡献，他是清华大学继续教育学院数个高级研修班，亚洲酒店论坛2个高级课程及其他学术研修班的讲师并在国内多本酒店及建筑地产类杂志上发表文章。<br>	鉴于苏先生在中国酒店业界的杰出表现及优越成绩,&nbsp;亚洲酒店论坛中心于2013第八届中国酒店星光奖颁给苏先生<中国酒店业最佳设计师>奖。<br>','Soh&nbsp;Leen&nbsp;How&nbsp;is&nbsp;currently&nbsp;the&nbsp;Principal&nbsp;of&nbsp;SRSS&nbsp;and&nbsp;he&nbsp;is&nbsp;heading&nbsp;the&nbsp;China&nbsp;market.&nbsp;<br>Mr&nbsp;Soh&nbsp;joined&nbsp;SRSS&nbsp;in&nbsp;2003&nbsp;and&nbsp;he&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;executive&nbsp;to&nbsp;station&nbsp;in&nbsp;China.&nbsp;Riding&nbsp;on&nbsp;SRSS’&nbsp;excellent&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;design&nbsp;track&nbsp;records&nbsp;in&nbsp;US&nbsp;and&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific;&nbsp;and&nbsp;his&nbsp;endeavor&nbsp;to&nbsp;develop&nbsp;and&nbsp;manage&nbsp;“SRSS&nbsp;Hospitality”&nbsp;design&nbsp;services&nbsp;in&nbsp;China,&nbsp;SRSS&nbsp;has&nbsp;become&nbsp;a&nbsp;top&nbsp;notch&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;design&nbsp;brand.&nbsp;Under&nbsp;the&nbsp;SRSS&nbsp;Team’s&nbsp;effort,&nbsp;SRSS’&nbsp;first&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;in&nbsp;China,&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;Marriott&nbsp;Yalong&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;&&nbsp;Spa&nbsp;was&nbsp;completed&nbsp;in&nbsp;2005.&nbsp;Since,&nbsp;SRSS&nbsp;have&nbsp;seen&nbsp;the&nbsp;completion&nbsp;of&nbsp;Holiday&nbsp;Inn&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Resort,&nbsp;Holiday&nbsp;Inn&nbsp;Suifenhe,&nbsp;Sofitel&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;Sheshan&nbsp;Oriental,&nbsp;InterContinental&nbsp;Suzhou,&nbsp;Crowne&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Nanchang&nbsp;Riverside,&nbsp;Changzhou&nbsp;Jiuzhou&nbsp;Sheraton,&nbsp;Sheraton&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;Haitang&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;and&nbsp;The&nbsp;Royal&nbsp;Begonia&nbsp;-&nbsp;A&nbsp;Luxury&nbsp;Collection&nbsp;Resort.&nbsp;Projects&nbsp;under&nbsp;construction&nbsp;include&nbsp;Zhengzhou&nbsp;Manhattan&nbsp;Hilton,&nbsp;Wuxi&nbsp;Crowne&nbsp;Plaza,&nbsp;Luoyang&nbsp;Hilton’s&nbsp;Double&nbsp;Trees,&nbsp;Zhengzhou&nbsp;Shenlong&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;Double&nbsp;Trees,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Jinghope&nbsp;Zhuzhou&nbsp;Hyatt&nbsp;Regency.&nbsp;Of&nbsp;which,&nbsp;Sofitel&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;Sheshan&nbsp;Oriental&nbsp;and&nbsp;Suzhou&nbsp;InterContinental&nbsp;have&nbsp;gained&nbsp;notable&nbsp;reputation&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;segment.<br>Mr&nbsp;Soh&nbsp;always&nbsp;focuses&nbsp;on&nbsp;creativity&nbsp;and&nbsp;pragmatism&nbsp;and&nbsp;emphasizes&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;efficiency&nbsp;of&nbsp;investment&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;developers.&nbsp;He&nbsp;believes&nbsp;in&nbsp;high&nbsp;service&nbsp;attitude&nbsp;and&nbsp;endeavor&nbsp;in&nbsp;creating&nbsp;a&nbsp;well&nbsp;coordinated&nbsp;working&nbsp;relationship&nbsp;with&nbsp;local&nbsp;design&nbsp;institutes&nbsp;and&nbsp;consultants.<br>As&nbsp;for&nbsp;his&nbsp;contribution&nbsp;to&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;profession&nbsp;and&nbsp;academia,&nbsp;he&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;a&nbsp;regular&nbsp;lecturer&nbsp;for&nbsp;several&nbsp;Tsinghua&nbsp;University&nbsp;Continued&nbsp;Education&nbsp;Executive&nbsp;Training&nbsp;Program,&nbsp;2&nbsp;Advanced&nbsp;Courses&nbsp;by&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Forum&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;Academic&nbsp;Programs.&nbsp;He&nbsp;has&nbsp;published&nbsp;articles&nbsp;in&nbsp;various&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;and&nbsp;Real&nbsp;Estate&nbsp;Magazines.<br>For&nbsp;Mr&nbsp;Soh&nbsp;excellent&nbsp;performance&nbsp;in&nbsp;China&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;Industry,&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Forum&nbsp;has&nbsp;awarded&nbsp;the&nbsp;Best&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;Designer&nbsp;in&nbsp;China&nbsp;Award&nbsp;to&nbsp;him&nbsp;at&nbsp;The&nbsp;8th&nbsp;China&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Starlight&nbsp;Awards,&nbsp;2013.<br>'),(5,14.5,'刘伟立','Liu Wei Li','亚太区资深副总裁, 设计与工程筹划','Senior Vice President, Design & Technical Services, Asia Pacific','喜达屋酒店与度假村国际集团','Starwood Hotels & Resorts Worldwide Inc.','','public/2013/07/LiuLiWei145.png','public/2013/07/LiuLiWei145_small.png','刘伟立任职喜达屋酒店与度假村亚太区资深副总裁，带领设计与工程筹划部门。他于2006&nbsp;年加入喜达屋，负责管理喜达屋亚太区旗下九大知名品牌的创意与设计资源，这些品牌包括瑞吉、豪华精选、W&nbsp;酒店、喜来登、威斯汀、艾美、福朋酒店（喜来登集团管理）、雅乐轩和源宿。刘先生与其团队目前正着手于亚太地区170&nbsp;多个的新酒店项目。<br>&nbsp;加入喜达屋之前，刘伟立先生曾经在新加坡与中国的大型房地产发展及酒店业主、品牌公司工作，对酒店业、商业零售与住宅的设计发展上拥有相当的经验，参与项目涉及美国、欧洲与亚太地区。<br>&nbsp;刘先生毕业于哈佛大学设计学院，拥有建筑与城市设计的双学位，是美国纽约州的注册建筑师。','Liu&nbsp;Wei&nbsp;Li&nbsp;is&nbsp;Senior&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President,&nbsp;Design&nbsp;&&nbsp;Technical&nbsp;Services&nbsp;for&nbsp;Starwood&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific.&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Liu&nbsp;joined&nbsp;Starwood&nbsp;in&nbsp;2006&nbsp;and&nbsp;oversees&nbsp;all&nbsp;creative&nbsp;and&nbsp;design&nbsp;resources&nbsp;forStarwood’s&nbsp;nine&nbsp;brands&nbsp;in&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;including&nbsp;St.&nbsp;Regis,&nbsp;The&nbsp;Luxury&nbsp;Collection,&nbsp;W&nbsp;Hotels,&nbsp;Sheraton,&nbsp;Westin,&nbsp;Le&nbsp;Meridien,&nbsp;Four&nbsp;Points&nbsp;by&nbsp;Sheraton,&nbsp;Aloft&nbsp;and&nbsp;Element.&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Liu&nbsp;and&nbsp;his&nbsp;team&nbsp;are&nbsp;currently&nbsp;involved&nbsp;with&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;170&nbsp;new&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;projects&nbsp;across&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific.&nbsp;Prior&nbsp;to&nbsp;Starwood,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Liu&nbsp;worked&nbsp;for&nbsp;major&nbsp;developers&nbsp;and&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;owners&nbsp;in&nbsp;Singapore&nbsp;and&nbsp;China.&nbsp;He&nbsp;had&nbsp;extended&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hospitality,&nbsp;Retail&nbsp;and&nbsp;Residential&nbsp;design&nbsp;&&nbsp;developments&nbsp;and&nbsp;his&nbsp;projects&nbsp;cover&nbsp;USA,&nbsp;Europe&nbsp;and&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific.<br>&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Liu,&nbsp;licensed&nbsp;architect&nbsp;in&nbsp;New&nbsp;York&nbsp;State,&nbsp;holds&nbsp;both&nbsp;Architectural&nbsp;and&nbsp;Urban&nbsp;Design&nbsp;degrees&nbsp;from&nbsp;Harvard&nbsp;Graduate&nbsp;School&nbsp;of&nbsp;Design.'),(6,28,'吴姿莹','Zoe Wu','董事','Director','浩华管理顾问公司','Horwath HTL','','public/2013/08/ZoeWu145_update.png','public/2013/08/ZoeWu145_update_small.png','吴姿莹小姐是浩华管理顾问公司董事及浩华上海办公室的创办人。吴小姐拥有近20&nbsp;年在美国、加拿大、台湾、香港及中国从事酒店业的经验，曾为中国多个城市以及越南、泰国、台湾等地的商务酒店、经济型酒店、度假酒店、精品酒店及餐饮从事过各类型项目包括可行性、市场研究、市场定位、财政预算、投资回报评估以及整体规划等。在加入浩华之前，吴小姐曾为凯悦国际集团亚太地区及Pan&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;北美地区负责人力资源及培训发展管理工作；她还曾在华盛顿市专业酒店市场分析公司担任顾问效力两年。吴小姐拥有康奈尔大学酒店管理学院的学士及硕士学位，现任康奈尔酒店学院协会上海分会主席，曾任香港分会主席。','Zoe&nbsp;Wu&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;Director&nbsp;for&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;HTL&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;founding&nbsp;member&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;Office.&nbsp;&nbsp;Ms.&nbsp;Wu&nbsp;has&nbsp;close&nbsp;to&nbsp;20&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;industry&nbsp;experience&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;US,&nbsp;Canada,&nbsp;Taiwan,&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;and&nbsp;China.&nbsp;&nbsp;Ms&nbsp;Wu&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;involved&nbsp;in&nbsp;feasibility&nbsp;studies,&nbsp;market&nbsp;research,&nbsp;financial&nbsp;forecasts,&nbsp;cash&nbsp;flow&nbsp;analysis&nbsp;and&nbsp;master&nbsp;planning&nbsp;projects&nbsp;in&nbsp;both&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;and&nbsp;food&nbsp;&&nbsp;beverage&nbsp;industries&nbsp;in&nbsp;China,&nbsp;Thailand,&nbsp;Taiwan&nbsp;and&nbsp;Vietnam.&nbsp;&nbsp;Prior&nbsp;to&nbsp;joining&nbsp;HHTL,&nbsp;Ms.&nbsp;Wu&nbsp;was&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;regional&nbsp;education&nbsp;and&nbsp;training&nbsp;for&nbsp;Pan&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;North&nbsp;America,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Grand&nbsp;Hyatt&nbsp;Taipei&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;preceding&nbsp;years.&nbsp;&nbsp;Ms.&nbsp;Wu&nbsp;also&nbsp;spent&nbsp;two&nbsp;years&nbsp;with&nbsp;Driving&nbsp;Revenue&nbsp;in&nbsp;Washington&nbsp;DC&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;marketing&nbsp;consultant&nbsp;specializing&nbsp;in&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;market&nbsp;analysis.&nbsp;&nbsp;Ms.&nbsp;Wu&nbsp;holds&nbsp;both&nbsp;an&nbsp;undergraduate&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;graduate&nbsp;degree&nbsp;from&nbsp;Cornell&nbsp;University&nbsp;School&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Administration&nbsp;and&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;current&nbsp;president&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Cornell&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Society&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;Chapter&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;past&nbsp;president&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;Chapter.'),(7,32,'张工','Gong Zhang','总裁和首席设计师','President and Chief Designer','美达麦斯国际建筑','Metamax International Architecture','','public/2013/07/GongZhang1458842.png','public/2013/07/GongZhang1458842_small.png','张工是美达麦斯国际建筑的总裁和首席设计师，有20多年在法国、美国和中国的建筑设计专业经验。以他在酒店及综合体设计上的雄厚实力，设计和主持了很多重要项目。他和他所领导的美达麦斯国际建筑曾荣获&nbsp;“2009年中国最具影响力酒店设计公司”称号。他是&nbsp;“Hall&nbsp;of&nbsp;Fame”&nbsp;(China)即“名人堂”（中国）的成员。张工也是成功的艺术家，他曾应法国美术协会邀请参加法国巴黎卢浮宫举办的“法国美术协会年展”，并荣获法国美术协会授予的“特殊奖”。他将其美学和建筑学造诣融入每一个项目的设计之中。','Gong&nbsp;Zhang,&nbsp;President&nbsp;and&nbsp;Chief&nbsp;Designer&nbsp;of&nbsp;Metamax&nbsp;International&nbsp;Architecture,&nbsp;has&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;20&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;professional&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;France,&nbsp;the&nbsp;United&nbsp;States&nbsp;and&nbsp;China.&nbsp;With&nbsp;his&nbsp;strong&nbsp;expertise&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;and&nbsp;Mixed-use&nbsp;Complexes&nbsp;designs,&nbsp;he&nbsp;has&nbsp;designed&nbsp;and&nbsp;managed&nbsp;many&nbsp;significant&nbsp;projects.&nbsp;He&nbsp;and&nbsp;his&nbsp;company&nbsp;were&nbsp;awarded&nbsp;“Most&nbsp;Influential&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Design&nbsp;&&nbsp;Architecture&nbsp;Company&nbsp;of&nbsp;2009&nbsp;China”.&nbsp;He&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;member&nbsp;of&nbsp;“Hall&nbsp;of&nbsp;Fame”&nbsp;(China).&nbsp;Gong&nbsp;Zhang&nbsp;is&nbsp;also&nbsp;a&nbsp;successful&nbsp;artist.&nbsp;He&nbsp;was&nbsp;invited&nbsp;by&nbsp;SNBF&nbsp;for&nbsp;Annual&nbsp;Exhibition&nbsp;in&nbsp;The&nbsp;Museum&nbsp;of&nbsp;Louver&nbsp;in&nbsp;Paris&nbsp;and&nbsp;won&nbsp;the&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Price.&nbsp;He&nbsp;brings&nbsp;his&nbsp;aesthetic&nbsp;and&nbsp;architectural&nbsp;ideas&nbsp;to&nbsp;bear&nbsp;on&nbsp;each&nbsp;project.'),(8,5.5,'郑忠','Joe Cheng','董事長','Chairman','香港鄭中設計事務所 ','Cheng Chung Design (HK) Ltd.','','public/2013/07/JoeCheng145.png','public/2013/07/JoeCheng145_small.png','鄭中先生近二十年的品牌酒店设计经验，带领着CCD（www.ccd.com.hk）设计团队走在酒店设计行业的前沿，以其远见卓识及坚定的设计理念，指引着CCD的发展。他一直坚信，真正成功的设计就是建筑与室内设计所带来的高质量建设及专注细节的完美结合。因此，每接触一个新的酒店项目，鄭先生都坚持从建筑概念设计开始就必须参与其中，根据酒店室内功能设计提出自己独特的见解，务求达到以人为本完美的效果。同时，他还坚持参与工程中的每一个细节工作，其丰富的经验使许多现场的问题都能迎刃而解。郑先生一直与合作的专业顾问公司保持良好的沟通协调，充分将其标新立异的设计理念传达给对方，并获得了业主与国际酒店管理公司的高度认可。','Joe&nbsp;Cheng&nbsp;has&nbsp;20&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;design&nbsp;experience&nbsp;with&nbsp;international&nbsp;brands.&nbsp;His&nbsp;unique&nbsp;philosophies&nbsp;regarding&nbsp;the&nbsp;perfection&nbsp;of&nbsp;design&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;combination&nbsp;of&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;and&nbsp;interior&nbsp;design&nbsp;has&nbsp;led&nbsp;the&nbsp;CCD&nbsp;team&nbsp;to&nbsp;become&nbsp;pioneers&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;design&nbsp;industry.&nbsp;He&nbsp;firmly&nbsp;believes&nbsp;that&nbsp;a&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;design&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;combination&nbsp;of&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;and&nbsp;interior&nbsp;design.&nbsp;Based&nbsp;on&nbsp;this&nbsp;philosophy,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Cheng&nbsp;Chung&nbsp;made&nbsp;his&nbsp;own&nbsp;recommendations&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;architectural&nbsp;design&nbsp;consultant&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;intent&nbsp;of&nbsp;achieving&nbsp;the&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;design.&nbsp;In&nbsp;his&nbsp;opinion,&nbsp;the&nbsp;best&nbsp;design&nbsp;should&nbsp;embody&nbsp;high-quality&nbsp;construction.&nbsp;Therefore,&nbsp;he&nbsp;is&nbsp;involved&nbsp;with&nbsp;each&nbsp;element&nbsp;in&nbsp;creating&nbsp;the&nbsp;design,&nbsp;bringing&nbsp;his&nbsp;varied&nbsp;experience&nbsp;to&nbsp;help&nbsp;realize&nbsp;the&nbsp;best&nbsp;design.&nbsp;Beyond&nbsp;his&nbsp;design&nbsp;ability&nbsp;and&nbsp;experience,&nbsp;He&nbsp;has&nbsp;always&nbsp;working&nbsp;closely&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;owners&nbsp;and&nbsp;operators&nbsp;and&nbsp;keep&nbsp;a&nbsp;great&nbsp;communication&nbsp;to&nbsp;fully&nbsp;express&nbsp;his&nbsp;design&nbsp;concept&nbsp;and&nbsp;great&nbsp;ideas.'),(9,35,'周涛','Tao Zhou','首席执行官','CEO','鲁能集团酒店管理公司','Luneng Group Hotel Management Co.','','public/2013/07/TaoZhow145.png','public/2013/07/TaoZhow145_small.png','周涛先生现任鲁能集团酒店管理公司首席执行官，担任着鲁能旗下所有酒店的运营管理和资产管理，同时负责鲁能多个在建待建酒店项目的进展。到2015年，鲁能酒店业总客房数预计将超过10,000间。<br>在加盟鲁能前，周涛先生曾担任摩根士丹利不动产基金(MSREF)旗下近20家大、中型酒店的经营管理和资产管理。近年来在日本东京作为摩根士丹利的首席酒店资产经理(Portfolio&nbsp;Head),直接领导了该基金2007年从全日空集团收购的酒店组合群(市值达30亿美元，是亚太地区史上最大笔的不动产交易项目)的资产管理。<br>在回到亚洲前，周涛先生曾活跃在北美的酒店运营管理及资产管理行业16余年，也担任了酒店的收购、管理合同谈判、再融资等。曾任利时达国际酒店集团加拿大公司(Listel&nbsp;Canada&nbsp;Ltd.)的副总裁、首席运营官。<br>周涛先生毕业于上海外国语大学。曾在复旦大学研究生院、日本庆应大学法学院、美国康奈尔大学酒店管理学院深造、研究。周涛先生是加拿大女皇大学(Queen’s&nbsp;University)商学院的MBA，也是加拿大注册管理会计师。他还是全球酒店资产经理协会(HAMA:&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;Asset&nbsp;Managers&nbsp;Association)日本分会的理事。除了母语汉语外，周涛先生还精通英语、日语。<br>','Mr.&nbsp;Tao&nbsp;Zhou&nbsp;currently&nbsp;serves&nbsp;as&nbsp;CEO&nbsp;of&nbsp;Luneng&nbsp;Group&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Management&nbsp;-&nbsp;the&nbsp;newly&nbsp;established&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Division&nbsp;of&nbsp;Luneng&nbsp;Group.&nbsp;Tao&nbsp;oversees&nbsp;both&nbsp;operation&nbsp;and&nbsp;asset&nbsp;management&nbsp;for&nbsp;all&nbsp;Luneng’s&nbsp;existing&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;assets&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;progress&nbsp;of&nbsp;its&nbsp;many&nbsp;pipeline&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;projects&nbsp;across&nbsp;China.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Prior&nbsp;to&nbsp;joining&nbsp;Luneng,&nbsp;Tao&nbsp;was&nbsp;with&nbsp;Morgan&nbsp;Stanley&nbsp;Capital&nbsp;overseeing&nbsp;a&nbsp;large&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;portfolio&nbsp;in&nbsp;Japan&nbsp;as&nbsp;Portfolio&nbsp;Head&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;focus&nbsp;on&nbsp;asset&nbsp;management,&nbsp;including&nbsp;duties&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;refinancing&nbsp;and&nbsp;underwriting.&nbsp;Before&nbsp;that,&nbsp;Tao&nbsp;was&nbsp;a&nbsp;senior&nbsp;asset&nbsp;manager&nbsp;at&nbsp;Panorama&nbsp;Hospitality,&nbsp;Morgan&nbsp;Stanley’s&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;asset&nbsp;management&nbsp;and&nbsp;operating&nbsp;unit.&nbsp;At&nbsp;Panorama,&nbsp;Tao&nbsp;was&nbsp;heavily&nbsp;involved&nbsp;in&nbsp;operation&nbsp;for&nbsp;Panorama’s&nbsp;self-operated&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;acquired&nbsp;by&nbsp;Morgan&nbsp;Stanley&nbsp;Real&nbsp;Estate&nbsp;Fund.&nbsp;During&nbsp;his&nbsp;close&nbsp;to&nbsp;six-year&nbsp;career&nbsp;at&nbsp;Morgan&nbsp;Stanley/Panorama,&nbsp;Tao&nbsp;also&nbsp;worked&nbsp;closely&nbsp;with&nbsp;various&nbsp;international&nbsp;brands.<br>Before&nbsp;moving&nbsp;back&nbsp;to&nbsp;Asia,&nbsp;Tao&nbsp;worked&nbsp;for&nbsp;over&nbsp;sixteen&nbsp;years&nbsp;in&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;industry&nbsp;in&nbsp;Canada.&nbsp;He&nbsp;worked&nbsp;on&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;acquisition,&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;agreement&nbsp;negotiation,&nbsp;refinancing,&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;asset&nbsp;management&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;operation.&nbsp;His&nbsp;last&nbsp;position&nbsp;held&nbsp;was&nbsp;COO&nbsp;for&nbsp;Listel&nbsp;Canada&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;–&nbsp;the&nbsp;Canadian&nbsp;operation&nbsp;of&nbsp;Tokyo&nbsp;based&nbsp;Listel&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Group.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Tao&nbsp;earned&nbsp;a&nbsp;BA&nbsp;from&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;International&nbsp;Studies&nbsp;University&nbsp;in&nbsp;China&nbsp;and&nbsp;an&nbsp;MBA&nbsp;from&nbsp;Queen’s&nbsp;University&nbsp;of&nbsp;Canada.&nbsp;He&nbsp;also&nbsp;studied&nbsp;and&nbsp;conducted&nbsp;research&nbsp;at&nbsp;Graduate&nbsp;Schools&nbsp;of&nbsp;Fudan&nbsp;University&nbsp;in&nbsp;China,&nbsp;Keio&nbsp;University&nbsp;in&nbsp;Japan&nbsp;and&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;School&nbsp;at&nbsp;Cornell&nbsp;University&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;USA.&nbsp;Tao&nbsp;received&nbsp;his&nbsp;designation&nbsp;of&nbsp;Certified&nbsp;Management&nbsp;Accountant&nbsp;from&nbsp;British&nbsp;Columbia,&nbsp;Canada.&nbsp;He&nbsp;was&nbsp;also&nbsp;a&nbsp;board&nbsp;member&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;Asset&nbsp;Managers&nbsp;Association&nbsp;(HAMA)&nbsp;Japan.&nbsp;Tao&nbsp;is&nbsp;fluent&nbsp;in&nbsp;Chinese,&nbsp;English&nbsp;and&nbsp;Japanese.<br>'),(10,3,'詹姆斯·查普尔','James Chappell','全球市场总监','Global Marketing Director','浩华管理顾问公司','Horwath HTL','','public/2013/08/JamesChapell145.png','public/2013/08/JamesChapell145_small.png','\"作为浩华管理顾问公司的全球营销总监，James&nbsp;Chappell&nbsp;先生工作在伦敦，负责浩华管理顾问公司全球50家分支机构的营销工作。Chappell&nbsp;先生也是浩华管理顾问公司管理委员会委员及市场营销委员会主席。<br>James&nbsp;Chappell&nbsp;先生拥有超过13年的酒店业国际销售及市场营销经验，其最初于伦敦从事广告和品牌推广，在斯德哥尔摩一家精品酒店完成了为期三年的管理培训计划后致力于酒店管理顾问工作、同时负责新酒店的概念设计。Chappell&nbsp;先生还开创了数据库收集汇总概念，由此促成了两家最成功的、可为全球市场提供最广泛竞争性信息数据公司的诞生。<br>James&nbsp;Chappell&nbsp;先生是The&nbsp;Bench公司的创始人兼董事总经理。2002年创立于斯德哥尔摩的The&nbsp;Bench公司彻底改变了酒店业数据的收集及分配格局，首次创建了供酒店业高效使用的每日市场资讯数据标杆工具。公司在发展过程中所建立的法律先例随后成为行业标准，并且该公司也因其创新品牌和市场定位广为人知。Chappell&nbsp;先生还推动The&nbsp;Bench公司与Smith&nbsp;Travel&nbsp;Research合并成为全球规模最大且运营最成功的酒店资讯公司，在40多个国家开展业务。Chappell&nbsp;先生监督了整个合并过程并担任合并后STR&nbsp;Global的总经理。在18个月的任职期间，STR&nbsp;Global的营业额增长60%。<br>Chappell&nbsp;先生也是新闻定期评论员，曾接受BBC、彭博财经电视、广播频道广播4台及涉及酒店行业的其他节目的专访。<br>\"','James&nbsp;is&nbsp;currently&nbsp;the&nbsp;Global&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;Marketing&nbsp;for&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;HTL,&nbsp;based&nbsp;in&nbsp;London&nbsp;and&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;all&nbsp;50&nbsp;HTL&nbsp;offices&nbsp;Globally.&nbsp;Jamie&nbsp;sits&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;HTL&nbsp;Management&nbsp;Committee&nbsp;and&nbsp;Chairs&nbsp;the&nbsp;Marketing&nbsp;Committee.<br>James&nbsp;has&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;13&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;international&nbsp;sales&nbsp;and&nbsp;marketing&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;industry.&nbsp;Originally&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;of&nbsp;advertising&nbsp;and&nbsp;branding&nbsp;in&nbsp;London,&nbsp;James&nbsp;completed&nbsp;a&nbsp;three-year&nbsp;management&nbsp;trainee&nbsp;programme&nbsp;at&nbsp;a&nbsp;Boutique&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;in&nbsp;Stockholm,&nbsp;before&nbsp;leaving&nbsp;to&nbsp;join&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Consultants&nbsp;Overlook&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;Management,&nbsp;with&nbsp;responsibility&nbsp;for&nbsp;designing&nbsp;new&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;concepts.&nbsp;James&nbsp;was&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;developing&nbsp;a&nbsp;data&nbsp;collection&nbsp;concept&nbsp;that&nbsp;became&nbsp;two&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;successful&nbsp;companies&nbsp;supplying&nbsp;competitive&nbsp;market&nbsp;information&nbsp;across&nbsp;the&nbsp;Globe.<br>James&nbsp;was&nbsp;founder&nbsp;and&nbsp;managing&nbsp;director&nbsp;of&nbsp;The&nbsp;Bench,&nbsp;founded&nbsp;in&nbsp;Stockholm&nbsp;in&nbsp;2002&nbsp;which&nbsp;revolutionised&nbsp;how&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;data&nbsp;was&nbsp;collected&nbsp;and&nbsp;distributed,&nbsp;creating&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;daily&nbsp;benchmarking&nbsp;tool&nbsp;adopted&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;industry.&nbsp;In&nbsp;the&nbsp;process,&nbsp;the&nbsp;company&nbsp;set&nbsp;legal&nbsp;precedents&nbsp;that&nbsp;have&nbsp;subsequently&nbsp;become&nbsp;industry&nbsp;standards&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;company&nbsp;became&nbsp;well&nbsp;known&nbsp;for&nbsp;its&nbsp;innovative&nbsp;branding&nbsp;and&nbsp;positioning.&nbsp;James&nbsp;was&nbsp;then&nbsp;instrumental&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;merger&nbsp;between&nbsp;The&nbsp;Bench,&nbsp;Deloitte&nbsp;and&nbsp;Smith&nbsp;Travel&nbsp;Research&nbsp;to&nbsp;create&nbsp;the&nbsp;worlds&nbsp;largest&nbsp;and&nbsp;most&nbsp;successful&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;Information&nbsp;Company,&nbsp;doing&nbsp;business&nbsp;in&nbsp;over&nbsp;40&nbsp;countries.&nbsp;James&nbsp;oversaw&nbsp;the&nbsp;merger&nbsp;and&nbsp;was&nbsp;Managing&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;new&nbsp;company&nbsp;STR&nbsp;Global&nbsp;for&nbsp;18&nbsp;months,&nbsp;overseeing&nbsp;a&nbsp;60%&nbsp;rise&nbsp;in&nbsp;turnover.&nbsp;<br>James&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;regular&nbsp;commenter&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;Press&nbsp;and&nbsp;has&nbsp;appeared&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;BBC,&nbsp;Bloomberg&nbsp;TV,&nbsp;Radio&nbsp;4&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;programmes&nbsp;talking&nbsp;about&nbsp;the&nbsp;industry.<br><br>'),(12,12,'梁子庚','Jereme Leung','执行总裁','CEO','梁子庚餐饮概念工作室有限公司','Jereme Leung Concepts Limited','','public/2013/08/JeremeLeung145.png','public/2013/08/JeremeLeung145_small.png','作为亚洲最具创意的新式中餐革新者,梁子庚先生是最早成功地将世界餐饮的概念完美融合进传统中餐烹饪当中的亚洲名厨。&nbsp;2002-2008年之间，梁子庚先生在上海外滩三号和北京金融街四合院内两个蜚声国内外的中餐厅—黄浦会所提供的以上海菜和北京菜为基础的新式菜肴，掀起了创意中餐的风潮，为业界提供了将国际元素与传统中餐完美结合的典范，也成为饕客追捧的时尚热点。<br>在&nbsp;2000年，梁子庚先生荣获美国餐饮管理学院颁发的&nbsp;“五星钻石国际大奖&nbsp;”，成为当之无愧的世界最佳厨师之一，与&nbsp;Charles&nbsp;Trotter、Wolfgang&nbsp;Puck、Jean-George&nbsp;Vongerichten等世界超级名厨共享盛名，并成为世界上第四位摘取此项殊荣的华人厨师。2008年梁子庚先生再次摘取了该奖项。在&nbsp;2000同年，梁子庚先生也荣获了由轩尼诗&nbsp;XO与马来西亚《巅峰》杂志联合颁发的厨艺大奖，该著名奖项旨在嘉奖在烹饪技艺上有独特创新，引领现代美食潮流的创意大师。&nbsp;<br>今天，梁子庚先生已成为一名炙手可热的餐饮顾问，并以自己的名字创立了“JL创意餐饮概念工作室”。为全球范围内的高级餐厅提供餐饮顾问，&nbsp;W台北酒店紫艳中餐厅、W广州酒店宴遇中餐厅、杭州黄龙饭店龙吟阁中餐厅、北京金茂威斯汀酒店中国元素中餐厅、重庆申基索菲特大酒店锦肴轩中餐厅等项目的餐饮都是梁子庚先生与世界各大知名酒店品牌合作开发一系列全新的餐饮品牌的餐饮顾问事业的成功范例。<br>继2009年CCTV&nbsp;10“人物”栏目的拍摄后，梁子庚于2012年参与了CCTV&nbsp;1的大型美食纪录片“舌尖上的中国”（第五集）的拍摄，成为杭州地区舌尖上美食的代表。同年，梁子庚还接到上海东方卫视的邀约，成为“星光耀东方”节目第一位厨师嘉宾。继而又跟探索频道合作，共同拍摄了“创艺启示录之食悟”宣传片。2013年，梁子庚接受了上海东方卫视“顶级厨师”节目组的邀请，成为“顶级厨师”第二季的主评委，重磅出击打造中国首档美食才艺秀节目，为中国饮食界挖掘更多有才能及潜质的餐饮人才。<br>','As&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;creative&nbsp;Asian&nbsp;pioneer&nbsp;of&nbsp;Modern&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;Cuisines,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Jereme&nbsp;Leung&nbsp;is&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;pioneer&nbsp;chef&nbsp;who&nbsp;perfectly&nbsp;blends&nbsp;the&nbsp;concept&nbsp;of&nbsp;Modern&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;Cuisines&nbsp;with&nbsp;classical&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;provincial&nbsp;food.&nbsp;Between&nbsp;2002&nbsp;and&nbsp;2008,&nbsp;he&nbsp;created&nbsp;and&nbsp;operates&nbsp;two&nbsp;&nbsp;Whampoa&nbsp;Club&nbsp;Restaurant&nbsp;serving&nbsp;new&nbsp;Shanghainese&nbsp;and&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;cuisines,&nbsp;located&nbsp;at&nbsp;Shanghai\'s&nbsp;Three&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;Bund&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;quadrangle&nbsp;courtyard&nbsp;on&nbsp;Financial&nbsp;Street&nbsp;in&nbsp;Beijing.&nbsp;Both&nbsp;venues&nbsp;stirred&nbsp;up&nbsp;great&nbsp;enthusiasm&nbsp;for&nbsp;“Modern&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;Cuisines”&nbsp;around&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;and&nbsp;set&nbsp;excellent&nbsp;examples&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;integration&nbsp;of&nbsp;traditional&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;cuisines&nbsp;with&nbsp;international&nbsp;elements&nbsp;which&nbsp;were&nbsp;very&nbsp;well&nbsp;received&nbsp;and&nbsp;much&nbsp;lauded&nbsp;among&nbsp;gourmands.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>In&nbsp;2000,&nbsp;Leung&nbsp;joined&nbsp;the&nbsp;ranks&nbsp;of&nbsp;culinary&nbsp;supernovas&nbsp;like&nbsp;Charlie&nbsp;Trotter,&nbsp;Paul&nbsp;Bocuse,&nbsp;Wolfgang&nbsp;Puck&nbsp;and&nbsp;Jean-Georges&nbsp;Vongerichten&nbsp;when&nbsp;The&nbsp;American&nbsp;Academy&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;Science&nbsp;conferred&nbsp;upon&nbsp;him&nbsp;the&nbsp;Five&nbsp;Star&nbsp;Diamond&nbsp;Award,&nbsp;naming&nbsp;him&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;\"World\'s&nbsp;Best&nbsp;Chefs\"&nbsp;He&nbsp;was&nbsp;awarded&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;honor&nbsp;again&nbsp;in&nbsp;2008.&nbsp;Leung&nbsp;was&nbsp;also&nbsp;awarded&nbsp;the&nbsp;prestigious&nbsp;XO&nbsp;Hennessy&nbsp;Culinary&nbsp;Award&nbsp;in&nbsp;2000,&nbsp;which&nbsp;recognizes&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;chefs&nbsp;working&nbsp;in&nbsp;Malaysia&nbsp;for&nbsp;their&nbsp;creativity&nbsp;and&nbsp;prominence&nbsp;in&nbsp;developing&nbsp;gourmet&nbsp;culinary&nbsp;trends.&nbsp;<br>Today,&nbsp;Jereme&nbsp;Leung&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;renowned&nbsp;food&nbsp;and&nbsp;beverage&nbsp;concept&nbsp;services&nbsp;consultant.&nbsp;He&nbsp;established&nbsp;Jereme&nbsp;Leung&nbsp;Creative&nbsp;Concepts&nbsp;－J.L.&nbsp;after&nbsp;his&nbsp;own&nbsp;name&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;food&nbsp;service&nbsp;consulting&nbsp;for&nbsp;top&nbsp;restaurants&nbsp;around&nbsp;the&nbsp;world.&nbsp;The&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;cuisines&nbsp;served&nbsp;in&nbsp;those&nbsp;world-famous&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;W&nbsp;Taipei’s&nbsp;Yen&nbsp;Restaurant,&nbsp;W&nbsp;Guangzhou’s&nbsp;Yan&nbsp;Yu&nbsp;Restaurant,&nbsp;Dragon&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Hangzhou’s&nbsp;Grand&nbsp;Dragon&nbsp;Restaurant,&nbsp;Westin&nbsp;Beijing’s&nbsp;Zen5se&nbsp;Restaurant,&nbsp;Sofitel&nbsp;Chongqing’s&nbsp;JYX&nbsp;Restaurant&nbsp;and&nbsp;Yalongwan&nbsp;Seaview&nbsp;International&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;are&nbsp;all&nbsp;successful&nbsp;examples&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;cooperation&nbsp;between&nbsp;Jereme&nbsp;Leung&nbsp;and&nbsp;world-famous&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;chains&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;development&nbsp;of&nbsp;new&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;cuisine&nbsp;brands.&nbsp;<br>Following&nbsp;the&nbsp;shooting&nbsp;of&nbsp;“People”&nbsp;Program&nbsp;of&nbsp;CCTV&nbsp;Channel&nbsp;10&nbsp;in&nbsp;2009,&nbsp;Jereme&nbsp;Leung&nbsp;participated&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;shooting&nbsp;of&nbsp;“A&nbsp;Bite&nbsp;of&nbsp;China”&nbsp;(Episode&nbsp;5),&nbsp;a&nbsp;large&nbsp;cuisine&nbsp;documentary&nbsp;of&nbsp;CCTV&nbsp;Channel&nbsp;1&nbsp;in&nbsp;2012&nbsp;and&nbsp;became&nbsp;the&nbsp;cuisine&nbsp;