onal&nbsp;and&nbsp;Local&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;in&nbsp;China&nbsp;and&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific,&nbsp;performing&nbsp;Revenue&nbsp;Management&nbsp;Audits,&nbsp;Remote&nbsp;support,&nbsp;SOP&nbsp;development,&nbsp;training&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;Revenue&nbsp;Management&nbsp;improvement&nbsp;projects.'),(14,27,'Lachlan Wolfers','Lachlan Wolfers','税务合伙人','Partner','毕马威','KPMG','','public/2013/08/LachlanWolfers145.png','public/2013/08/LachlanWolfers145_small.png','自2011年7月起，Lachlan从毕马威澳大利亚调任至毕马威中国任合伙人职位。<br>Lachlan负责毕马威上海的增值税改革项目，在此期间，他为客户提供了超过40场的研讨会，涉及一般咨询服务、金融服务、交通和物流服务、资产租赁等多个议题。<br>应许多跨国公司客户的要求，Lachlan领导了若干增值税改革项目和有关的营业税项目，并帮助客户向税务机关澄清技术性问题或有争议的事宜。<br>在加入毕马威中国之前，Lachlan曾任毕马威澳大利亚的流转税实务和税务争议实务的合伙人。他现为毕马威全球间接税领导小组成员。<br>Lachlan曾任澳大利亚最大税务协会的董事。在此期间，澳洲税局和联邦税署多次邀请他参与税务事宜讨论。此外，他还曾为中国和美国的官员提供关于流转税改革的咨询服务。<br>在加入毕马威前,&nbsp;Lachlan担任过大型律所的合伙人，因此，他对国外的税务和法务事宜经验丰富。他曾在澳大利亚高等法院、澳大利亚联邦法院、行政上诉法庭等法庭出庭，包括澳大利亚首例巨额流转税案件。<br>Lachlan善于增值税方面的演讲，他曾多次为专业机构、行业组织和客户就中国增值税改革提供演讲。','Lachlan&nbsp;has&nbsp;led&nbsp;KPMG’s&nbsp;efforts&nbsp;in&nbsp;relation&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;VAT&nbsp;reform&nbsp;pilot&nbsp;program&nbsp;in&nbsp;China.&nbsp;In&nbsp;the&nbsp;course&nbsp;of&nbsp;this,&nbsp;Lachlan&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;asked&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;advice&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Ministry&nbsp;of&nbsp;Finance,&nbsp;the&nbsp;State&nbsp;Administration&nbsp;of&nbsp;Taxation&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;Government&nbsp;agencies&nbsp;in&nbsp;relation&nbsp;to&nbsp;several&nbsp;key&nbsp;aspects&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;VAT&nbsp;reforms,&nbsp;including&nbsp;the&nbsp;application&nbsp;of&nbsp;VAT&nbsp;to&nbsp;financial&nbsp;services,&nbsp;insurance,&nbsp;transfers&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;business,&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;other&nbsp;reforms&nbsp;relating&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;introduction&nbsp;of&nbsp;Advance&nbsp;Rulings&nbsp;in&nbsp;China.<br>Lachlan&nbsp;has&nbsp;also&nbsp;led&nbsp;projects&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;VAT&nbsp;reforms,&nbsp;and&nbsp;related&nbsp;business&nbsp;tax&nbsp;issues,&nbsp;for&nbsp;a&nbsp;large&nbsp;number&nbsp;of&nbsp;multinational&nbsp;clients,&nbsp;including&nbsp;assisting&nbsp;clients&nbsp;with&nbsp;seeking&nbsp;clarification&nbsp;of&nbsp;technical&nbsp;or&nbsp;contentious&nbsp;issues&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;tax&nbsp;authorities.&nbsp;<br>Lachlan&nbsp;is&nbsp;formerly&nbsp;a&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;The&nbsp;Tax&nbsp;Institute,&nbsp;which&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;prestigious&nbsp;tax&nbsp;professional&nbsp;association&nbsp;in&nbsp;Australia.&nbsp;In&nbsp;this&nbsp;role,&nbsp;Lachlan&nbsp;was&nbsp;frequently&nbsp;invited&nbsp;to&nbsp;consult&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;Australian&nbsp;Taxation&nbsp;Office&nbsp;and&nbsp;Commonwealth&nbsp;Treasury&nbsp;on&nbsp;tax&nbsp;issues,&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;consulting&nbsp;with&nbsp;Government&nbsp;officials&nbsp;from&nbsp;both&nbsp;China&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;United&nbsp;States&nbsp;in&nbsp;relation&nbsp;to&nbsp;reforms&nbsp;of&nbsp;indirect&nbsp;taxes&nbsp;while&nbsp;he&nbsp;was&nbsp;in&nbsp;Australia.<br>Prior&nbsp;to&nbsp;joining&nbsp;KPMG,&nbsp;Lachlan&nbsp;was&nbsp;a&nbsp;partner&nbsp;in&nbsp;a&nbsp;major&nbsp;law&nbsp;firm,&nbsp;and&nbsp;has&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;a&nbsp;broad&nbsp;range&nbsp;of&nbsp;taxation&nbsp;and&nbsp;legal&nbsp;matters.&nbsp;He&nbsp;has&nbsp;appeared&nbsp;before&nbsp;the&nbsp;High&nbsp;Court&nbsp;of&nbsp;Australia,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Federal&nbsp;Court&nbsp;of&nbsp;Australia&nbsp;&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;Administrative&nbsp;Appeals&nbsp;Tribunal,&nbsp;including&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;substantive&nbsp;GST&nbsp;case&nbsp;in&nbsp;Australia.<br>Lachlan&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;noted&nbsp;speaker&nbsp;on&nbsp;VAT&nbsp;issues&nbsp;and&nbsp;has&nbsp;also&nbsp;presented&nbsp;numerous&nbsp;seminars&nbsp;for&nbsp;various&nbsp;professional&nbsp;associations,&nbsp;industry&nbsp;groups&nbsp;and&nbsp;clients&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;VAT&nbsp;reforms&nbsp;in&nbsp;China.'),(15,29,'夏农','Nong Xia','首席副总裁，地产及开发','Senior Vice President, Real Estate & Development','凯悦酒店及度假