s&nbsp;Group,&nbsp;Deputy&nbsp;General&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;of&nbsp;Greenland&nbsp;International&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;Group&nbsp;and&nbsp;several&nbsp;General&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;posts&nbsp;started&nbsp;with&nbsp;IHG&nbsp;since&nbsp;1999.<br>Mr.&nbsp;Zhang&nbsp;hold&nbsp;M.&nbsp;Ec&nbsp;and&nbsp;B.A.&nbsp;from&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;Renmin&nbsp;University&nbsp;since&nbsp;1983.<br>'),(18,1,'周卓瓴','Jolyon Bulley','大中华区首席运营官','Chief Operating Officer, Greater China','洲际酒店管理集团','InterContinental Hotels Group','','public/2013/08/JolyonBulley145.png','public/2013/08/JolyonBulley145_small.png','周卓瓴先生是大中华区首席运营官，自2011年3月起在上海总部管理领导洲际酒店集团（IHG）大中华区约200家酒店的运营战略方向和营运绩效工作，包括洲际酒店，皇冠假日酒店，英迪格酒店，假日酒店和智选假日酒店五大品牌。他同时还负责领导IHG大中华区约180家在建酒店的运营规划，并为华邑酒店及度假村品牌的推出提供运营标准方面的支持。除此之外，他还负责IHG的F&B战略，酒店开业流程并与IHG酒店的业主方通力协作。他是IHG全球运营委员会的成员之一。<br>周卓瓴最早通过在澳大利亚希尔顿酒店的工作开始与酒店行业结缘，随后曾在澳大利亚，新西兰，马来西亚和泰国的南太平洋酒店集团（如今的IHG）工作。1998年，他加入BT酒店（现为马化国际），成为海曼岛度假酒店的总经理，后来还参与了该公司奢侈品牌酒店的资产管理。他于2001年在悉尼重新加入IHG。在到中国工作之前，他还曾在新加坡任职6年，先后担任东南亚区和西南亚区运营副总裁。<br>','Jolyon&nbsp;is&nbsp;Chief&nbsp;Operating&nbsp;Officer&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China&nbsp;and&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;based&nbsp;in&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;since&nbsp;March&nbsp;2011&nbsp;where&nbsp;he&nbsp;leads&nbsp;IHG’s&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China&nbsp;operations&nbsp;strategic&nbsp;direction&nbsp;and&nbsp;operating&nbsp;performance&nbsp;for&nbsp;their&nbsp;around&nbsp;200&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;across&nbsp;the&nbsp;InterContinental,&nbsp;Crowe&nbsp;Plaza,&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Indigo,&nbsp;Holiday&nbsp;Inn&nbsp;and&nbsp;Holiday&nbsp;Inn&nbsp;Express&nbsp;brands.&nbsp;He&nbsp;also&nbsp;leads&nbsp;the&nbsp;operations&nbsp;planning&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;around&nbsp;180&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;in&nbsp;IHG’s&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China&nbsp;pipeline&nbsp;and&nbsp;operational&nbsp;standards&nbsp;to&nbsp;support&nbsp;the&nbsp;launch&nbsp;of&nbsp;HUALUXE&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;Resorts.&nbsp;Jolyon&nbsp;is&nbsp;also&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;IHG’s&nbsp;F&B&nbsp;strategy,&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Opening&nbsp;process&nbsp;and&nbsp;works&nbsp;collaboratively&nbsp;with&nbsp;IHG’s&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Owners.&nbsp;He&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;member&nbsp;of&nbsp;IHG’s&nbsp;Global&nbsp;Operations&nbsp;Council.<br>Jolyon&nbsp;started&nbsp;his&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;career&nbsp;with&nbsp;Hilton&nbsp;in&nbsp;Australia&nbsp;and&nbsp;Southern&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;Corporation&nbsp;(now&nbsp;IHG)&nbsp;working&nbsp;in&nbsp;Australia,&nbsp;New&nbsp;Zealand,&nbsp;Malaysia&nbsp;and&nbsp;Thailand.&nbsp;In&nbsp;1998&nbsp;he&nbsp;joined&nbsp;BT&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;(now&nbsp;Mulpha)&nbsp;as&nbsp;General&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;Hayman&nbsp;Island&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;and&nbsp;then&nbsp;Asset&nbsp;Managed&nbsp;their&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;portfolio.&nbsp;He&nbsp;rejoined&nbsp;IHG&nbsp;in&nbsp;Sydney&nbsp;in&nbsp;2001&nbsp;and&nbsp;prior&nbsp;to&nbsp;relocating&nbsp;to&nbsp;China&nbsp;spent&nbsp;6&nbsp;years&nbsp;in&nbsp;Singapore&nbsp;as&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President&nbsp;Operations&nbsp;South&nbsp;East&nbsp;and&nbsp;later&nbsp;also&nbsp;South&nbsp;West&nbsp;Asia.<br>'),(19,2,'陈国昌','Andy Chan','大中华区餐饮部副总裁','Vice President, Food & Beverage, Greater China','洲际酒店集团','InterContinental Hotels Group Greater China','','public/2013/08/AndyChan145.png','public/2013/08/AndyChan145_small.png','在上海总部，Andy致力于推动大中华区的餐饮（食品与饮料）品牌特色与优化运作绩效，并贯彻洲际酒店集团的核心策略，将集团文化与餐饮概念紧密结合。作为一名大中华区领导团队的先锋以及全球餐饮委员会的成员,他在引领大中华区餐饮团队不断发展和前进的同时还致力于挖掘和培养有潜力的人才。<br>超过30年的餐饮经验和丰富阅历，来自新加坡的Andy，在亚洲以及大中华区早已是享负盛名，非常受人尊崇。他的职业生涯启航于新加坡的凯悦集团。<br>于2001年开始，Andy相继在香格里拉的几个最大规模的酒店担任餐饮部总监。2005年起,他转战到香格里拉集团总部负责大中华区的餐饮运营工作并晋升到资深总监一职全权负责和开发所有在香港的餐饮项目。<br>','Based&nbsp;in&nbsp;Shanghai,&nbsp;Andy&nbsp;drives&nbsp;the&nbsp;Food&nbsp;and&nbsp;Beverage&nbsp;(F&B)&nbsp;Brands&nbsp;and&nbsp;Operations&nbsp;performance&nbsp;priorities&nbsp;for&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China,&nbsp;and&nbsp;executes&nbsp;the&nbsp;core&nbsp;strategies&nbsp;that&nbsp;embed&nbsp;IHG&nbsp;culture&nbsp;into&nbsp;F&B&nbsp;concepts.&nbsp;As&nbsp;a&nbsp;member&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China&nbsp;Operations&nbsp;Leadership&nbsp;team&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;Global&nbsp;F&B&nbsp;Council&nbsp;team,&nbsp;he&nbsp;has&nbsp;since&nbsp;been&nbsp;leading&nbsp;the&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China&nbsp;regional&nbsp;F&B&nbsp;team&nbsp;while&nbsp;developing&nbsp;great&nbsp;talents&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;time.&nbsp;<br>Having&nbsp;acquired&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;30&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;F&B&nbsp;experience,&nbsp;Andy&nbsp;originally&nbsp;from&nbsp;Singapore,&nbsp;has&nbsp;become&nbsp;a&nbsp;well-known&nbsp;leader&nbsp;and&nbsp;are&nbsp;highly&nbsp;respected&nbsp;in&nbsp;this&nbsp;field&nbsp;within&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;and&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China.&nbsp;He&nbsp;was&nbsp;initially&nbsp;with&nbsp;Hyatt&nbsp;Group&nbsp;based&nbsp;in&nbsp;Singapore.<br>In&nbsp;2001,&nbsp;Andy&nbsp;moved&nbsp;on&nbsp;to&nbsp;Shangri-La&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;F&B&nbsp;in&nbsp;some&nbsp;of&nbsp;their&nbsp;largest&nbsp;hotels.&nbsp;2005&nbsp;onwards,&nbsp;he&nbsp;moved&nbsp;on&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Shangri-La&nbsp;Corporate&nbsp;F&B&nbsp;Operations&nbsp;role&nbsp;for&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China&nbsp;region&nbsp;and&nbsp;progressed&nbsp;to&nbsp;a&nbsp;Senior&nbsp;Director&nbsp;position,&nbsp;in-charge&nbsp;of&nbsp;all&nbsp;F&B&nbsp;Project&nbsp;Developments&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong.&nbsp;<br>'),(20,4,'陈敏','Min Chen','酒店事业部副总经理','Deputy General Manager, Hotel Division','中粮置地有限公司','COFCO Land Limited','','public/2013/08/ChenMin145.png','public/2013/08/ChenMin145_small.png','陈敏先生毕业于对外经济贸易大学，加入中粮集团后担任主管小麦进口业务的经理。<br>之后，被派驻中粮在澳洲的澳大利亚鹏利有限公司工作，负责中粮在澳洲的粮食进口业务。2006年5月，担任中粮集团酒店投资部总经理。自2008年8月，担任中粮集团酒店事业部副总经理，负责集团的酒店发展规划和投资建设。自2008年以来，根据“清理、提升、发展”的原则，整合了中粮集团的酒店资产，并致力于高端商务酒店和度假酒店的投资、开发。目前，由原来三亚凯莱度假酒店改扩建的三亚美高梅度假酒店已隆重开业，同时，北京台湾饭店和北京凯莱大酒店正在进行原址重建，将建设成为华尔道夫酒店和W酒店。<br>','Graduated&nbsp;from&nbsp;University&nbsp;of&nbsp;International&nbsp;Business&nbsp;and&nbsp;Economics，Mr.&nbsp;Chen&nbsp;started&nbsp;his&nbsp;career&nbsp;in&nbsp;COFCO&nbsp;as&nbsp;wheat&nbsp;trade&nbsp;manager.&nbsp;Later,&nbsp;he&nbsp;worked&nbsp;for&nbsp;Top&nbsp;Glory&nbsp;(Australia)&nbsp;Pty&nbsp;Ltd.,&nbsp;a&nbsp;subsidiary&nbsp;overseas&nbsp;office&nbsp;of&nbsp;COFCO.&nbsp;As&nbsp;the&nbsp;general&nbsp;manager&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;company,&nbsp;he&nbsp;was&nbsp;in&nbsp;charge&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;grain&nbsp;import&nbsp;from&nbsp;Australia.&nbsp;From&nbsp;May&nbsp;2006,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Chen&nbsp;leads&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Investment&nbsp;Division&nbsp;of&nbsp;COFCO.&nbsp;Since&nbsp;Aug&nbsp;2008&nbsp;he&nbsp;has&nbsp;served&nbsp;as&nbsp;Deputy&nbsp;General&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;for&nbsp;COFCO\'s&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Division,&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;development&nbsp;and&nbsp;investment&nbsp;business.&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Chen&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;consolidating&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;assets&nbsp;of&nbsp;COFCO,&nbsp;and&nbsp;dedicated&nbsp;to&nbsp;invest&nbsp;and&nbsp;develop&nbsp;luxurious&nbsp;business&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;resorts.&nbsp;At&nbsp;present,&nbsp;Taiwan&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;and&nbsp;Gloria&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;are&nbsp;being&nbsp;redeveloped,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Waldorf&nbsp;Astoria&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;and&nbsp;W&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;are&nbsp;coming&nbsp;soon.'),(21,6,'杜宏新','Eric Du','总经理','General Manager','杭州黄龙饭店','The Dragon Hangzhou','','public/2013/08/EricDu145.png','public/2013/08/EricDu145_small.png','杜宏新先生于2002年6月加入了当时还是中外合资的杭州黄龙饭店担任总经理，这也是浙江省杭州市旅游集团第一次对外公开招聘职业经理人，杜宏新先生凭借自身卓越的实力和对饭店行业的热爱，最终获得了杭旅集团的青睐。<br>在此之前，杜宏新先生曾留学美国拉斯维加斯四年，攻读美国内华达州立大学的酒店管理硕士学位，实地的感受到世界顶级酒店的管理和服务，了解到国际酒店业发展新趋势，获得了真正的解决实际问题的方法和技巧。回国后，杜宏新先生并没有满足于杭州黄龙饭店已有的辉煌业绩，他深深的了解在经济全球化背景下，本土酒店业最终要走向世界，谋求国际化经营发展。&nbsp;<br>于是，在2007年杭州黄龙饭店开始全面的改扩建时，杜宏新先生就下定决心要实现自己打造最聪明酒店的梦想。他表示“未来酒店业的趋势，就是智能化和信息化。奢华是可以模仿的，服务却难以复制，新的杭州黄龙饭店会将智能化进行到底。恰到好处的IT应用一定会成为未来酒店竞争的关键。”<br>杜宏新先生亲自参与了杭州黄龙饭店的改建策划，并在自己擅长的IT、音乐及艺术鉴赏等方面积极地与设计师交换意见，为饭店的每一项改革倾尽心血。2010年，按照国际豪华五星级标准打造的杭州黄龙饭店全面竣工营业。这家承载着杜宏新先生梦想的饭店必定会以国际化卓越服务理念和创新精神成为行业的典范，带动整个酒店行业的发展和提升，引领中国本土高端品牌酒店发展的走向。<br>','Mr.&nbsp;Eric&nbsp;Du&nbsp;joined&nbsp;Dragon&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;Hangzhou&nbsp;and&nbsp;served&nbsp;as&nbsp;general&nbsp;manager&nbsp;in&nbsp;June&nbsp;2002,&nbsp;when&nbsp;this&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;was&nbsp;still&nbsp;a&nbsp;joint&nbsp;venture.&nbsp;This&nbsp;was&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;time&nbsp;that&nbsp;Hangzhou&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Group&nbsp;publicly&nbsp;recruited&nbsp;professional&nbsp;managers.&nbsp;The&nbsp;Group&nbsp;thought&nbsp;highly&nbsp;of&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Eric&nbsp;Du,&nbsp;by&nbsp;virtue&nbsp;of&nbsp;his&nbsp;superior&nbsp;strengths&nbsp;and&nbsp;enthusiasm&nbsp;for&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;industry.<br>Prior&nbsp;to&nbsp;this,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Eric&nbsp;Du&nbsp;had&nbsp;studied&nbsp;in&nbsp;University&nbsp;of&nbsp;Nevada,&nbsp;Las&nbsp;Vegas,&nbsp;United&nbsp;States&nbsp;for&nbsp;four&nbsp;years,&nbsp;assiduously&nbsp;for&nbsp;a&nbsp;master&nbsp;degree&nbsp;in&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management.&nbsp;He&nbsp;experienced&nbsp;the&nbsp;world’s&nbsp;leading&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;and&nbsp;services,&nbsp;learned&nbsp;about&nbsp;new&nbsp;trends&nbsp;in&nbsp;international&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;industry,&nbsp;and&nbsp;acquired&nbsp;real&nbsp;solutions&nbsp;and&nbsp;techniques&nbsp;regarding&nbsp;practical&nbsp;problems.&nbsp;After&nbsp;returning&nbsp;home,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Eric&nbsp;Du&nbsp;was&nbsp;not&nbsp;satisfied&nbsp;with&nbsp;brilliant&nbsp;performance&nbsp;of&nbsp;Dragon&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;as&nbsp;he&nbsp;was&nbsp;well&nbsp;aware&nbsp;that&nbsp;in&nbsp;context&nbsp;of&nbsp;economic&nbsp;globalization,&nbsp;local&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;industry&nbsp;would&nbsp;finally&nbsp;go&nbsp;global&nbsp;and&nbsp;seek&nbsp;for&nbsp;international&nbsp;business&nbsp;development.<br>Therefore,&nbsp;when&nbsp;Dragon&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;started&nbsp;all-sided&nbsp;reconstruction&nbsp;and&nbsp;expansion&nbsp;in&nbsp;2007,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Eric&nbsp;Du&nbsp;was&nbsp;determined&nbsp;to&nbsp;realize&nbsp;his&nbsp;dream&nbsp;of&nbsp;creating&nbsp;the&nbsp;smartest&nbsp;hotel.&nbsp;He&nbsp;indicated&nbsp;that&nbsp;“The&nbsp;future&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;industry&nbsp;trend&nbsp;is&nbsp;intelligence&nbsp;and&nbsp;information.&nbsp;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;easy&nbsp;to&nbsp;imitate&nbsp;luxury,&nbsp;but&nbsp;it&nbsp;is&nbsp;difficult&nbsp;to&nbsp;replicate&nbsp;services.&nbsp;The&nbsp;new&nbsp;smart&nbsp;Dragon&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;will&nbsp;follow&nbsp;through&nbsp;with&nbsp;intelligence.&nbsp;Proper&nbsp;IT&nbsp;applications&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;key&nbsp;to&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;competitions&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;future.&nbsp;”<br>Mr.&nbsp;Eric&nbsp;Du&nbsp;personally&nbsp;participated&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;reconstruction&nbsp;plans&nbsp;for&nbsp;Dragon&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;actively&nbsp;exchanged&nbsp;views&nbsp;with&nbsp;designers&nbsp;in&nbsp;such&nbsp;areas&nbsp;as&nbsp;IT,&nbsp;music&nbsp;and&nbsp;art&nbsp;appreciation&nbsp;in&nbsp;which&nbsp;he&nbsp;was&nbsp;adept,&nbsp;and&nbsp;made&nbsp;every&nbsp;effort&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel’s&nbsp;every&nbsp;reform.&nbsp;Dragon&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;in&nbsp;accordance&nbsp;with&nbsp;international&nbsp;standards&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;five-star&nbsp;hotel,&nbsp;was&nbsp;completed&nbsp;and&nbsp;opened&nbsp;for&nbsp;business&nbsp;in&nbsp;2010.&nbsp;This&nbsp;hotel,&nbsp;which&nbsp;carries&nbsp;the&nbsp;dream&nbsp;of&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Eric&nbsp;Du,&nbsp;will&nbsp;undoubtedly&nbsp;become&nbsp;an&nbsp;industry&nbsp;example&nbsp;relying&nbsp;on&nbsp;international&nbsp;excellent&nbsp;service&nbsp;concepts&nbsp;and&nbsp;innovative&nbsp;spirits,&nbsp;will&nbsp;drive&nbsp;development&nbsp;and&nbsp;upgrading&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;entire&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;industry,&nbsp;and&nbsp;will&nbsp;set&nbsp;trends&nbsp;for&nbsp;China’s&nbsp;domestic&nbsp;high-end&nbsp;hotels.<br>'),(22,7,'尤静芬','Eu Chin Fen','投资总监','Chief Investment Officer','辉盛国际管理有限公司','Frasers Hospitality Pte Ltd.','','public/2013/08/ChinFenEu145.png','public/2013/08/ChinFenEu145_small.png','尤静芬作为辉盛国际管理有限公司的投资总监，负责公司的业务开发与投资管理。在加入辉盛之前，她曾在新加坡发展银行（DBS）担任房地产投资信托基金及企业信托基金团队高级副总裁，在金融领域拥有15年的丰富经验。<br>在新加坡发展银行任职期间，尤女士在国内多个房地产投资信托基金和企业信托基金首次公开募股和第二次募股活动中发挥了关键作用，其中包括嘉茂信托、星狮地产信托、星狮商产信托、丰树物流信托、凯诗物流