','美高梅国际度假集团','MGM Resorts International','','public/2013/08/KennethFeng145.png','public/2013/08/KennethFeng145_small.png','冯小峰先生于2001年加入美高梅集团，担任高级财务分析师，并自此在该集团连续任职12年至今。在担任高级财务分析师期间，冯小峰先生协助集团财务副总裁在完成了对曼德拉湾酒店的并购及澳门项目的开发工作，并在澳门美高梅项目发展中扮演了重要角色。2006年，冯小峰先生倡导并参与促成了美高梅国际度假集团在中国首家合资企业的成立，即与中国的钓鱼台国宾馆合作的钓鱼台美高梅酒店管理公司，并在了该公司的主要项目开发事业中作出突出贡献。鉴于冯小峰先生在美高梅集团亚太区战略发展中的突出成绩，2007年冯先生被提拔为集团国际运营部副总裁，2009年成为高级副总裁。<br>冯小峰先生拥有哥伦比亚大学的财务硕士学位，出国前他就读于南开大学国际经济专业并获学士学位，大学毕业后，冯先生还曾在中国最大的国有企业之一工作过四年。','Kenneth&nbsp;joined&nbsp;MGM&nbsp;in&nbsp;2001&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;Sr.&nbsp;Financial&nbsp;Analyst&nbsp;and&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;company&nbsp;for&nbsp;twelve&nbsp;years&nbsp;since.&nbsp;&nbsp;When&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;Sr.&nbsp;Financial&nbsp;Analyst,&nbsp;Kenneth&nbsp;assisted&nbsp;VP&nbsp;of&nbsp;Corporate&nbsp;Finance&nbsp;in&nbsp;acquisition&nbsp;of&nbsp;Mandalay&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;and&nbsp;in&nbsp;Macau&nbsp;project&nbsp;development.&nbsp;&nbsp;He&nbsp;played&nbsp;a&nbsp;key&nbsp;role&nbsp;in&nbsp;developing&nbsp;MGM&nbsp;Macau.&nbsp;&nbsp;In&nbsp;2006&nbsp;he&nbsp;initiated&nbsp;MGM’s&nbsp;first&nbsp;JV&nbsp;in&nbsp;China&nbsp;with&nbsp;Diaoyutai&nbsp;State&nbsp;Guest&nbsp;House&nbsp;and&nbsp;successfully&nbsp;involved&nbsp;in&nbsp;major&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;projects&nbsp;there.&nbsp;&nbsp;Because&nbsp;of&nbsp;his&nbsp;performance&nbsp;and&nbsp;role&nbsp;in&nbsp;Asian&nbsp;strategic&nbsp;planning&nbsp;he&nbsp;was&nbsp;promoted&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;position&nbsp;of&nbsp;VP&nbsp;International&nbsp;Operation&nbsp;in&nbsp;2007,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Sr.&nbsp;VP&nbsp;MGM&nbsp;International&nbsp;in&nbsp;2009.&nbsp;<br>Kenneth&nbsp;holds&nbsp;a&nbsp;MS&nbsp;in&nbsp;Finance&nbsp;degree&nbsp;with&nbsp;Columbia&nbsp;University.&nbsp;&nbsp;Before&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;US&nbsp;he&nbsp;graduated&nbsp;from&nbsp;Nankai&nbsp;University&nbsp;in&nbsp;China&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;BS&nbsp;in&nbsp;International&nbsp;Economy&nbsp;and&nbsp;worked&nbsp;for&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;largest&nbsp;state&nbsp;o