nbsp;legal&nbsp;service.'),(27,14,'林聪','Colin Lin','中国地区酒店业务发展高级副总裁','Senior Vice President, Hotel Development, China ','万豪国际集团','Marriott International','','public/2013/08/ColinLin145.png','public/2013/08/ColinLin145_small.png','林聪先生现任万豪国际集团中国地区酒店业务发展高级副总裁，负责万豪国际集团旗下九个品牌在中国地区的发展。万豪旗下这九个品牌为宝格丽酒店品牌、丽思卡尔顿酒店品牌、JW万豪酒店品牌、艾迪逊酒店品牌、万豪酒店品牌、傲途格酒店品牌、万丽酒店品牌、万豪行政公寓品牌和万怡酒店品牌。林聪先生于2003年加入万豪国际集团。在此之前，自1989年起，林聪先生就职于美国麦克唐纳•道格拉斯飞机公司，负责麦道飞机在中国业务的拓展工作。从1994年起，林聪先生加入美国菲利普•莫里斯亚太集团中国部工作，曾担任公司市场开拓、团队管理、公司产品市场营销等重要工作职位。','Holding&nbsp;the&nbsp;position&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Senior&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President,&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Development,&nbsp;China&nbsp;of&nbsp;Marriott&nbsp;International,&nbsp;Inc.,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Colin&nbsp;Lin&nbsp;is&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;development&nbsp;of&nbsp;Marriott’s&nbsp;key&nbsp;brands,&nbsp;including&nbsp;Bulgari,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Ritz-Carlton,&nbsp;JW&nbsp;Marriott,&nbsp;EDITION,&nbsp;Marriott,&nbsp;Autograph&nbsp;Collection,&nbsp;Renaissance,&nbsp;Marriott&nbsp;Executive&nbsp;Apartments&nbsp;and&nbsp;Courtyard&nbsp;by&nbsp;Marriott&nbsp;in&nbsp;China.<br>Mr.&nbsp;Lin&nbsp;joined&nbsp;Marriott&nbsp;in&nbsp;2003.&nbsp;Before&nbsp;that,&nbsp;he&nbsp;worked&nbsp;for&nbsp;McDonnell-Douglas&nbsp;Corporation&nbsp;from&nbsp;1989.&nbsp;<br>Since&nbsp;1994,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Lin&nbsp;worked&nbsp;in&nbsp;Philip&nbsp;Morris&nbsp;(Asia-&nbsp;Pacific)&nbsp;Company&nbsp;Inc.,&nbsp;and&nbsp;held&nbsp;various&nbsp;positions&nbsp;of&nbsp;Development,&nbsp;Team&nbsp;Management&nbsp;and&nbsp;Marketing&nbsp;&&nbsp;Sales.<br>'),(28,15,'马里奥','Mario Piazza','Group Director of Recreation','Group Director of Recreation','悦榕庄','Banyan Tree Hotels & Resorts ','','public/2013/08/MarioPiazza145.png','public/2013/08/MarioPiazza145_small.png','马里奥（Mario&nbsp;Piazza）出生于澳大利亚布里斯班，三岁时移居悉尼，并在那里进行了他的大部分研究。在马里奥十二岁的时候，他的父母决定搬回意大利老家，因此又在那里生活了七年，之后再次回到悉尼。在意大利生活期间，苦于找不到合适的工作，马里奥最终进入了意大利一家管道设备公司，并在那里获得了一定的工作经验。在不久后，他返回悉尼，继续在建筑行业工作了七年。经过再三考虑，马里奥终于决定要改变自己的职业道路，进入酒店行业——这是改变他一生的决定。<br>在酒店作了一年的行李员之后，马里奥收到一份去印度尼西亚担任康乐部经理的工作邀请——由于他具有体育背景，而这正是该公司所需要的。久经辗转，他最终加入了悦榕集团。至今为止，他已在该集团担任Group&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;Recreation八年之多。<br>马里奥恪尽职守，为悦榕集团创造了巨大的价值。在他的正确领导下，公司的休闲业务不断走向标准化，业务范围也越来越广。迄今为止，他参与了悦榕庄许多新酒店和度假村的筹建工作。<br>此外，马里奥在很多职业体育赛事中也发挥了重要的作用。他连续7年担任泰国普吉岛乐古浪度假村国际铁人三项赛事的统筹，还在越南乐古浪度假村成功举办了首届铁人三项比赛并担任赛事总监。<br>目前，在悦榕集团总裁的要求下，马里奥前往上海，旨在为未来五年的酒店项目和开业筹备提供更多的支持。<br>作为娱乐界的领袖级人物，马里奥对体育活动也有着浓厚的兴趣，是个不可多得的体育全才。他酷爱自行车运动，并且会亲自参加铁人三项比赛，曾在悉尼和意大利打了9年多职业曲棍球，还喜欢在闲暇时间当DJ打碟。<br>马里奥已在亚洲生活工作逾17年，此间获得了广泛的生活经历和工作经验，并在与悦榕集团一起成长的过程中克服了重重挑战。<br>','Mario&nbsp;was&nbsp;born&nbsp;in&nbsp;Brisbane&nbsp;Australia&nbsp;and&nbsp;moved&nbsp;to&nbsp;Sydney&nbsp;when&nbsp;he&nbsp;was&nbsp;3&nbsp;years&nbsp;old&nbsp;and&nbsp;carried&nbsp;out&nbsp;most&nbsp;of&nbsp;his&nbsp;studies&nbsp;there.&nbsp;When&nbsp;he&nbsp;was&nbsp;12&nbsp;years&nbsp;old&nbsp;his&nbsp;parents&nbsp;decided&nbsp;to&nbsp;move&nbsp;back&nbsp;to&nbsp;Italy,&nbsp;and&nbsp;lived&nbsp;there&nbsp;for&nbsp;7&nbsp;years&nbsp;before&nbsp;moving&nbsp;back&nbsp;to&nbsp;Sydney.&nbsp;Whilst&nbsp;living&nbsp;in&nbsp;Italy&nbsp;he&nbsp;found&nbsp;it&nbsp;very&nbsp;hard&nbsp;to&nbsp;find&nbsp;work&nbsp;and&nbsp;was&nbsp;offered&nbsp;to&nbsp;work&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;plumbing&nbsp;company&nbsp;where&nbsp;he&nbsp;gained&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;this&nbsp;field.&nbsp;Not&nbsp;long&nbsp;after&nbsp;that&nbsp;he&nbsp;moved&nbsp;back&nbsp;to&nbsp;Sydney&nbsp;continuing&nbsp;his&nbsp;journey&nbsp;for&nbsp;another&nbsp;7&nbsp;years&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;building&nbsp;industry.&nbsp;After&nbsp;many&nbsp;considerations,&nbsp;Mario&nbsp;moved&nbsp;on&nbsp;and&nbsp;changed&nbsp;his&nbsp;whole&nbsp;career&nbsp;path&nbsp;and&nbsp;joined&nbsp;the&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;industry,&nbsp;where&nbsp;this&nbsp;changed&nbsp;his&nbsp;life&nbsp;forever.&nbsp;<br>After&nbsp;1&nbsp;year&nbsp;working&nbsp;as&nbsp;Bellman,&nbsp;he&nbsp;received&nbsp;an&nbsp;offer&nbsp;to&nbsp;work&nbsp;in&nbsp;Indonesia,&nbsp;as&nbsp;Recreation&nbsp;Manager;&nbsp;given&nbsp;his&nbsp;sports&nbsp;background,&nbsp;this&nbsp;matched&nbsp;the&nbsp;criteria&nbsp;the&nbsp;company&nbsp;was&nbsp;looking&nbsp;for.&nbsp;&nbsp;Some&nbsp;years&nbsp;down&nbsp;the&nbsp;line&nbsp;he&nbsp;finally&nbsp;joined&nbsp;the&nbsp;Banyan&nbsp;Tree&nbsp;Group,&nbsp;where&nbsp;he&nbsp;has&nbsp;successfully&nbsp;been&nbsp;working&nbsp;for&nbsp;over&nbsp;8&nbsp;years&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;Group&nbsp;Recreation&nbsp;Director.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>As&nbsp;a&nbsp;fully&nbsp;committed&nbsp;person,&nbsp;Mario&nbsp;has&nbsp;added&nbsp;tremendous&nbsp;value&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;group,&nbsp;standardizing&nbsp;recreation&nbsp;and&nbsp;bringing&nbsp;this&nbsp;department&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;right&nbsp;direction&nbsp;to&nbsp;attract&nbsp;more&nbsp;business&nbsp;for&nbsp;his&nbsp;company.&nbsp;He&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;involved&nbsp;in&nbsp;most&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;that&nbsp;has&nbsp;opened&nbsp;till&nbsp;date.<br>Also&nbsp;Mario&nbsp;has&nbsp;played&nbsp;an&nbsp;important&nbsp;role&nbsp;with&nbsp;our&nbsp;professional&nbsp;sporting&nbsp;events&nbsp;over&nbsp;the&nbsp;years,&nbsp;coordinating&nbsp;International&nbsp;Triathlon&nbsp;events&nbsp;in&nbsp;Laguna&nbsp;Phuket&nbsp;Thailand&nbsp;for&nbsp;7&nbsp;years&nbsp;and&nbsp;also&nbsp;successfully&nbsp;launched&nbsp;Laguna&nbsp;LangCo&nbsp;first&nbsp;Inaugural&nbsp;Triathlon&nbsp;event&nbsp;in&nbsp;Vietnam,&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;Race&nbsp;Director.&nbsp;<br>Mario&nbsp;is&nbsp;now&nbsp;based&nbsp;in&nbsp;Shanghai,&nbsp;which&nbsp;was&nbsp;decided&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;CEO&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;group,&nbsp;in&nbsp;order&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;further&nbsp;support&nbsp;with&nbsp;all&nbsp;the&nbsp;projects&nbsp;and&nbsp;openings&nbsp;coming&nbsp;up&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;next&nbsp;5&nbsp;years.&nbsp;<br>Being&nbsp;a&nbsp;Recreation&nbsp;guru,&nbsp;his&nbsp;pretty&nbsp;much&nbsp;into&nbsp;his&nbsp;sports&nbsp;as&nbsp;an&nbsp;all-rounder&nbsp;sporting&nbsp;person,&nbsp;and&nbsp;his&nbsp;really&nbsp;i