营董事会成员。在任期间，Ingo在东方文华酒店集团旗下创立了生活方式部门，同时负责集团全球运营，负责四大洲15个度假村SPA项目的设计与运营工作。<br>2005年，Ingo因其在酒店领域将养生与休闲服务独特的结合方式，荣获“年度杰出SPA行业个人”奖项；同时在2006年，凭借极富创意和有效的营销方式，获得“年度SPA行业杰出营销人”奖。2006年，在Ingo的领导下，东方文华酒店被欧洲SPA峰会、SpaAsia杂志授予“最佳SPA企业”。Ingo在集团中的概念及工作也在2007年纽约“Gold&nbsp;Key&nbsp;Award”颁奖盛典上被评为“杰出酒店设计”奖。<br>任职于东方文华之前，Ingo曾担任拉斐尔酒店集团南亚地区活动执行总监。在他的指导下，全球知名的SPA疗养地“喜马拉雅山阿南达温泉度假村”项目落成。Ingo还曾于1996至1998年期间担任奥拜瑞酒店的集团总监，负责了Rajvilas，Udaivilas及Amarvilas&nbsp;3个印度酒店项目的筹备。因在奥拜瑞集团期间的杰出贡献，美国酒店科学学院于1998年授予Ingo“年度杰出酒店人”奖项。<br>Ingo的诸多作品目前仍是行业内的顶尖项目，如&nbsp;Condé&nbsp;Nast&nbsp;Traveller曾获得“最佳SPA项目”奖项。<br>','Ingo&nbsp;Schweder,&nbsp;Founder&nbsp;and&nbsp;Managing&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;HTL&nbsp;Health&nbsp;and&nbsp;Wellness,&nbsp;leads&nbsp;the&nbsp;Market&nbsp;Research&nbsp;&&nbsp;Feasibility&nbsp;and&nbsp;Concept&nbsp;Development&nbsp;team&nbsp;to&nbsp;success.&nbsp;He&nbsp;brings&nbsp;with&nbsp;him&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;30&nbsp;years&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;fields&nbsp;of&nbsp;hospitality,&nbsp;wellness&nbsp;and&nbsp;spa.<br>In&nbsp;2009,&nbsp;after&nbsp;working&nbsp;his&nbsp;way&nbsp;up&nbsp;the&nbsp;corporate&nbsp;ladder&nbsp;and&nbsp;settling&nbsp;into&nbsp;a&nbsp;grouping&nbsp;of&nbsp;successful&nbsp;and&nbsp;influential&nbsp;roles&nbsp;with&nbsp;leading&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;companies,&nbsp;Ingo&nbsp;founded&nbsp;his&nbsp;own&nbsp;wellness&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;consulting&nbsp;and&nbsp;management&nbsp;company&nbsp;GOCO&nbsp;Hospitality.&nbsp;Based&nbsp;in&nbsp;Bangkok&nbsp;with&nbsp;regional&nbsp;offices&nbsp;in&nbsp;Berlin&nbsp;&&nbsp;soon&nbsp;Shanghai,&nbsp;the&nbsp;team&nbsp;numbers&nbsp;25&nbsp;people,&nbsp;14&nbsp;nationalities,&nbsp;and&nbsp;is&nbsp;working&nbsp;on&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;20&nbsp;projects&nbsp;across&nbsp;multiple&nbsp;continents.&nbsp;<br>Ingo&nbsp;is&nbsp;considered&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;foremost&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;&&nbsp;spa&nbsp;experts&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;world,&nbsp;and&nbsp;his&nbsp;experiences&nbsp;and&nbsp;accolades&nbsp;to&nbsp;date&nbsp;are&nbsp;a&nbsp;testament.&nbsp;<br>From&nbsp;2000&nbsp;–&nbsp;2006&nbsp;he&nbsp;served&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;member&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;operating&nbsp;board&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Mandarin&nbsp;Oriental&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Group.&nbsp;During&nbsp;his&nbsp;tenure,&nbsp;Ingo&nbsp;established&nbsp;the&nbsp;Mandarin&nbsp;Oriental&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Group’s&nbsp;Lifestyle&nbsp;Division&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;ground&nbsp;up.&nbsp;&nbsp;He&nbsp;was&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;worldwide&nbsp;operation,&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;development&nbsp;of&nbsp;15&nbsp;resort&nbsp;spas&nbsp;on&nbsp;four&nbsp;continents.&nbsp;<br>In&nbsp;2005,&nbsp;Ingo&nbsp;was&nbsp;recognized&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;“Spa&nbsp;Personality&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Year”&nbsp;award&nbsp;for&nbsp;his&nbsp;visionary&nbsp;approach&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;integration&nbsp;of&nbsp;wellness&nbsp;and&nbsp;leisure&nbsp;services&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;industry,&nbsp;and&nbsp;in&nbsp;2006&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;“Spa&nbsp;Marketer&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Year”&nbsp;for&nbsp;his&nbsp;innovative&nbsp;and&nbsp;effective&nbsp;marketing&nbsp;approach.&nbsp;In&nbsp;2006&nbsp;and&nbsp;under&nbsp;Ingo\'s&nbsp;leadership,&nbsp;the&nbsp;European&nbsp;Spa&nbsp;Summit&nbsp;and&nbsp;SpaAsia&nbsp;Magazine&nbsp;voted&nbsp;Mandarin&nbsp;Oriental&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;“Best&nbsp;Spa&nbsp;Company.”&nbsp;Ingo\'s&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;concept&nbsp;work&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;group&nbsp;was&nbsp;also&nbsp;honored&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;prestigious&nbsp;Gold&nbsp;Key&nbsp;Award&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;“Excellence&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;Design”&nbsp;event&nbsp;in&nbsp;New&nbsp;York&nbsp;City&nbsp;2007.<br>Prior&nbsp;to&nbsp;Mandarin,&nbsp;Ingo&nbsp;was&nbsp;Managing&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Rafael&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Groups’&nbsp;activities&nbsp;in&nbsp;South&nbsp;Asia.&nbsp;Under&nbsp;his&nbsp;guidance&nbsp;“Ananda&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;Himalayas,”&nbsp;the&nbsp;globally&nbsp;recognized&nbsp;destination&nbsp;spa,&nbsp;was&nbsp;established.&nbsp;Ingo&nbsp;was&nbsp;also&nbsp;group&nbsp;director&nbsp;of&nbsp;operations&nbsp;for&nbsp;Oberoi&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;from&nbsp;1996&nbsp;–&nbsp;1998&nbsp;where&nbsp;he&nbsp;headed&nbsp;the&nbsp;development&nbsp;of&nbsp;3&nbsp;new&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;projects&nbsp;—&nbsp;Rajvilas,&nbsp;Udaivilas&nbsp;and&nbsp;Amarvilas&nbsp;that&nbsp;transformed&nbsp;the&nbsp;landscape&nbsp;of&nbsp;Indian&nbsp;Hospitality.&nbsp;For&nbsp;his&nbsp;work&nbsp;with&nbsp;Oberoi&nbsp;Hotels,&nbsp;the&nbsp;American&nbsp;Academy&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;Sciences&nbsp;recognized&nbsp;him&nbsp;in&nbsp;1998&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;“Hotelier&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Year”&nbsp;award.<br>Many&nbsp;of&nbsp;his&nbsp;past&nbsp;projects&nbsp;still&nbsp;today&nbsp;top&nbsp;the&nbsp;list&nbsp;of&nbsp;some&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;leading&nbsp;industry&nbsp;awards&nbsp;including&nbsp;Condé&nbsp;Nast&nbsp;Traveller,&nbsp;winning&nbsp;“Best&nbsp;Spa’s”&nbsp;honors.&nbsp;<br><br>'),(31,18,'施政延','Cetin Sekercioglu','执行副总裁','Executive Vice President','香格里拉酒店集团','Shangri-La Hotels and Resorts','','public/2013/08/CetinSekercioglu145.png','public/2013/08/CetinSekercioglu145_small.png','施政延先生来自土耳其，于1994年9月加入香格里拉酒店集团，现在中国出任集团执行副总裁一职。拥有在土耳其、美国、法国、英国、瑞士和意大利的酒店管理经验。<br>在香格里拉，施政延先生曾担任香港集团总部要职，新加坡和上海的副总裁一职和泰国的区域总经理。他也曾任职多家香格里拉大酒店的总经理，包括马来西亚莎莉雅香格里拉、大连香格里拉、曼谷香格里拉、雅加达香格里拉、新加坡香格里拉和上海浦东香格里拉。<br>施政延先生可讲6国语言，并在哈佛商学院与斯坦福商学院修过经理人课程。<br><br>关于香格里拉酒店集团&nbsp;/&nbsp;享誉全球的待客之道<br>香格里拉酒店集团的第一家豪华酒店于1971年在新加坡开业。&nbsp;<br>「香格里拉」的名字，源于英国作家詹姆斯•希尔顿于1933年出版的传奇名著《消失的地平线》中所描写的一处梦幻世外桃源。许多年后，香格里拉酒店集团以其幽雅、安逸的环境与久负盛名、发自内心的殷勤待客之道，为这个名字作了完美的诠释。<br>时至今日，总部位于香港的香格里拉酒店集团已成为亚太地区最大的豪华酒店集团，同时是世界上公认的最佳酒店产权和管理公司之一。<br>香格里拉酒店集团的82家城市及度假酒店遍布亚太地区、北美、中东和欧洲，客房总数已超过34,000间。<br>此外，香格里拉酒店集团还在中国大陆、加纳、香港、印度、印尼、意大利、蒙古共和国、缅甸、菲律宾、新加坡、卡塔尔、斯里兰卡和英国兴建新的酒店。<br><br>','Cetin&nbsp;Sekercioglu&nbsp;is&nbsp;currently&nbsp;leading&nbsp;Shangri-la&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;Corporate&nbsp;Office&nbsp;as&nbsp;Executive&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President&nbsp;in&nbsp;China.&nbsp;He&nbsp;is&nbsp;of&nbsp;Turkish&nbsp;Nationality&nbsp;and&nbsp;joined&nbsp;the&nbsp;Group&nbsp;in&nbsp;Sept.&nbsp;1994.&nbsp;His&nbsp;previous&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;management&nbsp;experience&nbsp;includes&nbsp;posts&nbsp;in&nbsp;Turkey,&nbsp;USA,&nbsp;France,&nbsp;England,&nbsp;Switzerland&nbsp;and&nbsp;Italy.&nbsp;<br>Cetin&nbsp;has&nbsp;held&nbsp;Senior&nbsp;Corporate&nbsp;Executive&nbsp;Positions&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong,&nbsp;Singapore&nbsp;and&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;as&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President&nbsp;and&nbsp;Area&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;in&nbsp;Thailand.&nbsp;He&nbsp;also&nbsp;managed&nbsp;the&nbsp;following&nbsp;properties&nbsp;as&nbsp;General&nbsp;Manager;&nbsp;Shangri-la&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Rasa&nbsp;Ria&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;in&nbsp;Malaysia,&nbsp;Shangri-la&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Dalian&nbsp;in&nbsp;China,&nbsp;Shangri-la&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Bangkok,&nbsp;Shangri-la&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Jakarta,&nbsp;Shangri-la&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Singapore;&nbsp;Pudong&nbsp;Shangri-la&nbsp;in&nbsp;Shanghai.&nbsp;<br>He&nbsp;speaks&nbsp;6&nbsp;languages&nbsp;and&nbsp;attended&nbsp;executive&nbsp;programs&nbsp;both&nbsp;at&nbsp;Harvard&nbsp;and&nbsp;Stanford&nbsp;Business&nbsp;Schools.&nbsp;<br><br>ABOUT&nbsp;SHANGRI-LA&nbsp;GROUP/&nbsp;LEGENDARY&nbsp;HOSPITALITY<br>The&nbsp;Shangri-La&nbsp;story&nbsp;began&nbsp;in&nbsp;1971&nbsp;with&nbsp;our&nbsp;first&nbsp;deluxe&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;in&nbsp;Singapore.<br>Inspired&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;legendary&nbsp;land&nbsp;featured&nbsp;in&nbsp;James&nbsp;Hilton\'s&nbsp;1933&nbsp;novel,&nbsp;Lost&nbsp;Horizon,&nbsp;the&nbsp;name&nbsp;Shangri-La&nbsp;encapsulates&nbsp;the&nbsp;serenity&nbsp;and&nbsp;service&nbsp;for&nbsp;which&nbsp;our&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;resorts&nbsp;are&nbsp;renowned&nbsp;worldwide.<br>Today,&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong-based&nbsp;Shangri-La&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;is&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific\'s&nbsp;leading&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;group.&nbsp;&nbsp;We&nbsp;are&nbsp;also&nbsp;regarded&nbsp;as&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;world’s&nbsp;finest&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;ownership&nbsp;and&nbsp;management&nbsp;companies.<br>With&nbsp;82&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;resorts&nbsp;throughout&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific,&nbsp;North&nbsp;America,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Middle&nbsp;East,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Europe,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Shangri-La&nbsp;group&nbsp;has&nbsp;a&nbsp;room&nbsp;inventory&nbsp;of&nbsp;over&nbsp;34,000.&nbsp;<br>In&nbsp;addition,&nbsp;new&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;are&nbsp;under&nbsp;development&nbsp;in&nbsp;Mainland&nbsp;China,&nbsp;Ghana,&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong,&nbsp;India,&nbsp;Indonesia,&nbsp;Italy,&nbsp;Mongolia,&nbsp;Myanmar,&nbsp;Philippines,&nbsp;Singapore,&nbsp;Qatar,&nbsp;Sri&nbsp;Lanka&nbsp;and&nbsp;United&nbsp;Kingdom.<br>'),(32,19,'沈峰','Robin Shen','集团副总裁','Vice President','世茂地产集团','Shimao Real Estate Group','','public/2013/08/RobinShen145.png','public/2013/08/RobinShen145_small.png','沈峰先生现任世茂地产集团副总裁、世茂酒店管理公司总经理，负责世茂地产集团旗下所有托管酒店和自营酒店的投资于管理；沈峰从事酒店行业超过20年，曾服务于万达集团，任万达酒店建设有限公司副总经理兼运营部总经理，负责万达集团旗下所有酒店项目的管理合同谈判、酒店筹备及开业后的资产管理；还在厦门国际航空港集团、香格里拉集团、洲际集团及喜达屋集团任职。','Mr.&nbsp;Robin&nbsp;Shen&nbsp;is&nbsp;currently&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shimao&nbsp;Group&nbsp;and&nbsp;General&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shimao&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Management&nbsp;Corporation,&nbsp;and&nbsp;takes&nbsp;charge&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;investment&nbsp;and&nbsp;management&nbsp;of&nbsp;all&nbsp;managed&nbsp;and&nbsp;self-owned&nbsp;hotels.&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Robin&nbsp;Shen&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;industry&nbsp;for&nbsp;over&nbsp;two&nbsp;decades.&nbsp;He&nbsp;served&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Group&nbsp;as&nbsp;Deputy&nbsp;General&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;of&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Construction&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;and&nbsp;General&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;of&nbsp;Operations,&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;management&nbsp;contract&nbsp;negotiation,&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;preparation&nbsp;and&nbsp;post-opening&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;asset&nbsp;management&nbsp;for&nbsp;all&nbsp;its&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;projects.&nbsp;He&nbsp;once&nbsp;worked&nbsp;for&nbsp;Xiamen&nbsp;International&nbsp;Airport&nbsp;Group,&nbsp;Shangri-La&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts,&nbsp;InterContinental&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;Group,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Starwood&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts.'),(33,22,'孙斌','Bin Sun','校长','Principal','公益机构巅峰户外运动学校','Summit School (NPO)','','public/2013/08/BinSun145.png','public/2013/08/BinSun145_small.png','The&nbsp;North&nbsp;Face（美国）、Camp（意大利）、Sector（意大利）赞助运动员，北京师范大学珠海分院运动休闲学院客座教授，西藏户外协会常务理事，巅峰户外运动学校校长，巅峰探游负责人。毕业于北京大学，曾是北京大学山鹰社的骨干，攀岩队队长；2000年，因对攀登的激情和对山峰的热爱而加入国家登山队,&nbsp;拥有丰富的攀登经验和登山活动组织经验，国内系列攀岩、攀冰、高山向导课程的设计者和教练；2006-2008年服务于北京奥组委，任火炬接力中心珠峰传递组组长，负责火炬接力珠峰传递项目；2008年，&nbsp;从国家体育总局辞职，创立北京巅峰探游体育文化有限公司，致力于提供全球范围内的探险旅行服务；2012年，创立公益机构巅峰户外运动学校，并任校长，为国内的原住民向导、俱乐部领队、大学社团提供攀登相关培训课程。','Sun&nbsp;Bin&nbsp;is&nbsp;an&nbsp;athlete&nbsp;sponsored&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;North&nbsp;Face&nbsp;(United&nbsp;States),&nbsp;Camp&nbsp;(Italy),&nbsp;and&nbsp;Sector&nbsp;(Italy),&nbsp;and&nbsp;serves&nbsp;as&nbsp;visiting&nbsp;professor&nbsp;of&nbsp;Sports&nbsp;&&nbsp;Leisure&nbsp;College&nbsp;at&nbsp;Zhuhai&nbsp;Branch&nbsp;of&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Normal&nbsp;University,&nbsp;Executive&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;Tibet&nbsp;Outdoor&nbsp;Association,&nbsp;Principal&nbsp;of&nbsp;Summit&nbsp;School,&nbsp;and&nbsp;person&nbsp;in&nbsp;charge&nbsp;of&nbsp;Pinnacle&nbsp;Exploration.&nbsp;He&nbsp;graduated&nbsp;from&nbsp;Peking&nbsp;University&nbsp;and&nbsp;was&nbsp;the&nbsp;backbone&nbsp;of&nbsp;Eagle&nbsp;Club&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;rock&nbsp;climbing&nbsp;team&nbsp;captain.&nbsp;In&nbsp;2000,&nbsp;he&nbsp;joined&nbsp;the&nbsp;national&nbsp;climbing&nbsp;team&nbsp;out&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;passion&nbsp;for&nbsp;climbing&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;love&nbsp;to&nbsp;mountains.&nbsp;With&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;climbing&nbsp;and&nbsp;organizing&nbsp;mountaineering&nbsp;activities,&nbsp;Sun&nbsp;Bin&nbsp;has&nbsp;designed&nbsp;and&nbsp;instructed&nbsp;the&nbsp;domestic&nbsp;series&nbsp;of&nbsp;rock&nbsp;climbing,&nbsp;ice&nbsp;climbing,&nbsp;and&nbsp;mountain&nbsp;guide&nbsp;courses.&nbsp;He&nbsp;served&nbsp;the&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Olympic&nbsp;Organizing&nbsp;Committee&nbsp;during&nbsp;2006-2008&nbsp;as&nbsp;Everest&nbsp;relay&nbsp;team&nbsp;leader&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;torch&nbsp;relay&nbsp;center,&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;torch&nbsp;relay&nbsp;in&nbsp;Everest.&nbsp;He&nbsp;resigned&nbsp;from&nbsp;General&nbsp;Administration&nbsp;of&nbsp;Sport&nbsp;in&nbsp;2008,&nbsp;and&nbsp;founded&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Pinnacle&nbsp;Exploration&nbsp;and&nbsp;Physical&nbsp;Culture&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd,&nbsp;which&nbsp;is&nbsp;committed&nbsp;to&nbsp;worldwide&nbsp;adventure&nbsp;travel&nbsp;services.&nbsp;In&nbsp;2012,&nbsp;he&nbsp;created&nbsp;the&nbsp;nonprofit&nbsp;organization,&nbsp;Pinnacle&nbsp;Outdoor&nbsp;Sports&nbsp;School&nbsp;as&nbsp;Principal&nbsp;and&nbsp;provides&nbsp;climbing&nbsp;training&nbsp;courses&nbsp;for&nbsp;domestic&nbsp;aboriginal&nbsp;guides,&nbsp;club&nbsp;leaders,&nbsp;and&nbsp;university&nbsp;communities.'),(34,23,'丁华','Ting Wah','工程项目副总裁','Vice President, Project Development','马哥孛罗酒店管理集团','Marco Polo Hotels','','public/2013/08/WahTing145.png','public/2013/08/WahTing145_small.png','丁华先生是马哥孛罗酒店管理集团的工程项目副总裁，常驻香港。<br>丁华先生的建筑工程管理生涯开始于香港一家著名的建筑公司。在投身建筑领域数年之后，他加入了九龙仓集团有限公司，随后又转入该集团旗下的马哥孛罗酒店管理公司，并带头组建了企业工程技术部，主要提供酒店工程管理及相关技术服务。自此，他参与了中国香港、中国大陆、东南亚和美国多家酒店的建设和翻新工程设计工作。在中国工作20多年来，他积累了广泛的工程设计经验。<br>丁华先生毕业于香港理工大学，他还是香港大学跨学科设计及管理学理学硕士，具有注册专业工程师、英国皇家特许建造师和皇家特许测量师等认证资格。<br>','Mr&nbsp;Ting&nbsp;Wah&nbsp;is&nbsp;currently&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President,&nbsp;Project&nbsp;Development&nbsp;of&nbsp;Marco&nbsp;Polo&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;based&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong.&nbsp;<br>Mr&nbsp;Ting&nbsp;started&nbsp;his&nbsp;construction&nbsp;management&nbsp;career&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;leading&nbsp;building&nbsp;construction&nbsp;company&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong.&nbsp;After&nbsp;spending&nbsp;several&nbsp;years&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;construction&nbsp;field,&nbsp;he&nbsp;joined&nbsp;The&nbsp;Wharf&nbsp;(Holdings)&nbsp;Limited,&nbsp;and&nbsp;was&nbsp;subsequently&nbsp;transferred&nbsp;internally&nbsp;to&nbsp;Marco&nbsp;Polo&nbsp;Hotels,&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;subsidiary,&nbsp;to&nbsp;set&nbsp;up&nbsp;the&nbsp;Corporate&nbsp;Project&nbsp;&&nbsp;Technical&nbsp;division&nbsp;which&nbsp;focuses&nbsp;on&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;project&nbsp;management&nbsp;and&nbsp;technical&nbsp;services.&nbsp;Since&nbsp;then,&nbsp;he&nbsp;was&nbsp;involved&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;development&nbsp;of&nbsp;numerous&nbsp;new&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;renovation&nbsp;projects&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong,&nbsp;China,&nbsp;South&nbsp;East&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;and&nbsp;USA.&nbsp;He&nbsp;has&nbsp;gained&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;project&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;China&nbsp;for&nbsp;20&nbsp;years.&nbsp;<br>Mr&nbsp;Ting&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;Registered&nbsp;Professional&nbsp;Engineer,&nbsp;Chartered&nbsp;Builder&nbsp;and&nbsp;Chartered&nbsp;Surveyor,&nbsp;a&nbsp;graduate&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;Polytechnic&nbsp;and&nbsp;received&nbsp;his&nbsp;MSc&nbsp;in&nbsp;Interdisciplinary&nbsp;Design&nbsp;&&nbsp;Management&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;University&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong.<br>'),(35,25,'王新','Wang Xin','凯燕国际饭店管理有限公司副总经理、诺金国际饭店管理有限公司总经理','Deputy General Manager of Key International Hotels Management Co., Ltd. and Managing Director of NUO','','','','public/2013/08/XinWang145.png','public/2013/08/XinWang145_small.png','王新，拥有32年酒店管理经验，曾就读于北京市旅游局服务学校，之后在德国多特蒙德饭店管理学校学习酒店管理专业，并于澳门国际公开大学获得MBA硕士学位。<br>从最初的北京燕京饭店的厨师，到如今凯宾斯基酒店在中国项目拓展的负责人以及诺金饭店品牌的推广者，王新将自己酒店经营的才能发挥得淋漓尽致。<br>从1988到1990年，作为北京市旅游局饭店星级评定办公室官员，王新参与了200多家饭店的星级评定；1990年到1995年，王新担任北京凯宾斯基饭店高级行政助理及餐饮部总监职务，并参与了凯宾斯基饭店的筹建工作，使餐饮部的工作步入正轨；1995年至2001年，于北京燕莎城酒店管理公司任总经理一职。自2001年凯宾斯基进入中国以来，作为北京凯燕国际饭店管理有限公司的副总经理，王新开发了位于成都、沈阳、大连、无锡、上海、天津、银川、惠州、呼和浩特、深圳、重庆、苏州、贵阳和青岛等城市的凯宾斯基饭店项目，并签定了管理合同，成功地将凯宾斯基推广到中国重要的一线及二线城市。<br>如今，王新致力于民族品牌NUO诺金饭店项目的开发，秉承“中式、奢华、现代、绿色”的理念，力图在继承中国传统文化的基础上进行创新，使来自于全球各地的顾客体味视觉、听觉、嗅觉、味觉以及触觉等方方面面的中国式独特感觉，体验具有国际标准的中国式服务，让属于中华民族的五星级酒店品牌在国际舞台上熠熠生辉。<br>','Wang&nbsp;Xin&nbsp;has&nbsp;over&nbsp;32&nbsp;years&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;industry.Graduated&nbsp;from&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Administration&nbsp;Service&nbsp;School,&nbsp;Wang&nbsp;Xin&nbsp;then&nbsp;studied&nbsp;at&nbsp;Dultmund&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Management&nbsp;School&nbsp;in&nbsp;Germany&nbsp;and&nbsp;Obtained&nbsp;MBA&nbsp;Master&nbsp;Degree&nbsp;at&nbsp;Macau&nbsp;International&nbsp;Public&nbsp;University&nbsp;in&nbsp;2001.			<br>From&nbsp;1988&nbsp;to1990,Wang&nbsp;Xin&nbsp;took&nbsp;the&nbsp;place&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Officer&nbsp;of&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Administration&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Star&nbsp;Evaluation&nbsp;Department.<br>From&nbsp;1990&nbsp;to&nbsp;1995,Wang&nbsp;Xin,who&nbsp;became&nbsp;the&nbsp;Senior&nbsp;Executive&nbsp;Assistant&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;&nbsp;F&B&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;Kempinski&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;in&nbsp;Beijing,was&nbsp;involved&nbsp;for&nbsp;pre-opening&nbsp;and&nbsp;got&nbsp;the&nbsp;Food&nbsp;&&nbsp;Beverage	team&nbsp;adopted&nbsp;to&nbsp;international&nbsp;5&nbsp;star&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;standards.<br>From&nbsp;1995&nbsp;to&nbsp;2001,Wang&nbsp;Xin&nbsp;became&nbsp;the&nbsp;General&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;of&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Yan&nbsp;Sha&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Management&nbsp;Co.,Ltd.	<br>From&nbsp;2001&nbsp;until&nbsp;now,&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;Deputy&nbsp;Managing&nbsp;Director&nbsp;Key&nbsp;International&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;Management&nbsp;Co.,Ltd.,&nbsp;Wang&nbsp;Xin&nbsp;has&nbsp;developed&nbsp;Kempinski&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;projects&nbsp;in&nbsp;various&nbsp;cities&nbsp;and&nbsp;get&nbsp;Management&nbsp;Agreement&nbsp;signed&nbsp;in&nbsp;Chengdu,&nbsp;Shenyang,&nbsp;Dalian,&nbsp;Wuxi,&nbsp;Shanghai,&nbsp;Tianjin,&nbsp;Yinchuan,&nbsp;Huizhou,&nbsp;Hohhot,&nbsp;Shenzhen,&nbsp;Chongqing,&nbsp;Suzhou,&nbsp;Guiyang&nbsp;and&nbsp;Qingdao.&nbsp;<br>'),(36,31,'翟月','Darlena Zhai','项目总监','Project Director','浩华管理顾问公司','Horwath HTL','','public/2013/08/DarlenaZhai145.png','public/2013/08/DarlenaZhai145_small.png','翟月是浩华管理顾问公司香港办公室的项目总监。自2007年加入浩华以来，翟小姐曾参与中国地区及亚洲主要市场的80多个项目，项目内容主要包括财务及市场可行性研究，重新定位的翻修改造项目研究，旅游目的地策划及管理公司筛选等工作。在工作期间，翟小姐所参与的项目类型广泛，包括独立单体酒店，&nbsp;度假区整体开发规划及大型综合开发项目等。&nbsp;翟小姐拥有美国纽约州康乃尔大学酒店管理学院的学士学位。','Darlena&nbsp;Zhai&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;Project&nbsp;Director&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;office&nbsp;of&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;HTL.&nbsp;&nbsp;Since&nbsp;joining&nbsp;Horwath&nbsp;HTL&nbsp;in&nbsp;2007,&nbsp;Ms.&nbsp;Zhai&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;involved&nbsp;in&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;80&nbsp;projects,&nbsp;including&nbsp;feasibility&nbsp;and&nbsp;market&nbsp;studies,&nbsp;renovation&nbsp;and&nbsp;repositioning&nbsp;studies,&nbsp;destination&nbsp;tourism&nbsp;planning,&nbsp;and&nbsp;operator&nbsp;selection&nbsp;engagements&nbsp;in&nbsp;key&nbsp;markets&nbsp;across&nbsp;China&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific.&nbsp;&nbsp;The&nbsp;types&nbsp;of&nbsp;projects&nbsp;that&nbsp;she&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;involved&nbsp;in&nbsp;range&nbsp;from&nbsp;stand-alone&nbsp;business&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;resort&nbsp;properties,&nbsp;to&nbsp;integrated&nbsp;resort&nbsp;developments&nbsp;and&nbsp;large&nbsp;scale&nbsp;mixed-use&nbsp;urban&nbsp;developments.&nbsp;&nbsp;Ms.&nbsp;Zhai&nbsp;holds&nbsp;a&nbsp;Bachelors&nbsp;of&nbsp;Science&nbsp;degree&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Management&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;School&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Administration&nbsp;at&nbsp;Cornell&nbsp;University,&nbsp;New&nbsp;York,&nbsp;United&nbsp;States&nbsp;of&nbsp;America.'),(37,36,'朱晓东','Lily Zhu','副总裁','Vice President','中国银泰投资有限公司','Beijing Yin Tai Property Co., Ltd.','','public/2013/08/LilyZhu145.png','public/2013/08/LilyZhu145_small.png','朱晓东女士是一位资深酒店管理专家和商业地产&nbsp;运营者,她在中国高星级酒店有长达二十多年的从业经验,因其在旅游与酒店行业的卓越成绩而屡获殊荣。目前为国家级旅游饭店星评员。<br>朱晓东女士具有浙江大学(原杭州大学)经济学学士学位,并获得清华大学高层管理人员工商管理硕士学位。<br>朱晓东女士自2006年加入北京银泰置业有限公司至今,全面负责北京银泰中&nbsp;心的开业筹备和运营管理。作为北京CBD核心地带的高端城市综合体,北京银泰中心包含北京柏悦酒店、柏悦府与柏悦居(公寓)、银泰写字楼以及一座拥有四十余&nbsp;家国际奢侈品牌专卖店的北京银泰中心商场。几年来,朱晓东率其团队成功地将北京银泰中心打造成为长安街上的地标性商业地产项目和高品质现代生活的卓越典范。<br>朱晓东女士还负责银泰集团业务中酒店板块工作,领衔多个城市的酒店项目规划并代表业主与多家国际知名酒店(品牌)管理公司合作开展酒店筹备、开业经营等全程工作。在其领导下,已有北京柏悦酒店、宁波柏悦酒店及上海安达仕酒店三&nbsp;家高星级酒店成功开业。2012&nbsp;年又成功促成中国银泰与希尔顿全球合作,签署成都华尔道夫酒店。另有多家酒店正在筹备。<br>','Ms.&nbsp;Lily&nbsp;Zhu&nbsp;is&nbsp;an&nbsp;expert&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;industry&nbsp;and&nbsp;in&nbsp;high-end&nbsp;property&nbsp;management.&nbsp;Lily&nbsp;has&nbsp;served&nbsp;in&nbsp;China’s&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;business&nbsp;for&nbsp;over&nbsp;twenty&nbsp;years,&nbsp;taking&nbsp;management&nbsp;roles&nbsp;at&nbsp;Diaoyutai&nbsp;State&nbsp;Guesthouse&nbsp;(Beijing),&nbsp;Jingguang&nbsp;Centre&nbsp;(Beijing),&nbsp;Zhejiang&nbsp;World&nbsp;Trade&nbsp;Centre&nbsp;Grand&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;(Hangzhou),&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;Golden&nbsp;Palm&nbsp;(Sanya)&nbsp;and&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;Intime&nbsp;(Sanya).&nbsp;Due&nbsp;to&nbsp;her&nbsp;excellences&nbsp;in&nbsp;career,&nbsp;Lily&nbsp;continuously&nbsp;received&nbsp;awards&nbsp;and&nbsp;honours&nbsp;from&nbsp;both&nbsp;within&nbsp;and&nbsp;out&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;industry.&nbsp;She&nbsp;is&nbsp;now&nbsp;a&nbsp;member&nbsp;of&nbsp;National&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Administration&nbsp;Appraisal&nbsp;Committee&nbsp;of&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Star-rating.<br>Lily&nbsp;holds&nbsp;a&nbsp;BA&nbsp;degree&nbsp;in&nbsp;Economics&nbsp;from&nbsp;Zhejiang&nbsp;University&nbsp;and&nbsp;obtains&nbsp;EMBA&nbsp;degree&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;renowned&nbsp;Tsinghua&nbsp;University.<br>Lily&nbsp;joined&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Yintai&nbsp;Property&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;in&nbsp;2006&nbsp;since&nbsp;when&nbsp;she&nbsp;took&nbsp;her&nbsp;current&nbsp;position,&nbsp;taking&nbsp;full&nbsp;responsibility&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;operation&nbsp;management&nbsp;of&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Yintai&nbsp;Centre.&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Yintai&nbsp;Centre&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;high-end&nbsp;commercial&nbsp;property&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;core&nbsp;area&nbsp;of&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;CBD&nbsp;district.&nbsp;It&nbsp;accommodates&nbsp;Park&nbsp;Hyatt&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;the&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;boutique&nbsp;hotel,&nbsp;Park&nbsp;Hyatt&nbsp;Penthouses&nbsp;and&nbsp;Park&nbsp;Hyatt&nbsp;Residence,&nbsp;Yintai&nbsp;Office&nbsp;Tower&nbsp;and&nbsp;Park&nbsp;Life&nbsp;the&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;retails&nbsp;centre.&nbsp;Lily&nbsp;and&nbsp;her&nbsp;team&nbsp;have&nbsp;made&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Yintai&nbsp;Centre&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;landmark&nbsp;of&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;and&nbsp;along&nbsp;its&nbsp;most&nbsp;prestigious&nbsp;Chang’an&nbsp;Avenue.<br>During&nbsp;the&nbsp;recent&nbsp;years,&nbsp;Lily&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;in&nbsp;charge&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;section&nbsp;of&nbsp;Yintai&nbsp;Group.&nbsp;On&nbsp;behalf&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;owner,&nbsp;she&nbsp;works&nbsp;with&nbsp;several&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;leading&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;(brand)&nbsp;management&nbsp;companies&nbsp;on&nbsp;projects&nbsp;located&nbsp;in&nbsp;several&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;cities,&nbsp;from&nbsp;project&nbsp;design&nbsp;to&nbsp;operation.&nbsp;Under&nbsp;her&nbsp;leadership,&nbsp;three&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;(Park&nbsp;Hyatt&nbsp;Beijing,&nbsp;Park&nbsp;Hyatt&nbsp;Ningbo&nbsp;and&nbsp;Andaz&nbsp;Shanghai)&nbsp;have&nbsp;opened&nbsp;and&nbsp;rapidly&nbsp;achieved&nbsp;market&nbsp;recognition.&nbsp;She&nbsp;brought&nbsp;about&nbsp;the&nbsp;cooperation&nbsp;between&nbsp;Yintai&nbsp;and&nbsp;Hilton&nbsp;Worldwide&nbsp;in&nbsp;2012&nbsp;on&nbsp;Waldorf&nbsp;Astoria&nbsp;Chengdu&nbsp;while&nbsp;several&nbsp;others&nbsp;are&nbsp;currently&nbsp;under&nbsp;preparation.<br>'),(38,15.5,'包铂','Ilja Poepper','市场销售副总裁','Vice President of Global Sales & Marketing','万达酒店及度假村管理集团','Wanda Hotels & Resorts','','public/2013/08/PoepperIlja145.png','public/2013/08/PoepperIlja145_small.png','Ilja&nbsp;Poepper（中文名：包铂）先生，1971年出生于德国，1984-1991年随父母生活于中国。在北京大学学习一年以后，包铂回到德国，在斯图加特史蒂根伯格酒店管理学院学习酒店管理，师从史蒂根伯格•格拉芙•齐柏林。<br>1998年，包铂回到中国，开始自己的酒店事业。曾服务于ZENITH&nbsp;INTERNATIONAL、洲际、豪生等国际著名酒店管理集团。曾任豪生酒店管理集团大中华区运营副总裁。现任万达酒店及度假村管理集团市场销售副总裁。<br>','Mr.&nbsp;Ilja&nbsp;Poepper&nbsp;was&nbsp;born&nbsp;in&nbsp;Germany&nbsp;in&nbsp;1971&nbsp;and&nbsp;grew&nbsp;up&nbsp;with&nbsp;his&nbsp;parents&nbsp;in&nbsp;China&nbsp;from&nbsp;1984&nbsp;–&nbsp;1991.&nbsp;After&nbsp;studying&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;University&nbsp;for&nbsp;one&nbsp;year&nbsp;Poepper&nbsp;went&nbsp;back&nbsp;to&nbsp;Germany&nbsp;to&nbsp;study&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Management&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;Steigenberger&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Management&nbsp;school&nbsp;in&nbsp;Bad&nbsp;Reichall&nbsp;followed&nbsp;by&nbsp;an&nbsp;apprenticeship&nbsp;with&nbsp;Steigenberger&nbsp;Graf&nbsp;Zeppelin&nbsp;in&nbsp;Stuttgart.<br>Mr.&nbsp;Poepper&nbsp;returned&nbsp;back&nbsp;to&nbsp;China&nbsp;in&nbsp;1998&nbsp;and&nbsp;continued&nbsp;his&nbsp;carrier&nbsp;with&nbsp;various&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;groups&nbsp;like&nbsp;Zenith&nbsp;International,&nbsp;IHG&nbsp;and&nbsp;Howard&nbsp;Johnson.&nbsp;Before&nbsp;joining&nbsp;Wanda&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;as&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President&nbsp;for&nbsp;S&M&nbsp;Global&nbsp;Poepper&nbsp;was&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President&nbsp;of&nbsp;Operations&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China&nbsp;for&nbsp;over&nbsp;25&nbsp;operating&nbsp;40&nbsp;pre-opening&nbsp;Howard&nbsp;Johnson&nbsp;and&nbsp;Wyndham&nbsp;Grand&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;Royal&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;stationed&nbsp;in&nbsp;Shanghai.<br>'),(39,22.5,'孙健','Kent Sun','大中华区首席发展官','Chief Development Officer, Greater China','洲际酒店集团','InterContinental Hotels Group','','public/2013/08/KentSun145.png','public/2013/08/KentSun145_small.png','孙健，洲际酒店集团大中华区首席发展官，负责管理洲际酒店集团在大中华区的业务发展。其主要职责包括部署公司开发战略、管理发展计划以及改善经营绩效。他带领团队不断寻求突破开发增长的新途径，并加强了洲际酒店集团的品牌建设。<br>作为酒店行业资深人士，孙健拥有20多年酒店管理与开发经验。他曾历任上海索菲特海仑宾馆副总经理、上海广场长城假日酒店以及武汉晴川假日酒店市场销售总监，并于2004年加入洲际酒店集团大中华区总部。凭借在品牌发展方面的突出表现、建立战略伙伴关系的出色能力以及卓越的领导才能，孙健于2008年被任命为洲际酒店集团大中华区发展副总裁，并于2013年1月荣任大中华区首席发展官。<br>2007年，孙健因对洲际酒店集团在大中华区战略发展的突出贡献，被洲际酒店集团亚太地区授予“年度开拓者”大奖。<br>孙健先生毕业于西安交通大学酒店旅游管理专业，并获得香港大学工商管理硕士学位。<br><br>','Kent&nbsp;Sun,&nbsp;Chief&nbsp;Development&nbsp;Officer&nbsp;of&nbsp;IHG&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China,&nbsp;oversees&nbsp;the&nbsp;development&nbsp;of&nbsp;IHG&nbsp;properties&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;region.&nbsp;He&nbsp;is&nbsp;primarily&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;strategic&nbsp;planning,&nbsp;managing&nbsp;development&nbsp;initiatives&nbsp;and&nbsp;improving&nbsp;performance.&nbsp;He&nbsp;leads&nbsp;the&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China&nbsp;Development&nbsp;Team&nbsp;as&nbsp;it&nbsp;continues&nbsp;to&nbsp;explore&nbsp;new&nbsp;avenues&nbsp;for&nbsp;growth&nbsp;and&nbsp;strengthens&nbsp;IHG’s&nbsp;brands&nbsp;across&nbsp;the&nbsp;region.&nbsp;<br>Kent,&nbsp;a&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;veteran,&nbsp;has&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;20&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;professional&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;industry.&nbsp;His&nbsp;career&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;industry&nbsp;includes&nbsp;serving&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;Deputy&nbsp;General&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;of&nbsp;Sofitel&nbsp;Hyland&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;and&nbsp;as&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;Sales&nbsp;&&nbsp;Marketing&nbsp;for&nbsp;both&nbsp;Holiday&nbsp;Inn&nbsp;Downtown&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;and&nbsp;Holiday&nbsp;Inn&nbsp;Riverside&nbsp;Wuhan,&nbsp;before&nbsp;joining&nbsp;the&nbsp;IHG&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China&nbsp;corporate&nbsp;office&nbsp;in&nbsp;2004.&nbsp;He&nbsp;was&nbsp;appointed&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;President&nbsp;of&nbsp;IHG&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China&nbsp;Development&nbsp;in&nbsp;2008,&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;his&nbsp;excellent&nbsp;brand&nbsp;development&nbsp;performance,&nbsp;ability&nbsp;to&nbsp;develop&nbsp;strategic&nbsp;partnerships&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;his&nbsp;competent&nbsp;leadership&nbsp;skills.&nbsp;In&nbsp;January&nbsp;2013,&nbsp;Kent&nbsp;was&nbsp;promoted&nbsp;to&nbsp;Chief&nbsp;Development&nbsp;Officer,&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China.<br>IHG&nbsp;Asia&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;awarded&nbsp;Kent&nbsp;“Developer&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Year”&nbsp;in&nbsp;2007,&nbsp;for&nbsp;his&nbsp;outstanding&nbsp;contribution&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;company’s&nbsp;strategic&nbsp;growth&nbsp;and&nbsp;development&nbsp;in&nbsp;China.&nbsp;<br>Kent&nbsp;holds&nbsp;a&nbsp;Bachelor’s&nbsp;degree&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;&&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Management&nbsp;from&nbsp;Xi’an&nbsp;Jiaotong&nbsp;University&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;MBA&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;University&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong.<br>'),(40,18.5,'沈钢','Gang Shen','酒店运营部总监','Director, Hotel Operation Dept.','仁恒置地集团有限公司','Yanlord Land Group Limited ','','public/2013/08/ShenGang145.png','public/2013/08/ShenGang145_small.png','新加坡仁恒置地集团酒店运营部总监&nbsp;&nbsp;工商管理博士&nbsp;&nbsp;从事酒店经营管理30年，负责集团酒店发展的定位、合同谈判以及运营管理，先后从事大型商业综合体的酒店定位规划，熟悉国际酒店品牌的合作流程以及业主管理内容。','Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Operations&nbsp;Department&nbsp;of&nbsp;Yanlord&nbsp;Land&nbsp;Group,&nbsp;Doctor&nbsp;Degree&nbsp;holder&nbsp;of&nbsp;Business&nbsp;Administration,&nbsp;has&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;30&nbsp;years&nbsp;rich&nbsp;experience&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management.&nbsp;His&nbsp;current&nbsp;job&nbsp;scope&nbsp;includes&nbsp;the&nbsp;development&nbsp;and&nbsp;positioning&nbsp;for&nbsp;Yanlord&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;properties,&nbsp;management&nbsp;contact&nbsp;negotiations&nbsp;and&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;operations&nbsp;management.&nbsp;Mr&nbsp;Shen&nbsp;also&nbsp;has&nbsp;solid&nbsp;background&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;large&nbsp;retail&nbsp;complex&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;positioning&nbsp;and&nbsp;planning,&nbsp;is&nbsp;also&nbsp;familiar&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;cooperation&nbsp;with&nbsp;international&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;companies&nbsp;and&nbsp;owner&nbsp;management&nbsp;process.'),(41,1.5,'曹丹青','Danqing Cao','酒店专项化团队设计总监','Director of Design, Hotel Division','华东建筑设计研究总院','ECADI','','public/2013/08/CaoDanqing145.png','public/2013/08/CaoDanqing145_small.png','曹丹青女士是华东建筑设计研究总院的酒店专业团队设计总监，她所负责的酒店团队是一个设计与研究并重的专业化设计团队，拥有大量的高级酒店项目的设计经历，包括世博洲际酒店、三亚海棠湾万丽度假酒店、苏州东方之门康拉德酒店、苏州IFC的马克吐温酒店、江阴西城皇冠假日酒店、昆山一醉皇冠会展酒店、鄂尔多斯东胜皇冠假日酒店、三亚凤凰岛超五星级酒店等。曹女士所率领的这个设计团队将设计与研究紧密结合，把握酒店设计的前沿趋势，对酒店各方面的设计核心技术深入研究，这些都对设计和服务的优秀品质提供了保证。','Ms.&nbsp;Cao&nbsp;Danqing&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;Director&nbsp;of&nbsp;Design&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Division&nbsp;with&nbsp;East&nbsp;China&nbsp;Architectural&nbsp;Design&nbsp;&&nbsp;Research&nbsp;Institute&nbsp;(ECADI).&nbsp;She&nbsp;leads&nbsp;the&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Division,&nbsp;a&nbsp;professional&nbsp;design&nbsp;team&nbsp;integrating&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;research,&nbsp;and&nbsp;has&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;experience&nbsp;in&nbsp;premium&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;project&nbsp;design,&nbsp;including&nbsp;InterContinental&nbsp;Expo,&nbsp;Renaissance&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;Haitang&nbsp;Bay,&nbsp;Suzhou&nbsp;Gate&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Orient&nbsp;Conrad&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;Suzhou&nbsp;IFC&nbsp;Mark&nbsp;Twain&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;Jiangyin&nbsp;Xicheng&nbsp;Crowne&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts,&nbsp;Kunshan&nbsp;Yizui&nbsp;Crown&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;Crowne&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;Ordos,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;Phoenix&nbsp;Island&nbsp;Super&nbsp;Five-star&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;etc.&nbsp;The&nbsp;Design&nbsp;Division&nbsp;Ms.&nbsp;Cao&nbsp;leads&nbsp;combines&nbsp;design&nbsp;with&nbsp;research&nbsp;closely,&nbsp;well&nbsp;grasps&nbsp;the&nbsp;frontier&nbsp;trends&nbsp;of&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;conducts&nbsp;in-depth&nbsp;research&nbsp;on&nbsp;core&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;design&nbsp;technologies&nbsp;in&nbsp;various&nbsp;aspects,&nbsp;all&nbsp;of&nbsp;which&nbsp;guarantees&nbsp;the&nbsp;excellent&nbsp;quality&nbsp;of&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;services.');

