insert  into `end_chat_sponsorhotel`(`hotel_id`,`sponsor_id`,`order_id`,`name_cn`,`name_en`,`guide_image`,`description_cn`,`description_en`) values (7,NULL,5.3,'厦门汇广源朗豪酒店','Langham Place Xiamen','public/2013/08/Langham_Xiamen1833.png','厦门朗豪酒店将于2013开业，酒店位于厦门商业枢纽，拥有330间设计时尚的客房及套房，并设有多元化的休闲及会议设施，当中包括位于22楼能俯瞰厦门景色的星愿厅、大型宴会厅及多功能的会议室，可灵活地配合举行不同宴会和会议活动的需要。<br>厦门朗豪酒店将以朗豪品牌的风格为旅客带来乐趣无穷的住宿体验，包括集商务中心及酒吧一身的Portal&nbsp;–&nbsp;Work&nbsp;&&nbsp;Play和让宾客放松及充电的Club&nbsp;L&nbsp;贵宾会。客人除了享用设备完善的健身中心外，亦可于以传统中医学为基础的「川」水疗中心享受一系列特色疗程。酒店亦提供一系列精彩的餐饮选择，在香港荣获米其林二星殊荣的明阁、露天餐饮餐厅，和提供全天候餐饮服务的The&nbsp;Place餐厅。<br>','Featuring&nbsp;330&nbsp;modern&nbsp;guestrooms&nbsp;and&nbsp;stunning&nbsp;suites,&nbsp;Langham&nbsp;Place,&nbsp;Xiamen&nbsp;is&nbsp;nestled&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;heart&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;business&nbsp;hub&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;city.&nbsp;The&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;opened&nbsp;in&nbsp;2013.&nbsp;It&nbsp;will&nbsp;also&nbsp;offer&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;meeting&nbsp;spaces.&nbsp;These&nbsp;include&nbsp;the&nbsp;Star&nbsp;Room&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;22nd&nbsp;floor&nbsp;overlooking&nbsp;the&nbsp;city,&nbsp;a&nbsp;grand&nbsp;ballroom,&nbsp;and&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;flexible&nbsp;meeting&nbsp;facilities&nbsp;with&nbsp;breakout&nbsp;areas.<br>The&nbsp;property&nbsp;will&nbsp;feature&nbsp;Langham&nbsp;Place\'s&nbsp;signature&nbsp;elements&nbsp;include&nbsp;the&nbsp;unique&nbsp;Portal&nbsp;–&nbsp;Work&nbsp;&&nbsp;Play&nbsp;where&nbsp;guests&nbsp;can&nbsp;work&nbsp;and&nbsp;play&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;space&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;Club&nbsp;L&nbsp;lounge&nbsp;with&nbsp;areas&nbsp;to&nbsp;\"Relax,&nbsp;Refuel&nbsp;and&nbsp;Replay\".&nbsp;Guests&nbsp;will&nbsp;also&nbsp;be&nbsp;able&nbsp;to&nbsp;enjoy&nbsp;Chuan&nbsp;Spa&nbsp;with&nbsp;its&nbsp;signature&nbsp;treatments&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;Traditional&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;Medicine&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;state-of-the-art&nbsp;fitness&nbsp;centre&nbsp;as&nbsp;part&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;wellness&nbsp;experience.&nbsp;Dining&nbsp;experiences&nbsp;will&nbsp;include&nbsp;the&nbsp;signature&nbsp;Cantonese&nbsp;Ming&nbsp;Court&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;its&nbsp;two&nbsp;Michelin&nbsp;Star&nbsp;counterpart&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong,&nbsp;outdoor&nbsp;dining&nbsp;and&nbsp;The&nbsp;Place,&nbsp;the&nbsp;group\'s&nbsp;popular&nbsp;all-day&nbsp;dining&nbsp;concept.<br>'),(5,NULL,5.1,'广州南丰朗豪酒店','Langham Place Guangzhou','public/2013/08/Langham_Guangzhow1923.png','广州南丰朗豪酒店将于2013年开业。新酒店是唯一连接亚洲最大的展览空间,举世闻名的中国进出口商品交易会（广交会）举办地广州国际会议展览中心，广州南丰朗豪酒店拥有488间现代时尚的客房和套房，由世界顶尖设计公司Yabu&nbsp;Pushelberg倾力打造。酒店连接地铁站入口，交通便捷，商旅人士可以轻而易举地从酒店来往城市及邻近地区。创新的酒店设计将为各种规模商务会议和活动增添国际化的魅力。酒店会配备最先进的设施及宽敞会议场地，其中一间3,000平方米的大宴会厅，相当于三个奥运会标准泳池的面积。酒店宽敞的露天场地，可作举行优雅或富感官的户外活动。同时，酒店亦是唯一设有冷气专用通道通向会展中心及广交会的酒店。','An&nbsp;iconic&nbsp;architectural&nbsp;gem&nbsp;set&nbsp;to&nbsp;open&nbsp;in&nbsp;2013,&nbsp;Langham&nbsp;Place,&nbsp;Guangzhou&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;the&nbsp;only&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;directly&nbsp;connected&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Guangzhou&nbsp;International&nbsp;Convention&nbsp;and&nbsp;Exhibition&nbsp;Centre,&nbsp;home&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Canton&nbsp;Import&nbsp;and&nbsp;Export&nbsp;Fair&nbsp;and&nbsp;Asia’s&nbsp;largest&nbsp;Exhibition&nbsp;space.<br>With&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel’s&nbsp;strategic&nbsp;location&nbsp;and&nbsp;its&nbsp;direct&nbsp;entrance&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;subway&nbsp;network,&nbsp;key&nbsp;destinations&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;city&nbsp;are&nbsp;within&nbsp;easy&nbsp;reach.&nbsp;Whenever&nbsp;you&nbsp;want,&nbsp;you&nbsp;can&nbsp;also&nbsp;seamlessly&nbsp;access&nbsp;the&nbsp;neighboring&nbsp;world-class&nbsp;exhibition&nbsp;facilities&nbsp;via&nbsp;a&nbsp;private&nbsp;air-conditioned&nbsp;walkway.<br>Within&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel’s&nbsp;cutting-edge&nbsp;designer&nbsp;setting,&nbsp;you&nbsp;will&nbsp;find&nbsp;exceptionally&nbsp;large&nbsp;meeting&nbsp;spaces&nbsp;including&nbsp;the&nbsp;3,000&nbsp;sq&nbsp;m&nbsp;Great&nbsp;Room,&nbsp;which&nbsp;is&nbsp;almost&nbsp;the&nbsp;size&nbsp;of&nbsp;three&nbsp;Olympic&nbsp;swimming&nbsp;pools,&nbsp;and&nbsp;stunning&nbsp;alfresco&nbsp;spaces&nbsp;for&nbsp;chic&nbsp;and&nbsp;sensuous&nbsp;outdoor&nbsp;events<br>'),(6,NULL,5.2,'宁波文化广场朗豪酒店','Langham Place Ningbo Cultural Plaza','public/2013/08/Langham_Ningbo2144.png','座落于宁波文化广场的朗豪酒店拥有140间客房，包括7间套房，由两座别具特色低层塔楼结合而成，并由一条摩登的艺术装饰走廊连接起来。<br>为迎合宁波文化广场的艺术氛围，以及贯彻朗豪品牌对艺术的热切追求，酒店四周皆展示经过精心挑选的当地艺术品，触动宾客的感官，启发无穷的想象空间。<br>宁波文化广场朗豪酒店致力为宾客带来愉悦的感官刺激，除了视觉享受外，&nbsp;酒店亦准备连绵不绝的盛宴，触动宾客的味蕾。琳琅满目的餐饮选择，包括提供广东及本地美馔的明阁，与位于香港并被米芝莲点选的明阁同出一彻，餐厅拥有非凡地位。<br>入住宁波文化广场朗豪酒店，城中所有最好的，只在咫尺之遥。<br>','Surrounded&nbsp;by&nbsp;engaging&nbsp;entertainment,&nbsp;Langham&nbsp;Place&nbsp;guests&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;stimulated&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;artistic&nbsp;vibe,&nbsp;the&nbsp;retail&nbsp;buzz&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;range&nbsp;of&nbsp;fun&nbsp;options.<br>Set&nbsp;within&nbsp;two&nbsp;distinctive&nbsp;low-rise&nbsp;towers&nbsp;and&nbsp;linked&nbsp;by&nbsp;a&nbsp;deco-inspired&nbsp;corridor,&nbsp;Langham&nbsp;Place,&nbsp;Ningbo&nbsp;Culture&nbsp;Plaza,&nbsp;will&nbsp;offer&nbsp;140&nbsp;modern&nbsp;rooms&nbsp;including&nbsp;seven&nbsp;ultra-stylish&nbsp;suites.<br>Reflecting&nbsp;the&nbsp;community’s&nbsp;love&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;arts,&nbsp;Langham&nbsp;Place&nbsp;will&nbsp;stir&nbsp;your&nbsp;senses&nbsp;and&nbsp;spark&nbsp;your&nbsp;imagination&nbsp;with&nbsp;its&nbsp;hotel-wide&nbsp;collection&nbsp;of&nbsp;local&nbsp;artwork.<br>While&nbsp;the&nbsp;art&nbsp;pieces&nbsp;offer&nbsp;food&nbsp;for&nbsp;thought,&nbsp;Langham&nbsp;Place,&nbsp;Ningbo&nbsp;Culture&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;will&nbsp;also&nbsp;provide&nbsp;food&nbsp;for&nbsp;pleasure.&nbsp;The&nbsp;delicious&nbsp;dining&nbsp;options&nbsp;includes&nbsp;Ming&nbsp;Court,&nbsp;a&nbsp;sibling&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Michelin-honored&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;landmark&nbsp;serving&nbsp;Cantonese&nbsp;and&nbsp;local&nbsp;specialties.&nbsp;<br>Stay&nbsp;at&nbsp;Langham&nbsp;Place,&nbsp;Ningbo&nbsp;Culture&nbsp;Plaza,&nbsp;and&nbsp;you’ll&nbsp;discover&nbsp;the&nbsp;city’s&nbsp;best&nbsp;offerings&nbsp;are&nbsp;as&nbsp;close&nbsp;as&nbsp;your&nbsp;doorstep.&nbsp;<br><br>'),(8,NULL,6.1,'西双版纳避寒皇冠假日度假酒店','Crowne Plaza Resort Xishuangbanna','public/2013/08/IHG_Xishuangbanna.png','酒店位于云南省西双版纳热带雨林，是第一家拥有&nbsp;520间客房的五星级国际品牌度假村。<br>&nbsp;受古代傣王宫以及历经周遭傣族文化洗涤的建筑灵感启发，西双版纳避寒皇冠假日度假酒店位于风景如画的景洪市郊。度假酒店拥有独具一格的东南亚风情，您可尽情享受绝妙的地理位置，四季宜人的气候，宽敞舒适的客房和别墅以及户外热带花园景观泳池。<br>&nbsp;酒店的每间客房都拥有超大阳台，可随时欣赏热带花园美景。酒店拥有种类多样的房型和套房，其中包括80平米的豪华大床房，豪华套房，行政豪华房，两套面积达470平米的皇家套房和两栋面积超过1,600平米的总统别墅。皇冠假日行政俱乐部拥有独立的前台接待、户外私人泳池和酒廊，以供客人独享私人空间。<br>&nbsp;酒店拥有6间风格迥异的餐厅和酒吧，休闲健身中心总面积达2,000平米，酒店拥有三间大型宴会厅，会议设施总面积超过5,000平米，各类会议室总共有16间。<br>','Crowne&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;Xishuangbanna,&nbsp;the&nbsp;company’s&nbsp;first&nbsp;Crowne&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;in&nbsp;China.&nbsp;Set&nbsp;among&nbsp;the&nbsp;tropical&nbsp;rainforests&nbsp;of&nbsp;Xishuangbanna,&nbsp;Yunnan&nbsp;Province,&nbsp;straddling&nbsp;the&nbsp;Lancang&nbsp;River&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;border&nbsp;with&nbsp;Myanmar&nbsp;and&nbsp;Laos,&nbsp;the&nbsp;520-room&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;five-star&nbsp;resort&nbsp;in&nbsp;China’s&nbsp;southernmost&nbsp;region,&nbsp;a&nbsp;UNESCO&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;World&nbsp;Biosphere&nbsp;Reserve.&nbsp;<br>Taking&nbsp;the&nbsp;theme&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;Dai&nbsp;Palace&nbsp;and&nbsp;inspired&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;surrounding&nbsp;architecture&nbsp;that&nbsp;is&nbsp;steeped&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;history&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Dai&nbsp;culture,&nbsp;Crowne&nbsp;Plaza&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;Xishuangbanna&nbsp;sits&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;edge&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;picturesque&nbsp;town&nbsp;of&nbsp;Jinghong.&nbsp;The&nbsp;resort&nbsp;has&nbsp;a&nbsp;distinctively&nbsp;Southeast&nbsp;Asian&nbsp;feel&nbsp;in&nbsp;line&nbsp;with&nbsp;its&nbsp;location,&nbsp;year-round&nbsp;great&nbsp;weather&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;spacious&nbsp;rooms,&nbsp;villas&nbsp;and&nbsp;beautifully&nbsp;landscaped&nbsp;outdoor&nbsp;pool.<br>&nbsp;The&nbsp;rooms&nbsp;feature&nbsp;oversize&nbsp;balconies&nbsp;with&nbsp;views&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;resort’s&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;tropical&nbsp;gardens.&nbsp;The&nbsp;resort&nbsp;has&nbsp;six&nbsp;Food&nbsp;and&nbsp;Beverage&nbsp;outlets,&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;huge&nbsp;2,000&nbsp;square&nbsp;meter&nbsp;fitness&nbsp;and&nbsp;leisure&nbsp;centre,&nbsp;and&nbsp;meeting&nbsp;facilities&nbsp;of&nbsp;over&nbsp;5,000&nbsp;square&nbsp;meters&nbsp;in&nbsp;total.<br>'),(9,NULL,6.2,'上海瑞金洲际酒店','InterContinental Shanghai Ruijin','public/2013/08/IHG_Ruijin.png','洲际酒店及度假村集团正式揭幕上海瑞金洲际酒店为其大中华地区首家经典文化遗产酒店。历经了一个世纪的时光更迭，上海瑞金洲际酒店（前上海瑞金宾馆）愈加雍容华美，全新的客房设施尽显国际风范。毗邻淮海路商圈及众多市内著名旅游景点，坐拥上海市中心55000平方米花园绿地，闹中取静的葱郁花园环抱各栋欧式别墅建筑群，恍然世外的美景就在您呼吸吐纳间翩然展开。独家呈现20世纪初黄金时代老上海的雍容华贵，为来自全球各地的尊贵宾客提供原汁原味的旅行文化体验。','InterContinental&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;unveils&nbsp;its&nbsp;first&nbsp;China&nbsp;heritage&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;–&nbsp;the&nbsp;InterContinental&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;Ruijin&nbsp;–&nbsp;located&nbsp;across&nbsp;a&nbsp;100-acre&nbsp;historic&nbsp;garden&nbsp;estate&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;heart&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanghai.&nbsp;Guests&nbsp;from&nbsp;around&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;can&nbsp;now&nbsp;experience&nbsp;an&nbsp;important&nbsp;part&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanghai’s&nbsp;glamorous&nbsp;early&nbsp;20th-century&nbsp;heritage&nbsp;in&nbsp;an&nbsp;exclusive&nbsp;garden&nbsp;setting,&nbsp;while&nbsp;enjoying&nbsp;InterContinental’s&nbsp;world-class&nbsp;‘In&nbsp;the&nbsp;Know’&nbsp;service&nbsp;and&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;amenities.'),(10,NULL,6.3,'港岛英迪格酒店','Hotel Indigo Hong Kong Island','public/2013/08/IHG_Indigo.png','港岛英迪格酒店为香港最多元化的历史邻里之一的湾仔带来一股新的动力。酒店崭新和时尚的设计刻意唤起其丰富的邻里文化环境。通过独特设计和艺术作品，每间客房也会捕捉到邻里历史和文化。在屋顶上，你会发现充满现代气息的Skybar和扣人心弦的无边玻璃底游泳池&nbsp;(预计开放时间为今年十月底)。&nbsp;围绕酒店都是各具特色的商店，市场，餐馆和酒吧。湾仔地铁站也只是举步之遥。你亦可漫步各景点，深深体会充满丰富历史的湾仔。我们的团队将很乐意与您分享他们的邻里故事。<br>地址：香港皇后大道东246号<br>电话：852&nbsp;3926&nbsp;3888<br>www.hotelindigo.com/hongkong<br>','Hotel&nbsp;Indigo&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;Island&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;dynamic&nbsp;addition&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;fabric&nbsp;of&nbsp;Wan&nbsp;Chai,&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong\'s&nbsp;most&nbsp;diverse&nbsp;and&nbsp;historic&nbsp;neighbourhoods.&nbsp;The&nbsp;hotel\'s&nbsp;fresh&nbsp;and&nbsp;stylish&nbsp;design&nbsp;is&nbsp;intriguing,&nbsp;original&nbsp;and&nbsp;deliberately&nbsp;evocative&nbsp;of&nbsp;its&nbsp;culturally&nbsp;rich&nbsp;urban&nbsp;environment.&nbsp;Our&nbsp;individually&nbsp;styled&nbsp;rooms&nbsp;capture&nbsp;the&nbsp;history&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;neighbourhood&nbsp;through&nbsp;its&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;artwork.&nbsp;On&nbsp;the&nbsp;rooftop&nbsp;you&nbsp;will&nbsp;discover&nbsp;our&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;bar,&nbsp;Skybar,&nbsp;and&nbsp;dramatic&nbsp;infinity&nbsp;glass&nbsp;bottomed&nbsp;pool&nbsp;(to&nbsp;be&nbsp;opened&nbsp;in&nbsp;end&nbsp;of&nbsp;October&nbsp;2013).&nbsp;Wan&nbsp;Chai’s&nbsp;shops,&nbsp;markets,&nbsp;restaurants&nbsp;&&nbsp;bars&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;Wan&nbsp;Chai&nbsp;MTR&nbsp;(subway)&nbsp;station&nbsp;are&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel’s&nbsp;doorstep.&nbsp;Our&nbsp;team&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;happy&nbsp;to&nbsp;share&nbsp;their&nbsp;neighbourhood&nbsp;stories&nbsp;with&nbsp;you.&nbsp;<br>Address:&nbsp;246&nbsp;Queen’s&nbsp;Road&nbsp;East,&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong<br>Tel:&nbsp;852&nbsp;3926&nbsp;3888<br>www.hotelindigo.com/hongkong<br>'),(11,NULL,7.1,'北京康莱德酒店','Conrad Beijing','public/2013/08/Hilton_C_BJ.png','北京康莱德酒店位于生机勃勃的朝阳区，仅需步行即可前往中央商务区与使馆区。同时，酒店临近各类高档餐饮、休闲场所与购物中心，包括三里屯、蓝色港湾和新光天地等。天安门广场、紫禁城和天坛等众多热门旅游景点仅需短途驱车即达。289间宽敞的客房与套房，从多数房间都可通过落地玻璃窗观赏到团结湖公园如诗如画的美景。每间现代奢华设计的客房都配备平板电视，Nespresso咖啡机，大理石浴室、加热地板和镜面电视机。<br>众多极具创意、引领时尚的餐厅与酒吧，必将成为酒店宾客和本地人士尽享美食的胜地。其中CHAPTER餐厅可谓是一家“美食图书馆”，独特的餐厅环境仿若一座宏大的欧洲图书馆，身在其中品味创意美食别有一番滋味。&nbsp;餐厅门口的巧克力精品店以巧克力制成的手工装饰，为宾客打造甜蜜惊喜，此外还有款款美味小食供宾客外带享用。陆羽餐厅是以茶圣之名命名的中式餐厅，这里有一面令人叹为观止的两层茶墙，装饰着各式中式茶叶。来宾可以在晚餐前先品茗茶香，清心养性。廿九閣餐厅以高档海鲜、进口牛肉和高品质奶酪为特色，还有众多优质葡萄酒作为佐餐佳品。绯酒吧坐落在大厦裙楼顶层平台上，是北京全新的夜生活热点。户外休闲区、标志性吧台、露天花园及舞池无不让人流连忘返。<br>酒店拥有超过1000平方米先进的会议设施，配合完美无瑕的服务；无论是举办重要的商务会议，还是时尚高雅的社交活动，将为每位客人留下难忘的回忆。<br>','Strategically&nbsp;located&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;vibrant&nbsp;Chaoyang&nb