l&nbsp;development&nbsp;teams&nbsp;around&nbsp;the&nbsp;world.<br>'),(27,NULL,12.1,'首旅集团','Ahn Luh','public/2013/08/Ahn_Luh_1.png','首旅集团董事长段强，安缦度假村创始人、吉合睦联合创始人&nbsp;ADRIAN&nbsp;ZECHA，泰鸿集团创始人、凯风公益基金会理事长<br>段伟红怀有共同的愿景，创建了安麓（北京）酒店管理有限公司，推广中国的奢侈品、生活方式酒店品牌&nbsp;——安麓。<br>安麓是为中国创建的奢侈品、生活方式酒店品牌。<br>安麓酒店体现按照最前沿的国际水准，融合本土特色，物超所值，打造中国名牌，弘扬并且实践中国服务的理念，安麓品牌是有伟大悠久历史传统的中国文化与现代文明融合的载体。<br>安麓酒店有独一无二的选址和独一无二的设计。<br>安麓品牌的个性，是中国人民传统的好客本质与和谐优雅绿色的环境与现代化的完美结合，是中国原生态与城市化的结合，酒店的服务、建筑设计、室内装修装饰等方面都将体现传统与现代并存的理念，都像一个独特的手工艺品，是生活方式的延伸。<br>','Ahn&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;was&nbsp;created&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;vision&nbsp;shared&nbsp;by&nbsp;Chairman&nbsp;Duan&nbsp;Qiang&nbsp;of&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Group,&nbsp;Whitney&nbsp;Duan&nbsp;of&nbsp;Great&nbsp;Ocean&nbsp;Group&nbsp;and&nbsp;Adrian&nbsp;Zecha&nbsp;of&nbsp;GHM&nbsp;Holdings.&nbsp;The&nbsp;partners&nbsp;behind&nbsp;Ahn&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;aspire&nbsp;to&nbsp;create&nbsp;an&nbsp;urban&nbsp;resort&nbsp;brand&nbsp;that&nbsp;epitomizes&nbsp;a&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;China&nbsp;while&nbsp;retaining&nbsp;the&nbsp;meaningful&nbsp;influences&nbsp;of&nbsp;its&nbsp;culture&nbsp;and&nbsp;traditions.<br>Ahn&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;marks&nbsp;the&nbsp;debut&nbsp;of&nbsp;an&nbsp;urban&nbsp;resort&nbsp;brand&nbsp;that&nbsp;epitomizes&nbsp;a&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;China&nbsp;meaningfully&nbsp;influenced&nbsp;by&nbsp;a&nbsp;long&nbsp;history&nbsp;of&nbsp;cultural&nbsp;traditions.<br>The&nbsp;Ahn&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;brand&nbsp;presents&nbsp;the&nbsp;essence&nbsp;of&nbsp;Old&nbsp;World&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;in&nbsp;today’s&nbsp;context&nbsp;of&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;elegance.&nbsp;Ahn&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;reflects&nbsp;–&nbsp;in&nbsp;service,&nbsp;architectural&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;interior&nbsp;décor&nbsp;–&nbsp;how&nbsp;tradition&nbsp;and&nbsp;modernity&nbsp;can&nbsp;intertwine&nbsp;to&nbsp;present&nbsp;an&nbsp;original,&nbsp;urban&nbsp;resort&nbsp;concept.&nbsp;It&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;the&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;brand&nbsp;that&nbsp;today’s&nbsp;contemporary,&nbsp;up-and-coming&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;deem&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;an&nbsp;extension&nbsp;of&nbsp;themselves&nbsp;and&nbsp;their&nbsp;lifestyles.<br>Styled&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;an&nbsp;intimate&nbsp;space&nbsp;where&nbsp;time&nbsp;and&nbsp;tradition&nbsp;are&nbsp;artfully&nbsp;juxtaposed&nbsp;with&nbsp;present-day&nbsp;luxuries,&nbsp;Ahn&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;properties&nbsp;are&nbsp;designed&nbsp;to&nbsp;become&nbsp;new&nbsp;hideaways&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;discerning&nbsp;traveller.<br>'),(28,NULL,12.2,'兰亭安麓','Ahn Luh Lanting','public/2013/08/Ahn_Luh_2.png','“兰亭安麓”是安麓酒店受王羲之创作的《兰亭集序》启发而得名，选址在群峰叠翠，河溪纵横，风景如画的绍兴市会稽山，占地9.2&nbsp;公顷，由古朴典雅、简洁自然的徽派建筑群组成，包括有35栋、99把钥匙的套房别墅，以及融合江浙地方菜特色的高品质中餐厅、全日餐厅、图书馆、小型会议设施、中药房、SPA、太极教练馆等精选设施。<br>兰亭安麓的每一栋建筑都使用了明清两代徽派住宅、家具、雕刻等方面的收藏。<br>2014年下半年开业的兰亭安麓，是安麓品牌第一个投入运营的项目，是拥有安麓灵魂的标志性旗舰店之一，是“走国际化路，创民族品牌”与“中国服务”战略的实践。<br>','Ahn&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;Lanting&nbsp;Named&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;calligraphy&nbsp;work&nbsp;-“Orchid&nbsp;Pavilion&nbsp;Preface”&nbsp;(Lanting&nbsp;Poems),&nbsp;which&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;best&nbsp;running&nbsp;script&nbsp;in&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;history&nbsp;written&nbsp;by&nbsp;Wang&nbsp;Xizhi.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Ahn&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;Lanting&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;a&nbsp;99-key&nbsp;development&nbsp;incorporated&nbsp;into&nbsp;35&nbsp;heritage&nbsp;houses&nbsp;in&nbsp;Shaoxing,&nbsp;30&nbsp;minutes&nbsp;from&nbsp;Hangzhou&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;province&nbsp;of&nbsp;Zhejiang.&nbsp;The&nbsp;hotel’s&nbsp;dining&nbsp;concepts&nbsp;will&nbsp;incorporate&nbsp;authentic&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;elements,&nbsp;as&nbsp;will&nbsp;the&nbsp;library,&nbsp;meeting&nbsp;area,&nbsp;medical&nbsp;hall,&nbsp;spa&nbsp;and&nbsp;wellness&nbsp;centre&nbsp;and&nbsp;tai&nbsp;chi&nbsp;facility.<br>Lanting&nbsp;Ahn&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;opened&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;second&nbsp;half&nbsp;of&nbsp;2014.&nbsp;It&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;Anh&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;come&nbsp;into&nbsp;service&nbsp;and&nbsp;also&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;an&nbsp;iconic&nbsp;property&nbsp;carrying&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;spirit&nbsp;of&nbsp;Anh&nbsp;Luh&nbsp;Brand.&nbsp;<br>'),(29,NULL,13.1,'千岛湖润和建国度假酒店','Runhe Jianguo Hotel','public/2013/08/BTG_Jianguo_1.png','千岛湖，垒石为堰，筑坝成湖，岛如星罗，湖似明镜。驻足湖畔，邂逅郭沫若笔下的“西子三千”，山水迷离，如诗如画，尽享天下第一秀水美誉。<br>回眸处--于山水之间，隐湖岛之中，着天然之色，看神来之笔。润万物之灵气，以缥缈承托奇葩之作，和天地之大美，以生态自然享仙境人间。一切奢华感受，由润和建国开始。一切美妙休闲，由润和建国创造。<br>“仁者乐山，智者乐水\"，山水相谐，静享品质。酒店依山临水，面湖向岛；梦姑公园，相守为邻；湖区码头，咫尺之遥。无论置身客房、落座餐厅，触目所及湖光山色、碧波荡漾。<br>感受中国服务，自在润和建国！千岛湖润和建国度假酒店为宾客朋友提供自然时尚，舒适友好的入住体验，让您感受无微不至的建国关怀！<br>','The&nbsp;Qiandao&nbsp;lake&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;young&nbsp;lake&nbsp;formed&nbsp;in&nbsp;1959&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;result&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;construction&nbsp;of&nbsp;Xin&nbsp;An&nbsp;jiang&nbsp;hydroelectric&nbsp;power&nbsp;station.&nbsp;The&nbsp;famous&nbsp;poet&nbsp;named&nbsp;GuoMoRuo&nbsp;ever&nbsp;described&nbsp;the&nbsp;lake&nbsp;which&nbsp;is&nbsp;verdurous&nbsp;mountains&nbsp;and&nbsp;crystal&nbsp;clear&nbsp;water&nbsp;.&nbsp;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;reputed&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;best&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;world.<br>Looking&nbsp;back—occupying&nbsp;between&nbsp;mountain&nbsp;and&nbsp;lake&nbsp;,&nbsp;enjoying&nbsp;exotic&nbsp;and&nbsp;misty&nbsp;view,&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;beautiful&nbsp;scenery&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;fresh&nbsp;air&nbsp;that&nbsp;will&nbsp;bring&nbsp;you&nbsp;a&nbsp;completely&nbsp;different&nbsp;experience&nbsp;.&nbsp;All&nbsp;enjoy&nbsp;luxuriously&nbsp;start&nbsp;from&nbsp;here&nbsp;,&nbsp;all&nbsp;wonderful&nbsp;leisure&nbsp;create&nbsp;from&nbsp;here.<br>As&nbsp;the&nbsp;generous&nbsp;love&nbsp;the&nbsp;mountains&nbsp;while&nbsp;the&nbsp;wise&nbsp;love&nbsp;the&nbsp;waters.&nbsp;Peacefully&nbsp;enjoy&nbsp;the&nbsp;beautiful&nbsp;scene&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;mountains&nbsp;and&nbsp;waters&nbsp;which&nbsp;stands&nbsp;together.&nbsp;The&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;is&nbsp;sited&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;riverside&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;mountain,&nbsp;facing&nbsp;the&nbsp;islands&nbsp;and&nbsp;lake&nbsp;and&nbsp;adjacent&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Menggu&nbsp;park，near&nbsp;the&nbsp;lake&nbsp;scenic&nbsp;zone&nbsp;wharf.&nbsp;Whether&nbsp;stay&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;room&nbsp;or&nbsp;restaurant&nbsp;,&nbsp;the&nbsp;lake&nbsp;view&nbsp;is&nbsp;full&nbsp;of&nbsp;your&nbsp;eyes.<br>Enjoy&nbsp;the&nbsp;China\'s&nbsp;service&nbsp;at&nbsp;Runhe&nbsp;Jianguo&nbsp;Hotel!&nbsp;We&nbsp;promise&nbsp;to&nbsp;&nbsp;offer&nbsp;&nbsp;natural,&nbsp;fashionable,&nbsp;comfortable&nbsp;and&nbsp;amicable&nbsp;experience&nbsp;of&nbsp;stay，we&nbsp;would&nbsp;be&nbsp;always&nbsp;ready&nbsp;to&nbsp;offer&nbsp;you&nbsp;attentive&nbsp;China\'s&nbsp;service&nbsp;and&nbsp;make&nbsp;you&nbsp;feel&nbsp;meticulous&nbsp;care&nbsp;of&nbsp;JianGuo&nbsp;hotel.<br>'),(30,NULL,13.2,'北京建国饭店','The Jianguo Hotel Beijing','public/2013/08/BTG_Jianguo_28200.png','北京建国饭店建立于1982年，是中国第一家合资酒店，也是北京CBD唯一的花园式酒店&nbsp;－&nbsp;您的绿色家园。室内设计融合传统与现代典雅风格，提供各项舒适周全的待客设施，亭园水榭，绿树成荫。<br>北京建国饭店的452套客房，全部采用低楼层设计，令每一位宾客都能充分享受绿色与阳光。<br>北京建国饭店荟萃了中西美食,&nbsp;宾客可随自己口味尽享合心意的佳肴。杰斯汀法餐厅久负盛名；咖啡厅可供您短叙闲谈；当然您更可在商宫-天下一品中餐厅里品尝御膳官府菜；在饭店的大堂内，会有乐队现场演奏经典名曲和醉人乐韵，令人心弛神往；您也可以亲临查理酒吧，在悠扬的乐曲声中与友伴一叙衷情。<br>北京建国饭店在这一方面久负盛名，会议设施也一应俱全，大部分场地均可灵活调配，以供举行各式宴会，酒会，发布会或者演讲会等，并可代为安排一切会议器材。并根据活动规模满足不同客户需求。训练有素的服务人员以您的所需为己任全程照顾每个细节,使您亲身感受轻松怡然的成功与喜悦。<br>','The&nbsp;Jianguo&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;joint-venture&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;in&nbsp;China&nbsp;since&nbsp;1982&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;only&nbsp;garden&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;in&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;CBD&nbsp;–&nbsp;Your&nbsp;Green&nbsp;Home.&nbsp;The&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;combines&nbsp;elegant&nbsp;traditional&nbsp;interiors&nbsp;with&nbsp;every&nbsp;modern&nbsp;guest&nbsp;amenities.&nbsp;Luxuriant&nbsp;water&nbsp;gardens&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;courtyard&nbsp;highlight&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel\'s&nbsp;low-rise&nbsp;setting.<br>Although&nbsp;located&nbsp;among&nbsp;Beijing’s&nbsp;most&nbsp;expensive&nbsp;real&nbsp;estate,&nbsp;the&nbsp;four&nbsp;hundred&nbsp;and&nbsp;fifty&nbsp;two&nbsp;guest&nbsp;rooms&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Jianguo&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;are&nbsp;designed&nbsp;in&nbsp;a&nbsp;low&nbsp;floor&nbsp;style,&nbsp;assuring&nbsp;that&nbsp;each&nbsp;of&nbsp;our&nbsp;guests&nbsp;enjoys&nbsp;the&nbsp;nature&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;sunshine&nbsp;of&nbsp;our&nbsp;garden&nbsp;to&nbsp;its&nbsp;fullest.<br>The&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;offers&nbsp;a&nbsp;wide&nbsp;variety&nbsp;of&nbsp;delicious&nbsp;international&nbsp;cuisines-the&nbsp;convenience&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;coffee&nbsp;shop&nbsp;menu&nbsp;in&nbsp;The&nbsp;Cafe,&nbsp;French&nbsp;fine&nbsp;dining&nbsp;in&nbsp;Justine\'s&nbsp;or&nbsp;Imperial&nbsp;food&nbsp;in&nbsp;Shang&nbsp;Court.&nbsp;Traditional&nbsp;or&nbsp;classical&nbsp;music&nbsp;is&nbsp;played&nbsp;live&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;Lobby&nbsp;Lounge,&nbsp;or&nbsp;for&nbsp;a&nbsp;more&nbsp;lively&nbsp;accompaniment&nbsp;in&nbsp;conversation&nbsp;with&nbsp;your&nbsp;friends&nbsp;in&nbsp;Charlie’s&nbsp;Bar.<br>We&nbsp;offer&nbsp;a&nbsp;wide&nbsp;variety&nbsp;of&nbsp;menu&nbsp;options&nbsp;including&nbsp;the&nbsp;banquet,&nbsp;cocktail&nbsp;reception,&nbsp;party,&nbsp;entertainment&nbsp;and&nbsp;meeting&nbsp;to&nbsp;suit&nbsp;your&nbsp;needs&nbsp;and&nbsp;budgetary&nbsp;requirements&nbsp;or&nbsp;all&nbsp;the&nbsp;important&nbsp;Wedding&nbsp;Banquet.&nbsp;Our&nbsp;banquet&nbsp;experts&nbsp;will&nbsp;instead&nbsp;you&nbsp;to&nbsp;focus&nbsp;on&nbsp;each&nbsp;details&nbsp;all&nbsp;through,&nbsp;and&nbsp;only&nbsp;left&nbsp;you&nbsp;the&nbsp;comfort,&nbsp;the&nbsp;success&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;happiness.<br>'),(31,NULL,14.1,'深圳瑞吉酒店','St. Regis Hotel Shenzhen','public/2013/08/CCD_Ruiji_Shenzhen.png','深圳瑞吉酒店位于深圳新地标京基国际金融中心顶部，酒店空中大堂设于建筑第96层，402米高空之上，可俯瞰深圳的壮观美景；酒店共有5个设计独具品味且优雅奢华的特色餐饮及酒吧。作为全球最高的瑞吉酒店，以“光”创造出独一无二的瑞吉品牌的贵族体验，整栋大厦的玻璃幕墙将建筑、艺术、环保有机结合，随着天然光线的变幻，酒店从不同角度呈现出流光溢彩班的动态之美，室内设计延续了这一风格，以炫灿夺目的钻石作为主要元素，与裸露的钢结构和瑰丽的装饰交相辉映，勾勒出一个光线的时间，配上这灵动迷离的光之秀，演绎出一场现实与梦想的穿越之旅。','The&nbsp;St.&nbsp;Regis&nbsp;Shenzhen&nbsp;is&nbsp;located&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;top&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shenzhen&nbsp;Kingkey&nbsp;International&nbsp;Financial&nbsp;Center,&nbsp;the&nbsp;new&nbsp;landmark&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shenzhen.&nbsp;The&nbsp;sky&nbsp;lobby&nbsp;is&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;96th&nbsp;floor,&nbsp;at&nbsp;an&nbsp;altitude&nbsp;of&nbsp;402&nbsp;meters,&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;spectacular&nbsp;view&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shenzhen.&nbsp;There&nbsp;are&nbsp;five&nbsp;specialty&nbsp;restaurants&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel,&nbsp;which&nbsp;uses&nbsp;\"light\"&nbsp;to&nbsp;create&nbsp;a&nbsp;unique&nbsp;and&nbsp;elegant&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;style.&nbsp;As&nbsp;the&nbsp;highest&nbsp;lobby&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;world,&nbsp;the&nbsp;St.&nbsp;Regis&nbsp;offers&nbsp;nobility&nbsp;experiences.&nbsp;The&nbsp;entire&nbsp;building\'s&nbsp;glass&nbsp;curtain&nbsp;wall&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;good&nbsp;combination&nbsp;of&nbsp;construction,&nbsp;art&nbsp;and&nbsp;environment&nbsp;protection.&nbsp;Along&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;natural&nbsp;light&nbsp;changes,&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;presents&nbsp;from&nbsp;different&nbsp;angles&nbsp;the&nbsp;dynamic&nbsp;beauty.&nbsp;The&nbsp;interior&nbsp;design&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;continuation&nbsp;of&nbsp;this&nbsp;style,&nbsp;with&nbsp;dazzling&nbsp;diamonds&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;main&nbsp;element,&nbsp;against&nbsp;exposed&nbsp;steel&nbsp;structure&nbsp;and&nbsp;magnificent&nbsp;decorative&nbsp;pavilions.&nbsp;It&nbsp;sketches&nbsp;out&nbsp;a&nbsp;splendid&nbsp;light&nbsp;show&nbsp;through&nbsp;the&nbsp;light&nbsp;changes,&nbsp;picturing&nbsp;reality&nbsp;and&nbsp;dream.'),(32,NULL,14.2,'丽江铂尔曼酒店','Pullman Lijiang Resort and SPA','public/2013/08/CCD_Pullman_Lijiang.png','丽江铂尔曼酒店紧靠束河古镇，将连绵的玉龙雪山美景尽收眼底，CCD的设计灵感源自云南纳西族的传统建筑，以灰色为主调的设计同时融入了现代的中式元素打造出一种古老与时尚的对立统一，是前卫与传统的完美结合，室内设计沿袭了建筑本身的纳西民族风格，中式灯具，东巴文化装饰等精致的丽江工艺品和纳西风格的家具装饰，让空间中渗透出一种独特的纳西风情。CCD凭借此酒店荣获了有室内设计奥斯卡之称的金钥匙奖，以及IIDA，HD，香港透视等共计6个奖项。在整体设计上沿袭了酒店建筑的现代中式风格，以淡雅的灰色调迎合玉龙雪山个角度景观。低层设计的同时融入了现代中式装饰元素，大小花园水流环绕，中心湖更是汇聚了酒店的诗画美景精华。室内的部份则将丽江淳朴的风情，纳西民族的神秘渗透于当代线条艺术及简约的空间之中，每一件摆设，每一处装饰都源自当地古老的纳西文化，彰显了扎根于当地艺术的设计理念。','PULLMAN&nbsp;LIJIANG&nbsp;RESORT&nbsp;located&nbsp;adjacent&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Shuhe&nbsp;Ancient&nbsp;Town,&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;superb&nbsp;panorama&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Jade&nbsp;Dragon&nbsp;Snow&nbsp;Mountain&nbsp;view.&nbsp;Inspired&nbsp;by&nbsp;Naxi&nbsp;&nbsp;traditional&nbsp;buildings,&nbsp;a&nbsp;gray&nbsp;tone&nbsp;design&nbsp;incorporating&nbsp;modern&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;elements&nbsp;to&nbsp;create&nbsp;a&nbsp;unity&nbsp;of&nbsp;opposites&nbsp;in&nbsp;an&nbsp;ancient&nbsp;fashion,&nbsp;avant-garde&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;combination&nbsp;of&nbsp;interior&nbsp;design&nbsp;follows&nbsp;the&nbsp;Naxi&nbsp;ethnic&nbsp;style&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;building,&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;lamps,&nbsp;Dongba&nbsp;culture&nbsp;decorative&nbsp;Lijiang&nbsp;fine&nbsp;crafts&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;Naxi&nbsp;style&nbsp;furniture,&nbsp;&nbsp;space&nbsp;to&nbsp;infiltrate&nbsp;a&nbsp;unique&nbsp;Naxi&nbsp;style.&nbsp;CCD&nbsp;won&nbsp;Golden&nbsp;Key&nbsp;Award,&nbsp;IIDA,&nbsp;HD&nbsp;and&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;perspective&nbsp;magazine,&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;total&nbsp;of&nbsp;six&nbsp;awards.&nbsp;Following&nbsp;the&nbsp;overall&nbsp;design&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;building&nbsp;with&nbsp;modern&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;style,&nbsp;elegant&nbsp;gray&nbsp;tone&nbsp;caters&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Jade&nbsp;Dragon&nbsp;Snow&nbsp;Mountain&nbsp;landscape.&nbsp;The&nbsp;lower&nbsp;level&nbsp;design&nbsp;incorporating&nbsp;a&nbsp;modern&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;decorative&nbsp;element,&nbsp;the&nbsp;size&nbsp;of&nbsp;garden&nbsp;water&nbsp;surround&nbsp;the&nbsp;central&nbsp;lake&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;brings&nbsp;together&nbsp;the&nbsp;poetry&nbsp;and&nbsp;beauty&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;essence.&nbsp;Simplicity&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;style&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;indoor&nbsp;part&nbsp;will&nbsp;Lijiang&nbsp;Naxi&nbsp;mysterious&nbsp;penetration&nbsp;into&nbsp;the&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;line&nbsp;art&nbsp;and&nbsp;minimalist&nbsp;space,&nbsp;every&nbsp;display,&nbsp;every&nbsp;decoration&nbsp;is&nbsp;from&nbsp;local&nbsp;ancient&nbsp;Naxi&nbsp;culture,&nbsp;local&nbsp;Art\'s&nbsp;design&nbsp;philosophy.'),(33,NULL,16.1,'三亚亚龙湾瑞吉度假酒店','The St. Regis Sanya Yalong Bay Resort','public/2013/08/COFCO_Yalongwan.png','三亚亚龙湾瑞吉度假酒店位于海南岛亚龙湾的绝佳位置，独享蜿蜒800米的至美海岸。不论是商界精英聚会还是情侣浪漫之游，亦或是家庭温馨度假，三亚亚龙湾瑞吉度假酒店在海南为宾客提供独特、精湛的服务，满足多样化的需求。酒店设计精妙、奢华，共有包括28栋海边别墅的401间客房和套房、3间全服务餐厅、1间酒窖并提供法式套餐和1间大堂吧，为全球和本地独具品味的宾客提供完美奢华体验。此外，三亚亚龙湾瑞吉度假酒店也将是三亚唯一为所有宾客提供招牌瑞吉管家服务的度假酒店，并且酒店也率先引进中国南部首家铱瑞水疗中心。','The&nbsp;St.&nbsp;Regis&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;Yalong&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;is&nbsp;ideally&nbsp;situated&nbsp;on&nbsp;a&nbsp;generous&nbsp;stretch&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;coveted&nbsp;location&nbsp;on&nbsp;Yalong&nbsp;Bay,&nbsp;with&nbsp;exclusive&nbsp;access&nbsp;to&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;800&nbsp;meters&nbsp;of&nbsp;pristine&nbsp;coastline.&nbsp;A&nbsp;resort&nbsp;unlike&nbsp;any&nbsp;other&nbsp;on&nbsp;Hainan,&nbsp;the&nbsp;St.&nbsp;Regis&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;Yalong&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;offers&nbsp;wide&nbsp;appeal&nbsp;across&nbsp;a&nbsp;variety&nbsp;of&nbsp;audiences,&nbsp;from&nbsp;business&nbsp;executives&nbsp;to&nbsp;couples&nbsp;seeking&nbsp;romance&nbsp;to&nbsp;families&nbsp;seeking&nbsp;a&nbsp;fun&nbsp;and&nbsp;relaxing&nbsp;vacation.&nbsp;The&nbsp;resort&nbsp;is&nbsp;exquisitely&nbsp;designed&nbsp;with&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;in&nbsp;mind,&nbsp;offering&nbsp;401&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;guest&nbsp;rooms&nbsp;including&nbsp;28&nbsp;beachside&nbsp;villas.&nbsp;&nbsp;The&nbsp;St.&nbsp;Regis&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;Yalong&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;offers&nbsp;a&nbsp;world&nbsp;of&nbsp;epicurean&nbsp;experiences,&nbsp;with&nbsp;three&nbsp;full-service&nbsp;restaurants,&nbsp;a&nbsp;wine&nbsp;cellar&nbsp;with&nbsp;French&nbsp;set&nbsp;menu,&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;lobby&nbsp;lounge.&nbsp;&nbsp;In&nbsp;addition,&nbsp;the&nbsp;St.&nbsp;Regis&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;Yalong&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;the&nbsp;only&nbsp;resort&nbsp;in&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;that&nbsp;offers&nbsp;the&nbsp;signature&nbsp;St.&nbsp;Regis&nbsp;butler&nbsp;service&nbsp;to&nbsp;all&nbsp;guests,&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;South&nbsp;China’s&nbsp;first&nbsp;Iridium&nbsp;Spa.'),(34,NULL,16.2,'三亚美高梅度假酒店','MGM Grand Sanya','public/2013/08/COFCO_MGG.png','三亚美高梅度假酒店位于享有“天下第一湾”美称的国际热带海滨风景旅游区的海南三亚亚龙湾，规划面积达10.8万平方米，提供675间创意设计客房，包括596间风格迥异舒适客房、73间豪华套房及6座至尊海滩别墅，壮阔海景尽收眼底，12间风格迥异的餐饮娱乐场及4,000多平米顶级会议空间等设施，满足度假的一切奢求。三亚美高梅秉承了“挑战活力、感受心跳、纵情娱乐”的品牌精髓，精选热辣惊艳的拉斯维加斯美高梅酒店的娱乐、餐饮和夜生活特色，传承钓鱼台卓尔不凡的经营理念与精益求精的恭殷服务，重新定义奢华度假旅游模式，开启一段非同凡响的海滩度假之旅。','MGM&nbsp;Grand&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;celebrated&nbsp;tropical&nbsp;waterfront&nbsp;scenic&nbsp;area&nbsp;located&nbsp;at&nbsp;Yalong&nbsp;Bay,&nbsp;Sanya,&nbsp;Hainan&nbsp;Province,&nbsp;which&nbsp;owns&nbsp;the&nbsp;reputation&nbsp;of&nbsp;“the&nbsp;most&nbsp;beautiful&nbsp;bay&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;world”.&nbsp;The&nbsp;property&nbsp;area&nbsp;covers&nbsp;108,000&nbsp;square&nbsp;meters&nbsp;with&nbsp;675&nbsp;guest&nbsp;rooms&nbsp;in&nbsp;total,&nbsp;inclusive&nbsp;of&nbsp;596&nbsp;Standard&nbsp;rooms,&nbsp;73&nbsp;suites&nbsp;and&nbsp;6&nbsp;exclusive&nbsp;villas&nbsp;on&nbsp;beachfront&nbsp;offer.&nbsp;The&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;offers&nbsp;incomparable&nbsp;resort&nbsp;destination&nbsp;experience&nbsp;featuring&nbsp;world-class&nbsp;amenities&nbsp;including&nbsp;7&nbsp;F&B&nbsp;outlets,&nbsp;over&nbsp;4,000&nbsp;square&nbsp;meters&nbsp;of&nbsp;technologically&nbsp;advanced&nbsp;flexible&nbsp;meeting&nbsp;space&nbsp;and&nbsp;4&nbsp;high-end&nbsp;retail&nbsp;shops.&nbsp;MGM&nbsp;Grand&nbsp;Sanya&nbsp;is&nbsp;inspired&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;dining,&nbsp;nightlife&nbsp;and&nbsp;entertainment&nbsp;elements&nbsp;from&nbsp;MGM&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;International’s&nbsp;successful&nbsp;brands&nbsp;in&nbsp;Las&nbsp;Vegas&nbsp;combined&nbsp;with&nbsp;Diaoyutai&nbsp;State&nbsp;Guesthouse’s&nbsp;outstanding&nbsp;service&nbsp;philosophy.'),(35,NULL,18.1,'华东建筑设计研究总院','East China Architectural Design & Research Institute','public/2013/08/ECADI_1.png','华东建筑设计研究总院——丰富的酒店设计经验<br>华东建筑设计研究总院（英文简称：ECADI）系中国最具影响力的建筑设计机构之一，设计项目遍布全国31个省份。ECADI为全球著名酒店管理集团的四十余个酒店品牌提供了高品质的设计服务，原创