E）始建于1962年，至今已经有50年的历史，是世界三大酒店管理名校之一。格里昂是美国劳瑞德国际大学联盟的一员，该网络由全球29个国家，超过60所受认可的大学和高等教育机构组成，至今服务了超过740,000多名学生。<br>1996年，格里昂受邀担任中国酒店与旅游业的发展顾问。2005年，格里昂获得美国权威性学术认证机构新英格兰院校协会（NEASC）及其下属高等教育机构委员会（CIHE,&nbsp;Commission&nbsp;on&nbsp;Institutions&nbsp;of&nbsp;Higher&nbsp;Education）认证，并成为NEASC的会员，表明格里昂具备优秀大学办学资格。目前为止，受NEASC最高等级（CIHE）认证的瑞士学校仅三间，除了格里昂外，还有洛桑酒店管理学院（Ecole&nbsp;hoteliere&nbsp;de&nbsp;Lausanne），以及瑞士理诺士国际酒店管理学院（Les&nbsp;Roches&nbsp;International&nbsp;School&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Management）<br>格里昂在全球酒店行业享有盛誉，多年来其毕业生在世界各地的酒店里身居要职，如Mr.&nbsp;Marcello&nbsp;Pigozzo，洲际酒店集团的前任亚太主席；Mr.&nbsp;Jaume&nbsp;Tapies，罗莱夏朵酒店集团的董事长；Mr.&nbsp;Marc&nbsp;Steinmeyer，雅高集团东南亚主席等，并组成了一个会员遍布100多个国家的格里昂校友会。','Fifty&nbsp;years&nbsp;ago,&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;Spring&nbsp;of&nbsp;1962,&nbsp;Glion&nbsp;Institute&nbsp;of&nbsp;Higher&nbsp;Education&nbsp;was&nbsp;born&nbsp;and&nbsp;now&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;ranked&nbsp;number&nbsp;2&nbsp;among&nbsp;all&nbsp;international&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;management&nbsp;schools&nbsp;for&nbsp;an&nbsp;international&nbsp;career.&nbsp;Glion&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;member&nbsp;of&nbsp;Laureate&nbsp;International&nbsp;Universities,&nbsp;a&nbsp;global&nbsp;network&nbsp;of&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;60&nbsp;accredited&nbsp;campus-based&nbsp;and&nbsp;online&nbsp;institutions&nbsp;of&nbsp;higher&nbsp;education&nbsp;serving&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;740,000&nbsp;students&nbsp;in&nbsp;29&nbsp;countries.<br><br>During&nbsp;50&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;excellence,&nbsp;Glion&nbsp;has&nbsp;gained&nbsp;a&nbsp;lot&nbsp;of&nbsp;awards&nbsp;and&nbsp;recognition.&nbsp;In&nbsp;1996,&nbsp;Glion&nbsp;was&nbsp;assigned&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;the&nbsp;development&nbsp;consultant&nbsp;of&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;and&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Industry&nbsp;by&nbsp;China&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Association.&nbsp;In&nbsp;2005,&nbsp;Glion&nbsp;was&nbsp;accredited&nbsp;at&nbsp;university&nbsp;level&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;New&nbsp;England&nbsp;Association&nbsp;of&nbsp;Schools&nbsp;and&nbsp;Colleges,&nbsp;Inc.&nbsp;(NEASC)&nbsp;through&nbsp;its&nbsp;Commission&nbsp;on&nbsp;Institutions&nbsp;of&nbsp;Higher&nbsp;Education&nbsp;(CIHE),&nbsp;with&nbsp;other&nbsp;two&nbsp;Swiss&nbsp;Hospitality&nbsp;Education&nbsp;school,&nbsp;Ecole&nbsp;hoteliere&nbsp;de&nbsp;Lausanne&nbsp;and&nbsp;Les&nbsp;Roches&nbsp;International&nbsp;School&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Management.&nbsp;Accreditation&nbsp;by&nbsp;NEASC&nbsp;indicates&nbsp;that&nbsp;Glion&nbsp;meets&nbsp;or&nbsp;exceeds&nbsp;the&nbsp;standards&nbsp;for&nbsp;institutional&nbsp;quality&nbsp;assurance.<br><br>Over&nbsp;the&nbsp;years,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Alumni&nbsp;have&nbsp;grown&nbsp;in&nbsp;number&nbsp;filling&nbsp;top&nbsp;management&nbsp;positions&nbsp;and&nbsp;raising&nbsp;the&nbsp;level&nbsp;of&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;management&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;profession.&nbsp;Their&nbsp;professionalism&nbsp;has&nbsp;built&nbsp;Glion’s&nbsp;reputation&nbsp;as&nbsp;an&nbsp;institute&nbsp;that&nbsp;grows&nbsp;strong&nbsp;leadership&nbsp;talent&nbsp;as&nbsp;it&nbsp;maintains&nbsp;a&nbsp;close&nbsp;relationship&nbsp;with&nbsp;industry&nbsp;partners,&nbsp;alumni&nbsp;and&nbsp;students,&nbsp;for&nbsp;decades&nbsp;on&nbsp;end.&nbsp;For&nbsp;example,&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Marcello&nbsp;Pigozzo,&nbsp;former&nbsp;Asian-pacific&nbsp;president,&nbsp;InterContinental&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;Group;&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Jaume&nbsp;Tapies,&nbsp;Chairman,&nbsp;Relais&nbsp;&&nbsp;Ch&nbsp;teaux;&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Marc&nbsp;Steinmeyer,&nbsp;Chairman&nbsp;of&nbsp;Southeast&nbsp;Asian,&nbsp;Accord&nbsp;Group.&nbsp;Besides,&nbsp;Glion&nbsp;Alumni&nbsp;Association&nbsp;(AAG)&nbsp;was&nbsp;created&nbsp;in&nbsp;1964&nbsp;and&nbsp;its&nbsp;network&nbsp;spans&nbsp;widely&nbsp;across&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;100&nbsp;countries&nbsp;offering&nbsp;wide&nbsp;social&nbsp;and&nbsp;professional&nbsp;relationships\'&nbsp;opportunities.<br>'),(38,NULL,19.2,'格里昂伦敦校区','Glion London Campus','public/2013/08/Glion_2.png','世界排名前三的酒店管理学校——格里昂高等教育管理学院，于2013年正式宣布在英国开设新的伦敦校区，意味着英国的学生和行业领导者将有机会体验格里昂优质的瑞士酒店管理教育。<br>伦敦融合了旅游、节事以及酒店管理的传统与现代趋势。她拥有悠久的酒店文化，以浓厚的英伦风格著称，其酒店业兴起于维多利亚时代，涌现了许多大型奢华酒店，如克莱瑞奇（Claridges），甘蓝（Savoy）,&nbsp;多尔切斯特（Dorchester）&nbsp;和利思卡尔顿（Ritz）等。除了秉承传统外，伦敦也拥有充满创新意念的新餐馆和酒店。前卫的酒店设计，独特的客户体验，完美的奢华感受，令人耳目一新。<br>格里昂伦敦校区具备两大优势：绝佳的地理位置——位于欧洲商业中心的伦敦；顶级的师资队伍——由世界排名前三的酒店管理学校格里昂的教授学者组成。增设伦敦校区使学生能在瑞士和美国校区以外更广阔的国际化校园内学习酒店管理，体现了酒店管理教育全球化的新趋势。<br>','Glion&nbsp;Institute&nbsp;of&nbsp;Higher&nbsp;Education,&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;world’s&nbsp;top&nbsp;three&nbsp;institutions&nbsp;of&nbsp;higher&nbsp;education&nbsp;for&nbsp;an&nbsp;international&nbsp;career&nbsp;in&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;management,&nbsp;announced&nbsp;officially&nbsp;that&nbsp;it&nbsp;is&nbsp;opening&nbsp;its&nbsp;first&nbsp;branch&nbsp;campus&nbsp;in&nbsp;London&nbsp;n&nbsp;2013.&nbsp;The&nbsp;new&nbsp;campus&nbsp;expands&nbsp;the&nbsp;reach&nbsp;of&nbsp;Glion’s&nbsp;Swiss&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;education&nbsp;programmes&nbsp;to&nbsp;students&nbsp;and&nbsp;industry&nbsp;leaders&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;U.K.&nbsp;<br>London&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;great&nbsp;city&nbsp;to&nbsp;learn&nbsp;about&nbsp;the&nbsp;traditions&nbsp;and&nbsp;new&nbsp;trends&nbsp;in&nbsp;tourism,&nbsp;events&nbsp;and&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;management.&nbsp;Being&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;visited&nbsp;cities&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;world,&nbsp;London&nbsp;has&nbsp;a&nbsp;rich&nbsp;history&nbsp;of&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;culture&nbsp;and&nbsp;British&nbsp;traditions.&nbsp;The&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;industry&nbsp;grew&nbsp;in&nbsp;London&nbsp;during&nbsp;the&nbsp;Victorian&nbsp;period&nbsp;when&nbsp;many&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;large,&nbsp;luxurious&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;were&nbsp;built,&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;Claridges,&nbsp;The&nbsp;Savoy,&nbsp;The&nbsp;Dorchester&nbsp;and&nbsp;The&nbsp;Ritz.&nbsp;In&nbsp;addition&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;traditional&nbsp;side,&nbsp;London&nbsp;offers&nbsp;a&nbsp;wide&nbsp;range&nbsp;of&nbsp;innovative&nbsp;new&nbsp;restaurants&nbsp;and&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;that&nbsp;are&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;cutting-edge&nbsp;of&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;design,&nbsp;unique&nbsp;guest&nbsp;experiences,&nbsp;and&nbsp;refined&nbsp;luxury.&nbsp;<br>The&nbsp;new&nbsp;Glion&nbsp;London&nbsp;campus&nbsp;offers&nbsp;the&nbsp;best&nbsp;of&nbsp;two&nbsp;worlds:&nbsp;an&nbsp;opportunity&nbsp;to&nbsp;study&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;management&nbsp;in&nbsp;London,&nbsp;Europe’s&nbsp;business&nbsp;hub,&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;Swiss&nbsp;expertise&nbsp;of&nbsp;Glion,&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;world’s&nbsp;top-ranking&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;management&nbsp;institutes.&nbsp;The&nbsp;expansion&nbsp;of&nbsp;Glion&nbsp;to&nbsp;London&nbsp;allows&nbsp;students&nbsp;worldwide&nbsp;to&nbsp;define&nbsp;their&nbsp;own&nbsp;pathway&nbsp;for&nbsp;earning&nbsp;a&nbsp;Swiss&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;management&nbsp;degree&nbsp;through&nbsp;study&nbsp;at&nbsp;campus&nbsp;locations&nbsp;in&nbsp;Switzerland,&nbsp;the&nbsp;United&nbsp;States&nbsp;or&nbsp;the&nbsp;U.K.<br>'),(39,NULL,20.1,'港中旅酒店有限公司','HK CTS Hotels Co., Ltd','public/2013/08/HK_CTS.png','港中旅酒店有限公司是中国最大旅游集团——中国港中旅集团的全资子公司，自1985年于香港成立以来，秉承“为客人服务、为业主服务、为员工服务、为酒店服务”的理念，拥有维景国际、维景、旅居和旅居快捷等四大品牌，目前旗下近70家酒店，客房总数20,000间，分布于中国香港、澳门、北京、上海、重庆、西安、沈阳、南京、苏州、杭州、三亚、深圳、珠海、合肥、宜春、常州、扬州、太原、济南、青岛、唐山、新郑、商丘、咸阳、济源等商务和旅游城市。公司以多年的业主身份，对酒店业主的感受有着十分深刻的体会，辅以良好的品牌声誉、全方位的营销渠道和完善的中央预订系统，致力于为客人创造独特的、个性的旅游住宿体验，为业主获取最大效益，实现酒店可持续增长。','Registered&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;in&nbsp;1985,&nbsp;HK&nbsp;CTS&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;wholly-owned&nbsp;subsidiary&nbsp;of&nbsp;China&nbsp;National&nbsp;Travel&nbsp;Service&nbsp;Group&nbsp;Corporation.&nbsp;Focusing&nbsp;on:&nbsp;dedicating&nbsp;the&nbsp;best&nbsp;for&nbsp;guests;&nbsp;offering&nbsp;optimum&nbsp;values&nbsp;for&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;owners;&nbsp;providing&nbsp;career&nbsp;enhancement&nbsp;for&nbsp;employees;&nbsp;and&nbsp;contributing&nbsp;professional&nbsp;services&nbsp;to&nbsp;hotels,&nbsp;we&nbsp;manage&nbsp;about&nbsp;70&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;20,000&nbsp;guest&nbsp;rooms&nbsp;under&nbsp;four&nbsp;well-known&nbsp;brands,&nbsp;Grand&nbsp;Metropark&nbsp;Hotels,&nbsp;Metropark&nbsp;Hotels,&nbsp;Traveler&nbsp;Inn&nbsp;and&nbsp;Traveler&nbsp;Inn&nbsp;Express,&nbsp;throughout&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong,&nbsp;Macau,&nbsp;Beijing,&nbsp;Shanghai,&nbsp;Chongqing,&nbsp;Xi’an,&nbsp;Shenyang,Nanjing,&nbsp;Suzhou,&nbsp;Hangzhou,&nbsp;Sanya,&nbsp;Shenzhen,&nbsp;Zhuhai,&nbsp;Hefei,&nbsp;Yichun,&nbsp;Changzhou,&nbsp;Yangzhou,&nbsp;Taiyuan,&nbsp;Jinan,&nbsp;Qingdao,&nbsp;Tangshan,&nbsp;Xinzheng,&nbsp;Shangqiu,&nbsp;Xianyang&nbsp;and&nbsp;Jiyuan.&nbsp;HK&nbsp;CTS&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;leverages&nbsp;the&nbsp;unique&nbsp;core&nbsp;competence&nbsp;in&nbsp;brand&nbsp;reputation,&nbsp;integrated&nbsp;marketing&nbsp;channel&nbsp;and&nbsp;thorough&nbsp;central&nbsp;reservation&nbsp;system.'),(40,NULL,23.1,'诺金，一如既往的待客之道',' NUO, the Pioneer of Chinese Luxury Hospitality','public/2013/08/NUO_1.png','秉承“走国际化路，创民族品牌，践行中国服务”的理念，以中式、现代、绿色、奢华为四大支柱，诺金植根于中国传统文化，注重艺术的传承和发展，旨在以品牌的文化内涵传播当代中国的全新生活方式和态度，为客人提供前所未有的酒店体验。<br>诺金品牌的诞生，向酒店业界宣告了“中国风”的到来。首旅集团将以其雄厚的背景和实力，结合在国际高端酒店管理方面的丰富经验德国凯宾斯基饭店集团，将诺金打造成为具有中国特色的顶级酒店品牌。<br>','NUO,&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;international&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;brand,&nbsp;stepped&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;mainland&nbsp;onto&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;stage&nbsp;when&nbsp;it&nbsp;announced&nbsp;its&nbsp;global&nbsp;expansion&nbsp;strategy.&nbsp;The&nbsp;NUO&nbsp;brand&nbsp;is&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;four&nbsp;pillars:&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;heritage,&nbsp;luxury,&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;feel&nbsp;and&nbsp;green&nbsp;approach.&nbsp;These&nbsp;four&nbsp;pillars&nbsp;and&nbsp;service&nbsp;style&nbsp;represent&nbsp;NUO’s&nbsp;core&nbsp;philosophy&nbsp;ensuring&nbsp;that&nbsp;guests&nbsp;enjoy&nbsp;an&nbsp;unprecedented&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;experience.&nbsp;<br>Developed&nbsp;in&nbsp;conjunction&nbsp;with&nbsp;Kempinski&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;entirely&nbsp;owned&nbsp;by&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Group&nbsp;(BTG),NUO&nbsp;aims&nbsp;to&nbsp;disseminate&nbsp;the&nbsp;novel&nbsp;lifestyle&nbsp;and