;with&nbsp;city&nbsp;views&nbsp;overlooking&nbsp;the&nbsp;financial&nbsp;district&nbsp;and&nbsp;Oriental&nbsp;Pearl&nbsp;Tower,&nbsp;or&nbsp;spectacular&nbsp;views&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Bund&nbsp;and&nbsp;Huangpu&nbsp;River.&nbsp;Including&nbsp;four&nbsp;special&nbsp;access&nbsp;rooms,&nbsp;guests&nbsp;can&nbsp;choose&nbsp;from&nbsp;172&nbsp;Superior&nbsp;Rooms,&nbsp;356&nbsp;Deluxe&nbsp;Rooms,&nbsp;61&nbsp;Executive&nbsp;Rooms,&nbsp;22&nbsp;Studio&nbsp;Suites,&nbsp;22&nbsp;Executive&nbsp;Suites,&nbsp;43&nbsp;Diplomatic&nbsp;Suites,&nbsp;one&nbsp;Presidential&nbsp;Suite&nbsp;and&nbsp;one&nbsp;Imperial&nbsp;Suite.&nbsp;<br>Every&nbsp;guestroom&nbsp;or&nbsp;suite&nbsp;is&nbsp;designed&nbsp;in&nbsp;a&nbsp;modern&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;style&nbsp;and&nbsp;equipped&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;flat-screen&nbsp;TV,&nbsp;VOD,&nbsp;fax&nbsp;line,&nbsp;multiple&nbsp;phone&nbsp;sets,&nbsp;iPod&nbsp;docking&nbsp;station,&nbsp;Wi-Fi&nbsp;and&nbsp;high-speed&nbsp;Internet&nbsp;access.&nbsp;Within&nbsp;the&nbsp;bathrooms,&nbsp;the&nbsp;toilet&nbsp;has&nbsp;a&nbsp;separate&nbsp;closed&nbsp;area&nbsp;as&nbsp;does&nbsp;the&nbsp;walk-in&nbsp;shower.&nbsp;Complimentary&nbsp;national&nbsp;or&nbsp;international&nbsp;newspapers&nbsp;are&nbsp;provided&nbsp;for&nbsp;all&nbsp;guests.<br>The&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;has&nbsp;four&nbsp;restaurants&nbsp;and&nbsp;three&nbsp;bars&nbsp;offering&nbsp;international&nbsp;fare,&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;cuisine,&nbsp;Italian&nbsp;flavours&nbsp;and&nbsp;Spanish/South&nbsp;American&nbsp;cuisine&nbsp;Grand&nbsp;Kempinski&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;is&nbsp;delighted&nbsp;to&nbsp;invite&nbsp;guests&nbsp;to&nbsp;experience&nbsp;the&nbsp;unforgettable&nbsp;creations&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;award&nbsp;winning&nbsp;Michelin&nbsp;star&nbsp;Executive&nbsp;Chef,&nbsp;Mattias&nbsp;Roock.&nbsp;Guests&nbsp;can&nbsp;enjoy&nbsp;and&nbsp;savour&nbsp;Chef&nbsp;Roock’s&nbsp;unique&nbsp;brand&nbsp;of&nbsp;modern&nbsp;classic&nbsp;cooking&nbsp;with&nbsp;creative&nbsp;menus&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;unique&nbsp;gastronomic&nbsp;experience.&nbsp;Chef&nbsp;Roock&nbsp;works&nbsp;to&nbsp;continue&nbsp;the&nbsp;momentum&nbsp;started&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;transformation&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;and&nbsp;its&nbsp;ongoing&nbsp;culinary&nbsp;evolution&nbsp;and&nbsp;growing&nbsp;reputation.&nbsp;A&nbsp;German&nbsp;native,&nbsp;Roock&nbsp;brings&nbsp;with&nbsp;him&nbsp;12&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;mastery&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;culinary&nbsp;arts,&nbsp;10&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;knowledge&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Kempinski&nbsp;brand&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;passion&nbsp;for&nbsp;creating&nbsp;memorable&nbsp;guest&nbsp;experiences.&nbsp;<br>'),(42,NULL,24.1,'泛太平洋酒店集团','Pan Pacific Hotels Group','public/2013/08/PanPacific.png','创造难忘的酒店体验<br>著名的品牌，杰出的酒店，出色的员工及优良的交情<br>泛太平洋酒店集团麾下的酒店，度假村及服务式公寓分布在亚太地区和北美。从一个区域性的酒店资产公司演变成为一间既是拥有酒店也同时输出酒店管理服务的公司，我们能以业主的心态来经营我们旗下的酒店。我们适当的规模也使我们沟通更便捷，运作更灵活。这确保我们每一个业务伙伴都能得到我们的全力支持，关注及专注的解决方案。<br>欲知泛太平洋酒店集团如何成为您的酒店管理合作伙伴，请联系Joe&nbsp;Wu电邮至&nbsp;joe.wu@pphg.com或查询我们的网站pphg.com&nbsp;|&nbsp;panpacific.com&nbsp;|&nbsp;parkroyalhotels.com<br>','Creating&nbsp;Memorable&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Experiences<br>Great&nbsp;brands,&nbsp;great&nbsp;hotels,&nbsp;great&nbsp;people&nbsp;and&nbsp;great&nbsp;relationships!<br>Our&nbsp;Pan&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;Group&nbsp;portfolio&nbsp;consists&nbsp;of&nbsp;hotels,&nbsp;resorts&nbsp;and&nbsp;serviced&nbsp;suites&nbsp;across&nbsp;Asia,&nbsp;Australia&nbsp;and&nbsp;North&nbsp;America.&nbsp;Having&nbsp;evolved&nbsp;from&nbsp;a&nbsp;major&nbsp;regional&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;ownership&nbsp;company&nbsp;to&nbsp;one&nbsp;that&nbsp;both&nbsp;owns&nbsp;and&nbsp;operates&nbsp;hotels,&nbsp;we&nbsp;bring&nbsp;an&nbsp;ownership&nbsp;approach&nbsp;to&nbsp;each&nbsp;property.&nbsp;Our&nbsp;modest&nbsp;size&nbsp;ensures&nbsp;we&nbsp;remain&nbsp;approachable&nbsp;and&nbsp;agile;&nbsp;allowing&nbsp;every&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;our&nbsp;business&nbsp;partners&nbsp;to&nbsp;receive&nbsp;the&nbsp;dedicated&nbsp;support,&nbsp;attention&nbsp;and&nbsp;focused&nbsp;solutions&nbsp;they&nbsp;deserve.<br>To&nbsp;find&nbsp;out&nbsp;how&nbsp;Pan&nbsp;Pacific&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;Group&nbsp;can&nbsp;be&nbsp;your&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;partner,&nbsp;please&nbsp;contact&nbsp;Joe&nbsp;Wu&nbsp;at&nbsp;joe.wu@pphg.com&nbsp;or&nbsp;visit&nbsp;our&nbsp;websites&nbsp;at&nbsp;pphg.com&nbsp;|&nbsp;panpacific.com&nbsp;|&nbsp;parkroyalhotels.com<br>'),(43,NULL,25.1,'上海静安香格里拉大酒店','Jing An Shangri-La, West Shanghai','public/2013/08/Shangri-La_Jing_An.png','在品味高端的上海静安区，顶级购物商场、摩天大楼与精致小店、老洋房并肩林立，新与旧的水乳交融，东西文化的相互碰撞，让海派魅力在这里展现无遗。<br>静安嘉里中心位于静安区的中心地带，一个汇集各方活力，演绎优裕生活的商务休闲区。这个总建筑面积达450,000平米的“城中城”完美融合了酒店、购物、办公、住宅等多功能，更可包揽中庭“城市广场”的美丽景观。而最新揭幕的上海静安香格里拉大酒店，就座落于此。<br>酒店展现了浓郁的上海气质，是传统和现代的完美平衡。而您如果下榻于此，不单可以感受香格里拉一贯的经典设计风格，还有如同静安区般的现代与奢华，更多的是香格里拉固有的真诚质朴、热情好客。<br>香格里拉同时为您打造都市餐饮新风尚。酒店拥有4间餐厅和酒吧。其中夏宫中的陈设、艺术品、配饰均取材传统国画题材——孔雀，而橙色、绿色与蓝色基调加以金色斑点与之润饰，浑然一体，妙趣横生；1515牛排馆酒吧，将老上海电影与经典美食牛排馆风格有机融合；两咖啡色调靓丽明快，一层提供饕餮自助餐选，旋梯而上则是点餐式日本料理，随心配合您的用膳口味。<br>享受完精致美味的一餐后，来到位于55层的豪华阁贵宾廊放松小憩。透过巨幅落地玻璃窗，壮丽的沪上昼夜景观尽收眼底，您可以360度欣赏这座不夜城的流光溢彩。<br>艺术品味、时尚设计、美食盛宴、典雅奢华……凡此种种都无法道尽它的万千风华，在这座城市之心，传递出一股充满魅力的强劲脉动。它的名字就叫，静安香格里拉大酒店。<br>','This&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;city&nbsp;that&nbsp;seamlessly&nbsp;blends&nbsp;cutting&nbsp;edge&nbsp;modernity&nbsp;with&nbsp;ancient&nbsp;traditions.&nbsp;Glitzy&nbsp;skyscrapers,&nbsp;in&nbsp;every&nbsp;shape&nbsp;and&nbsp;size&nbsp;mingle&nbsp;with&nbsp;old&nbsp;markets&nbsp;and&nbsp;historic&nbsp;temples,&nbsp;buzzing&nbsp;streets&nbsp;intersect&nbsp;tree-line&nbsp;boulevards,&nbsp;filled&nbsp;with&nbsp;galleries&nbsp;and&nbsp;outdoor&nbsp;cafes.&nbsp;Everywhere&nbsp;you&nbsp;look&nbsp;is&nbsp;brimming&nbsp;with&nbsp;creative&nbsp;energy.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Jing&nbsp;An&nbsp;Shangri-La,&nbsp;West&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;is&nbsp;central&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;450,000&nbsp;square-metre&nbsp;Jing&nbsp;An&nbsp;Kerry&nbsp;Centre,&nbsp;which&nbsp;integrates&nbsp;prime&nbsp;hotel,&nbsp;retail,&nbsp;office&nbsp;and&nbsp;residential&nbsp;space&nbsp;overlooking&nbsp;a&nbsp;beautifully&nbsp;landscaped&nbsp;piazza.&nbsp;You&nbsp;cannot&nbsp;help&nbsp;but&nbsp;feel&nbsp;a&nbsp;sense&nbsp;of&nbsp;awe&nbsp;as&nbsp;you&nbsp;gaze&nbsp;out&nbsp;at&nbsp;it&nbsp;all.&nbsp;The&nbsp;vistas&nbsp;from&nbsp;this&nbsp;urban&nbsp;sanctuary&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;heart&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;city,&nbsp;where&nbsp;you&nbsp;always&nbsp;feel&nbsp;welcome&nbsp;and&nbsp;at&nbsp;home,&nbsp;are&nbsp;simply&nbsp;breathtaking.&nbsp;<br>The&nbsp;hotel’s&nbsp;four&nbsp;bars&nbsp;and&nbsp;restaurants&nbsp;offer&nbsp;you&nbsp;a&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;culinary&nbsp;delight.&nbsp;Inspired&nbsp;by&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;ink&nbsp;paintings,&nbsp;Summer&nbsp;Palace’s&nbsp;design&nbsp;blends&nbsp;splashes&nbsp;of&nbsp;golden&nbsp;yellow,&nbsp;orange,&nbsp;green&nbsp;and&nbsp;blue&nbsp;hues&nbsp;with&nbsp;modern&nbsp;motifs&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;peacock&nbsp;perfectly.&nbsp;Walking&nbsp;into&nbsp;the&nbsp;1515&nbsp;West&nbsp;Chophouse&nbsp;and&nbsp;Bar,&nbsp;you&nbsp;will&nbsp;find&nbsp;yourself&nbsp;immerse&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;movie&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;classic&nbsp;New&nbsp;York&nbsp;steakhouse;&nbsp;The&nbsp;two-level&nbsp;Café&nbsp;Liang&nbsp;&&nbsp;mezzanine&nbsp;greets&nbsp;guests&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;cheery&nbsp;palette&nbsp;of&nbsp;color&nbsp;alongside&nbsp;its&nbsp;semi-buffet&nbsp;spread&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;level;&nbsp;while&nbsp;you&nbsp;will&nbsp;also&nbsp;find&nbsp;a&nbsp;stylish&nbsp;spiral&nbsp;staircase&nbsp;that&nbsp;connects&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;second&nbsp;level&nbsp;serving&nbsp;modern&nbsp;Japanese-inspired&nbsp;cuisine.<br>After&nbsp;sampling&nbsp;the&nbsp;finest&nbsp;Cantonese&nbsp;and&nbsp;local&nbsp;delicacies,&nbsp;you&nbsp;head&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Horizon&nbsp;Club&nbsp;Lounge&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;55th&nbsp;floor&nbsp;to&nbsp;wind&nbsp;down.&nbsp;You&nbsp;step&nbsp;back&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;floor&nbsp;to&nbsp;ceiling&nbsp;window&nbsp;to&nbsp;enjoy&nbsp;the&nbsp;spectacular&nbsp;view&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;and&nbsp;contemplate&nbsp;the&nbsp;unforgettable&nbsp;experiences&nbsp;that&nbsp;beckon.<br>Nothing&nbsp;can&nbsp;be&nbsp;compared&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;heart&nbsp;of&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;city,&nbsp;where&nbsp;the&nbsp;boundless&nbsp;energy&nbsp;pulsates.&nbsp;The&nbsp;unspeakable&nbsp;joy&nbsp;comes&nbsp;easy&nbsp;at&nbsp;Jing&nbsp;An&nbsp;Shangri-La.<br>'),(44,NULL,25.2,'曲阜香格里拉大酒店','Shangri-La Hotel, Qufu','public/2013/08/Shangri-La_Qufu.png','孔圣谆谆教诲，要以礼乐待人，而作为孔子故里的‘曲阜’则被推崇为东方礼仪之邦的文化根源，孔庙、孔林等更被列为世界文化遗产加以保护，儒家文化的款客之道深深扎根在每个中国人的心中。如今，曲阜香格里拉大酒店将这一份款客之道盛情演绎，用心让您的文化朝圣之旅赏心悦目，亲身感受另一番奢华情趣。<br>酒店巧妙地将儒家理念、中国传统及现代建筑风格融为一体，以现代手法彰显历史传承。两栋主体建筑宛如中式亭苑，青砖飞檐的庑殿式屋顶错落有致，构成一组气势恢弘的建筑群。而正门车道，红漆回纹屋顶设计，由八根圆柱支撑，尽显皇家气派。<br>内部设计也秉承儒家思想，传递出浓郁的文化气息。酒店所有面向小忻河的客房均设有独立阳台，您可远眺宏伟的孔庙大殿和城墙，亦或近览小河流水和中式庭院的静谧优雅，与整个曲阜的城市建筑风格相得益彰。<br>曲阜的饮食文化也深受孔家的影响，孔府佳肴独树一帜，也是中国保存最为完好的宫府菜系之一。所以酒店的招牌中餐厅——香宫不仅主理粤菜，鲁菜，还特别推出孔府特色菜，一悦过往美食客。同时内部设计以柔金色、深木色及橙色相调和，古典而现代。墙面绢丝装饰有手工刺绣的花鸟庭院图案，寓意吉祥美满。<br>在曲阜一天的行程结束之际，相信您获得的不仅仅是中国几千年的文化熏陶，更可感受到的是身心涤荡的愉悦，和来自曲阜香格里拉发自内心的诚挚微笑。<br>','This&nbsp;is&nbsp;an&nbsp;enigmatic&nbsp;place,&nbsp;rich&nbsp;in&nbsp;culture&nbsp;and&nbsp;history,&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;reputation&nbsp;that’s&nbsp;almost&nbsp;mythical.&nbsp;As&nbsp;Confucius’&nbsp;hometown,&nbsp;this&nbsp;is&nbsp;where&nbsp;the&nbsp;famous&nbsp;philosopher’s&nbsp;personal&nbsp;beliefs&nbsp;are&nbsp;put&nbsp;into&nbsp;daily&nbsp;practice,&nbsp;where&nbsp;every&nbsp;stranger&nbsp;is&nbsp;greeted&nbsp;with&nbsp;open&nbsp;arms&nbsp;and&nbsp;an&nbsp;open&nbsp;heart.<br>Blending&nbsp;Confucian&nbsp;principles,&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;traditions&nbsp;and&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;style,&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel’s&nbsp;design&nbsp;reflects&nbsp;Qufu’s&nbsp;history&nbsp;but&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;modern&nbsp;aesthetic.&nbsp;Through&nbsp;sleek&nbsp;symmetry&nbsp;and&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;motif&nbsp;patterns,&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel\'s&nbsp;interior&nbsp;design&nbsp;concept&nbsp;expresses&nbsp;the&nbsp;three&nbsp;key&nbsp;principles&nbsp;of&nbsp;Confucian&nbsp;philosophy&nbsp;–&nbsp;order,&nbsp;harmony&nbsp;and&nbsp;hierarchy.<br>In&nbsp;our&nbsp;spacious&nbsp;guestrooms,&nbsp;those&nbsp;facing&nbsp;the&nbsp;Yi&nbsp;River&nbsp;are&nbsp;designed&nbsp;with&nbsp;balconies&nbsp;offering&nbsp;views&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;old&nbsp;city&nbsp;wall,&nbsp;palaces&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Temple&nbsp;of&nbsp;Confucius&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel\'s&nbsp;traditional&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;landscaped&nbsp;garden.&nbsp;The&nbsp;view&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;window&nbsp;is&nbsp;as&nbsp;expansive&nbsp;as&nbsp;it&nbsp;is&nbsp;beautiful.&nbsp;As&nbsp;you&nbsp;stretch&nbsp;out&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;lounge&nbsp;chair&nbsp;soaking&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;view,&nbsp;you&nbsp;could&nbsp;spend&nbsp;a&nbsp;lifetime&nbsp;here,&nbsp;at&nbsp;Shangri-La&nbsp;Hotel,&nbsp;Qufu.<br>Just&nbsp;steps&nbsp;away&nbsp;from&nbsp;your&nbsp;room&nbsp;is&nbsp;our&nbsp;signature&nbsp;restaurant,&nbsp;Shang&nbsp;Palace,&nbsp;serving&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;authentic&nbsp;selection&nbsp;of&nbsp;Qufu&nbsp;dishes&nbsp;and&nbsp;Cantonese&nbsp;delights&nbsp;that&nbsp;pay&nbsp;tribute&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;Family,&nbsp;descendants&nbsp;of&nbsp;Confucius.&nbsp;The&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;also&nbsp;features&nbsp;Café&nbsp;Kong,&nbsp;an&nbsp;all-day&nbsp;casual&nbsp;dining&nbsp;venue&nbsp;serving&nbsp;international&nbsp;dishes&nbsp;cooked&nbsp;in&nbsp;open&nbsp;kitchens.<br>Outside&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;lies&nbsp;a&nbsp;unique&nbsp;cultural&nbsp;excursion&nbsp;only&nbsp;found&nbsp;in&nbsp;Qufu.&nbsp;The&nbsp;Temple&nbsp;of&nbsp;Confucius&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;Family&nbsp;Mansion&nbsp;reveal&nbsp;the&nbsp;innumerable&nbsp;charms&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;past&nbsp;centuries&nbsp;along&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;legacy&nbsp;of&nbsp;Confucius.&nbsp;Then,&nbsp;you&nbsp;will&nbsp;realize&nbsp;that&nbsp;the&nbsp;great&nbsp;sage’s&nbsp;insightful&nbsp;wisdom&nbsp;has&nbsp;not&nbsp;only&nbsp;left&nbsp;an&nbsp;indelible&nbsp;mark&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;city,&nbsp;but&nbsp;you&nbsp;too.<br>Upon&nbsp;your&nbsp;return,&nbsp;you&nbsp;retreat&nbsp;to&nbsp;your&nbsp;suite&nbsp;where&nbsp;you&nbsp;succumb&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;soothing&nbsp;embrace&nbsp;of&nbsp;unparalleled&nbsp;hospitality.&nbsp;A&nbsp;warm&nbsp;bath&nbsp;in&nbsp;a&nbsp;sunken,&nbsp;full&nbsp;marble&nbsp;tub,&nbsp;infused&nbsp;with&nbsp;salts&nbsp;and&nbsp;essential&nbsp;oils&nbsp;nourishes&nbsp;the&nbsp;skin,&nbsp;the&nbsp;senses&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;soul&nbsp;while&nbsp;washing&nbsp;away&nbsp;the&nbsp;rigors&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;day.&nbsp;As&nbsp;you&nbsp;contemplate&nbsp;the&nbsp;priceless&nbsp;memories&nbsp;that&nbsp;tomorrow&nbsp;will&nbsp;bring,&nbsp;an&nbsp;effortless&nbsp;serenity&nbsp;lingers&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;comfort&nbsp;our&nbsp;heartfelt&nbsp;hospitality.&nbsp;<br>'),(45,NULL,26.1,'美国盛智律师事务所','Sheppard Mullin','public/2013/08/Sheppard_Mullin_c.png','我们了解酒店业<br><br>美国盛智律师事务所在酒店执业领域的国际律师事务所中一直处于领先地位。<br>我们的客户包括著名酒店品牌、运营商、开发商、贷款人及投资者。我们为客户在酒店业务的各个方面提供法律服务，包括酒店物业及所有权权益的收购和处置，酒店管理和合作协议的谈判，劳动和雇佣事宜和诉讼，抵押及无抵押融资，破产和重组，酒精饮料许可事宜，土地使用，建设和其他开发事宜，以及日常运作事宜<br><br>酒店管理合同<br><br>我们协助客户安排酒店管理事宜：<br><br>酒店管理公司竞标阶段：<br>1.	准备标书文件<br>2.	协助客户评估竞标，特别是对酒店管理公司拟提供条款的评估<br>3.	审阅、修改与拟酒店管理公司签署的谅解备忘录<br>&nbsp;<br>谈判阶段：<br>1.	负责对酒店管理公司就客户和酒店资产相关信息所提出的要求进行答复<br>2.	审阅、修改酒店管理合同和其他配套文件<br>3.	就拟定条款是否符合市场标准为客户提供咨询服务<br>4.	协助客户参与谈判，并完成相关法律文件<br>5.	翻译重要文件、会议纪要和邮件<br>6.	协助客户在签署法律文件之前获取执照或许可<br>7.	协调法律文件签署，并准备签署文件汇总<br>&nbsp;<br>交割阶段：<br>1.	协助客户获取就设立酒店分公司在相关政府机关的任何同意、批准或登记事宜；<br>2.	协助客户完成酒店管理合同在地方商务部门的备案事宜；<br>3.	负责对酒店管理公司就交割事项的文件和核实所提出的要求进行答复<br>4.	准备交割文件汇总<br><br>酒店知识产权&nbsp;<br>我们在北京的知产团队可以提供以下服务：<br><br>知识产权服务：<br>1.	协助客户申请注册文字、图形商标及企业名称&nbsp;<br>2.	协助在大中华地区申请注册外国公司专用标识所对应的中文名称<br>3.	协助客户在大中华地区对有关酒店、品牌住宅及休闲项目的商标及商号进行许可<br>4.	为酒店服务的推广，娱乐活动等现场服务中涉及的著作权及其他权利的许可提供建议<br>5.	协助商标权人在大中华地区通过行政、民事诉讼等手段向侵权者维权<br>6.	为客户提供关于互联网和社交媒体知识产权方面的建议<br>','We&nbsp;Know&nbsp;Hospitality<br>Sheppard&nbsp;Mullin&nbsp;is&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;forefront&nbsp;of&nbsp;international&nbsp;law&nbsp;firms&nbsp;in&nbsp;representing&nbsp;clients&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;industry.&nbsp;&nbsp;Our&nbsp;clients&nbsp;include&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;brands,&nbsp;operators,&nbsp;developers,&nbsp;lenders,&nbsp;and&nbsp;investors.&nbsp;We&nbsp;represent&nbsp;clients&nbsp;in&nbsp;all&nbsp;aspects&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;business,&nbsp;including&nbsp;the&nbsp;acquisition&nbsp;and&nbsp;disposition&nbsp;of&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;properties&nbsp;and&nbsp;ownership&nbsp;interests,&nbsp;negotiation&nbsp;of&nbsp;management&nbsp;and&nbsp;partnership&nbsp;agreements,&nbsp;labor&nbsp;and&nbsp;employment&nbsp;counseling&nbsp;and&nbsp;litigation,&nbsp;secured&nbsp;and&nbsp;unsecured&nbsp;financings,&nbsp;bankruptcy&nbsp;and&nbsp;restructurings,&nbsp;alcoholic&nbsp;beverage&nbsp;licensing,&nbsp;land&nbsp;use,&nbsp;construction&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;development&nbsp;issues,&nbsp;and&nbsp;daily&nbsp;operational&nbsp;matters.&nbsp;<br><br>Hotel&nbsp;Management&nbsp;Contracts<br>We&nbsp;assist&nbsp;developers&nbsp;and&nbsp;owners&nbsp;negotiate&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;arrangements&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;following&nbsp;scope&nbsp;of&nbsp;service&nbsp;in&nbsp;China:&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>Hotel&nbsp;Manager&nbsp;Bid&nbsp;Phase<br>1.	Preparation&nbsp;of&nbsp;bid&nbsp;documents<br>2.	Assisting&nbsp;client&nbsp;evaluate&nbsp;bids,&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;particular&nbsp;focus&nbsp;on&nbsp;evaluating&nbsp;proposed&nbsp;terms&nbsp;offered&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;manager<br>3.	Reviewing&nbsp;and&nbsp;amending&nbsp;the&nbsp;memorandum&nbsp;of&nbsp;understanding&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;proposed&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;manager<br>&nbsp;<br>Negotiation&nbsp;Phase<br>1.	Responding&nbsp;to&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;manager\'s&nbsp;requests&nbsp;for&nbsp;information&nbsp;regarding&nbsp;the&nbsp;client&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;property<br>2.	Reviewing&nbsp;and&nbsp;amending&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;agreement&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;ancillary&nbsp;documents<br>3.	Advising&nbsp;the&nbsp;client&nbsp;on&nbsp;whether&nbsp;proposed&nbsp;terms&nbsp;are&nbsp;in&nbsp;line&nbsp;with&nbsp;market&nbsp;standard&nbsp;terms<br>4.	Assisting&nbsp;client&nbsp;negotiate&nbsp;and&nbsp;finalize&nbsp;legal&nbsp;agreements&nbsp;<br>5.	Translating&nbsp;key&nbsp;documents,&nbsp;meeting&nbsp;notes&nbsp;and&nbsp;correspondence&nbsp;from&nbsp;English&nbsp;to&nbsp;Chinese<br>6.	Assisting&nbsp;client&nbsp;obtain&nbsp;licenses&nbsp;or&nbsp;permits&nbsp;prior&nbsp;to&nbsp;signing&nbsp;of&nbsp;legal&nbsp;agreements<br>7.	Coordinating&nbsp;legal&nbsp;document&nbsp;signing&nbsp;and&nbsp;preparing&nbsp;binders&nbsp;of&nbsp;execution&nbsp;documents<br>&nbsp;<br>Closing&nbsp;Phase:<br>1.	Assisting&nbsp;client&nbsp;obtain&nbsp;required&nbsp;consents,&nbsp;approvals&nbsp;and&nbsp;registrations&nbsp;in&nbsp;connection&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;establishment&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;branch<br>2.	Assisting&nbsp;the&nbsp;client&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;filing&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;agreement&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;local&nbsp;commerce&nbsp;departments<br>3.	Responding&nbsp;to&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;manager\'s&nbsp;request&nbsp;for&nbsp;documents&nbsp;and&nbsp;verification&nbsp;of&nbsp;closing&nbsp;items<br>4.	Preparation&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;binder&nbsp;of&nbsp;closing&nbsp;documents&nbsp;<br><br>Hotel&nbsp;Intellectual&nbsp;Property&nbsp;<br>Our&nbsp;IP&nbsp;team&nbsp;in&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;is&nbsp;equipped&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;the&nbsp;following&nbsp;services:&nbsp;<br>Intellectual&nbsp;Property&nbsp;Support:<br>1.	Assisting&nbsp;client&nbsp;with&nbsp;obtaining&nbsp;and&nbsp;prosecuting&nbsp;registrations&nbsp;for&nbsp;primary&nbsp;and&nbsp;secondary&nbsp;trademarks,&nbsp;logos&nbsp;and&nbsp;enterprise&nbsp;names<br>2.	Assisting&nbsp;with&nbsp;clearing&nbsp;and&nbsp;obtaining&nbsp;registration&nbsp;for&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;language&nbsp;variants&nbsp;of&nbsp;foreign&nbsp;house&nbsp;marks&nbsp;in&nbsp;Greater&nbsp;China<br>3.	Assisting&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;licensing&nbsp;of&nbsp;trade