p;project&nbsp;is&nbsp;planned&nbsp;to&nbsp;have&nbsp;242&nbsp;keys&nbsp;in&nbsp;total,&nbsp;and&nbsp;is&nbsp;contracted&nbsp;with&nbsp;AGON&nbsp;under&nbsp;an&nbsp;initial&nbsp;six&nbsp;year&nbsp;term.&nbsp;&nbsp;This&nbsp;marks&nbsp;AGON’s&nbsp;further&nbsp;movement&nbsp;towards&nbsp;the&nbsp;company’s&nbsp;evolution&nbsp;from&nbsp;a&nbsp;management&nbsp;services&nbsp;and&nbsp;consulting&nbsp;firm&nbsp;to&nbsp;a&nbsp;specialist&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;operator&nbsp;focusing&nbsp;on&nbsp;owner-branded&nbsp;properties&nbsp;and&nbsp;owner-friendly&nbsp;solutions.&nbsp;&nbsp;The&nbsp;owner&nbsp;was&nbsp;seeking&nbsp;AGON’s&nbsp;alternative&nbsp;solution&nbsp;for&nbsp;focused&nbsp;marketing,&nbsp;and&nbsp;to&nbsp;develop&nbsp;and&nbsp;leverage&nbsp;creation&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;owner’s&nbsp;own&nbsp;brand&nbsp;name.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>The&nbsp;property&nbsp;is&nbsp;ideally&nbsp;located&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;new&nbsp;town&nbsp;development&nbsp;along&nbsp;the&nbsp;shores&nbsp;of&nbsp;a&nbsp;pristine&nbsp;lake&nbsp;and&nbsp;adjacent&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;government&nbsp;headquarters;&nbsp;grade-A&nbsp;offices,&nbsp;and&nbsp;prime&nbsp;residential&nbsp;developments.&nbsp;&nbsp;Its&nbsp;smartly&nbsp;designed&nbsp;rooms,&nbsp;a&nbsp;luminescent&nbsp;“shell”&nbsp;restaurant,&nbsp;fitness&nbsp;centre&nbsp;and&nbsp;spa,&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;facilities&nbsp;are&nbsp;sure&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;a&nbsp;social&nbsp;hub&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;city&nbsp;and&nbsp;its&nbsp;VIP&nbsp;guests&nbsp;who&nbsp;will&nbsp;enjoy&nbsp;the&nbsp;creative&nbsp;spaces&nbsp;being&nbsp;developed&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;of&nbsp;AGON’s&nbsp;meticulous&nbsp;management&nbsp;services.<br>'),(47,NULL,30.1,'深圳市北极点建设工程设计有限公司和香港北极点国际酒店设计机构','Shenzhen Beijidian Construction Engineering Design Limited Company and Hong Kong Beijidian International Hotel Design Institution','public/2013/08/BJD.png','BJD&nbsp;&nbsp;深圳市北极点建设工程设计有限公司和香港北极点国际酒店设计机构简称，一直致力于酒店建筑工程全价值链设计服务，为全球的高端酒店业提供酒店前期规划设计、酒店建筑设计、酒店室内设计、机电设计等为客户提供无缝对接的设计服务。<br>帮助客户达到商业目标的同时也实现了自身专业技术的飞跃。BJD设计作品遍及全国和亚太地区，至今已和国际品牌合作在全国各地完成了很多五星级酒店的设计和筹建项目。<br>','BJD,&nbsp;short&nbsp;for&nbsp;Shenzhen&nbsp;Beijidian&nbsp;Construction&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Design&nbsp;Limited&nbsp;Company&nbsp;and&nbsp;Hong&nbsp;Kong&nbsp;Beijidian&nbsp;International&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Design&nbsp;Institution,&nbsp;supplies&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;architectural&nbsp;project&nbsp;value&nbsp;chain&nbsp;design&nbsp;service.&nbsp;We&nbsp;supply&nbsp;global&nbsp;high-end&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;industry&nbsp;for&nbsp;preliminary&nbsp;planning,&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;architectural&nbsp;design,&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;interior&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;electromechanical&nbsp;design.&nbsp;We&nbsp;give&nbsp;provide&nbsp;seamless&nbsp;service&nbsp;to&nbsp;our&nbsp;clients.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>We&nbsp;help&nbsp;cusomers&nbsp;to&nbsp;achieve&nbsp;business&nbsp;goals&nbsp;while&nbsp;also&nbsp;achieving&nbsp;our&nbsp;own&nbsp;professional&nbsp;and&nbsp;technical&nbsp;leap.&nbsp;BJD\'s&nbsp;design&nbsp;works&nbsp;are&nbsp;all&nbsp;over&nbsp;China&nbsp;and&nbsp;Asia-Pacific&nbsp;region.&nbsp;We&nbsp;have&nbsp;cooperated&nbsp;with&nbsp;many&nbsp;international&nbsp;brands&nbsp;and&nbsp;completed&nbsp;a&nbsp;lot&nbsp;of&nbsp;five-star&nbsp;hotels’&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;construction&nbsp;projects.<br>'),(48,NULL,31.1,'中国海南凯撒皇宫龙沐湾酒店','Caesars Palace Longmu Bay in Hainan','public/2013/08/Caesars_1.png','随着中国海南凯撒皇宫龙沐湾酒店的破土动工，凯撒娱乐公司的非博彩酒店分公司凯撒环球生活（“CGL”）启动了旗下第一个项目，该酒店项目预计将于2016年开业。该标志性奢华旗舰酒店标志着凯撒环球生活首次进入中国。凯撒皇宫龙沐湾酒店这一地标性项目是凯撒与国信龙沐湾投资控股有限公司的合作结晶，该公司是中国顶尖投资开发公司之一江苏国信资产管理集团有限公司的子公司。<br>这项投资总额达60亿人民币（9亿美元）的项目将采用“八爪鱼”形的建筑形态，是北京“水立方”奥林匹克游泳中心设计方，享誉全球的PTW建筑设计事务所设计而成。凯撒皇宫龙沐湾酒店将坐落在海南岛一段5.1公里的西海岸上一处15平方英里的总体规划度假景区内。龙沐湾的这个新景区是国信龙沐湾投资控股有限公司重要的长期经营项目。<br>凯撒皇宫龙沐湾酒店是龙沐湾开发项目的焦点，将提供超过800间度假村风格的奢华客房和套房，超过3,000平米的会展设施和众多特色餐厅和饮食体验。通过完美再现凯撒皇宫的风情，该酒店将提供独一无二的高端零售、大量水文和园林特色以及娱乐场所。<br>','Caesars&nbsp;Global&nbsp;Living&nbsp;(“CGL”),&nbsp;the&nbsp;non-gaming&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;arm&nbsp;of&nbsp;Caesars&nbsp;Entertainment&nbsp;Corporation,&nbsp;launched&nbsp;its&nbsp;first&nbsp;project&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;ground&nbsp;breaking&nbsp;of&nbsp;Caesars&nbsp;Palace&nbsp;Longmu&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;in&nbsp;Hainan&nbsp;(海南凯撒皇宫龙沐湾酒店),&nbsp;China,&nbsp;slated&nbsp;to&nbsp;open&nbsp;in&nbsp;2016.&nbsp;The&nbsp;flagship,&nbsp;iconic&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;resort&nbsp;will&nbsp;represent&nbsp;CGL’s&nbsp;first&nbsp;entry&nbsp;into&nbsp;China.&nbsp;&nbsp;For&nbsp;the&nbsp;landmark&nbsp;Caesars&nbsp;Palace&nbsp;Longmu&nbsp;Bay,&nbsp;Caesars&nbsp;is&nbsp;partnering&nbsp;with&nbsp;Guoxin&nbsp;Longmu&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Investment&nbsp;Holding&nbsp;Co.&nbsp;Ltd.&nbsp;(国信龙沐湾投资控股有限公司),&nbsp;a&nbsp;subsidiary&nbsp;of&nbsp;Jiangsu&nbsp;Guoxin&nbsp;Investment&nbsp;Group&nbsp;Limited&nbsp;(JSGX)&nbsp;(江苏国信资产管理集团有限公司的子公司),&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;premier&nbsp;investment&nbsp;and&nbsp;development&nbsp;companies&nbsp;in&nbsp;China.<br>The&nbsp;RMB&nbsp;6-billion&nbsp;(USD&nbsp;900M)&nbsp;investment&nbsp;will&nbsp;take&nbsp;on&nbsp;an&nbsp;iconic&nbsp;“Octopus”&nbsp;shaped&nbsp;building,&nbsp;designed&nbsp;by&nbsp;world&nbsp;famous&nbsp;PTW&nbsp;architects,&nbsp;the&nbsp;designer&nbsp;for&nbsp;Beijing’s&nbsp;“Water&nbsp;Cube”&nbsp;Olympics&nbsp;aquatic&nbsp;centre.&nbsp;&nbsp;Caesars&nbsp;Palace&nbsp;Longmu&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;located&nbsp;in&nbsp;a&nbsp;15-square&nbsp;mile&nbsp;master&nbsp;planned&nbsp;resort&nbsp;destination&nbsp;along&nbsp;a&nbsp;5.1-kilometer&nbsp;western&nbsp;shoreline&nbsp;of&nbsp;Hainan&nbsp;Island.&nbsp;&nbsp;The&nbsp;new&nbsp;destination&nbsp;of&nbsp;Longmu&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;significant&nbsp;and&nbsp;long-term&nbsp;undertaking&nbsp;of&nbsp;Guoxin&nbsp;Longmu&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Investment&nbsp;Holding.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>A&nbsp;focal&nbsp;point&nbsp;of&nbsp;Longmu&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;development,&nbsp;Caesars&nbsp;Palace&nbsp;Longmu&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;will&nbsp;offer&nbsp;over&nbsp;800&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;resort-style&nbsp;rooms&nbsp;and&nbsp;suites,&nbsp;over&nbsp;3,000&nbsp;square&nbsp;meters&nbsp;of&nbsp;convention&nbsp;and&nbsp;meeting&nbsp;facilities,&nbsp;a&nbsp;host&nbsp;of&nbsp;specialty&nbsp;restaurants&nbsp;and&nbsp;culinary&nbsp;experiences.&nbsp;&nbsp;In&nbsp;true&nbsp;Caesars&nbsp;Palace&nbsp;style,&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;will&nbsp;provide&nbsp;exclusive&nbsp;high-end&nbsp;retail,&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;water&nbsp;and&nbsp;garden&nbsp;features&nbsp;and&nbsp;an&nbsp;entertainment&nbsp;venue.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>'),(49,NULL,32.1,'青岛石老人综合体项目','Old Man Rock','public/2013/08/Dahlin.png','青岛石老人综合体项目是一个极具现代风格的海滨度假项目，道林公司负责其中公寓和酒店综合楼的设计。<br>这座拥有300间客房的高端度假型酒店，同时配以豪华Spa、三间餐厅、完善的会议设施以及大型室内外商场等功能设施。<br>毗邻酒店的是两座30层高的双子塔楼，一梯两户的大尺度户型，每户均带宽敞的阳台空间，透过公寓窗户，磅礴幽美的海景一览无余。<br>石老人的名字源于该度假项目海滨处有一块岩石，而这块岩石恰好勾勒出一位老人的身影，当地传说，这位“石老人”已在此屹立了几百年。<br>由道林公司负责对该项目建筑规划设计，计划于2015年对外开放。<br>在过去12年间，道林公司在中国完成了超过250个项目，而石老人项目也将成为其中光彩夺目的一个。<br>','Old&nbsp;Man&nbsp;Rock&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;contemporary&nbsp;coastal&nbsp;resort&nbsp;and&nbsp;mixed-use&nbsp;development&nbsp;in&nbsp;Qingdao,&nbsp;China.&nbsp;The&nbsp;condominium&nbsp;and&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;complex&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;design&nbsp;of&nbsp;Dahlin&nbsp;Group.<br>The&nbsp;300&nbsp;key&nbsp;resort&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;is&nbsp;complemented&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;spa,&nbsp;three&nbsp;restaurants,&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;meeting&nbsp;facilities,&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;large&nbsp;indoor/outdoor&nbsp;retail&nbsp;mall.<br>Adjacent&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;are&nbsp;twin&nbsp;30-story&nbsp;condominium&nbsp;towers.&nbsp;Each&nbsp;level&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;towers&nbsp;has&nbsp;two&nbsp;units,&nbsp;both&nbsp;with&nbsp;ocean&nbsp;view&nbsp;and&nbsp;large&nbsp;balcony.&nbsp;<br>The&nbsp;project&nbsp;name,&nbsp;Old&nbsp;Man&nbsp;Rock,&nbsp;comes&nbsp;from&nbsp;a&nbsp;rock&nbsp;outcropping&nbsp;just&nbsp;off&nbsp;the&nbsp;coast&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;resort&nbsp;and&nbsp;golf&nbsp;course.&nbsp;The&nbsp;silhouette&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;rock&nbsp;feature&nbsp;resembles&nbsp;that&nbsp;of&nbsp;an&nbsp;old&nbsp;man,&nbsp;the&nbsp;moniker&nbsp;has&nbsp;stayed&nbsp;in&nbsp;local&nbsp;lore&nbsp;for&nbsp;centuries.<br>Dahlin&nbsp;Group&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;planner&nbsp;and&nbsp;architect&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;mixed-use&nbsp;resort&nbsp;and&nbsp;opening&nbsp;is&nbsp;scheduled&nbsp;for&nbsp;2015.&nbsp;<br>The&nbsp;Old&nbsp;Man&nbsp;Rock&nbsp;resort&nbsp;will&nbsp;add&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;list&nbsp;of&nbsp;over&nbsp;250&nbsp;completed&nbsp;projects&nbsp;in&nbsp;China&nbsp;for&nbsp;Dahlin&nbsp;Group&nbsp;over&nbsp;the&nbsp;past&nbsp;12&nbsp;years&nbsp;of&nbsp;work&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;PRC.<br>'),(50,NULL,33.1,'卡尔森瑞德酒店集团','The Carlson Rezidor Hotel Group','public/2013/08/Carlson.png','卡尔森瑞德酒店集团是全球最大的、最具活力的酒店管理公司之一，旗下拥有六个独特品牌。<br>集团经营和正在筹备的酒店超过1300家，遍及81个国家和地区，旗下六个酒店品牌包括：丽笙、丽筠、丽亭、丽柏、丽怡、和米索尼。<br>拥有在全球成功经营酒店的历史，使卡尔森瑞德酒店集团在所有主要细分市场、商业模式、累积了丰富专业的经验，还具备了创造收益的强大能力。我们80,000名充满朝气的员工在整个集团创造了70亿美元的收入。我们致力在员工就业选择和共同投资方面成为首屈一指的酒店公司。此外，我们将扩大现有酒店组合，到2015年使运营的酒店数量至少增加50%，达到1500间。<br>','The&nbsp;Carlson&nbsp;Rezidor&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Group&nbsp;is&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;world’s&nbsp;largest&nbsp;and&nbsp;most&nbsp;dynamic&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;companies&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;stable&nbsp;of&nbsp;six&nbsp;extraordinary&nbsp;brands.<br>It&nbsp;has&nbsp;an&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;portfolio&nbsp;of&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;1,300&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;in&nbsp;operation&nbsp;and&nbsp;under&nbsp;development,&nbsp;a&nbsp;global&nbsp;footprint&nbsp;covering&nbsp;81&nbsp;countries&nbsp;and&nbsp;territories,&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;powerful&nbsp;set&nbsp;of&nbsp;global&nbsp;brands:&nbsp;Radisson&nbsp;Blu,&nbsp;Radisson,&nbsp;Park&nbsp;Plaza,&nbsp;Park&nbsp;Inn&nbsp;by&nbsp;Radisson,&nbsp;Country&nbsp;Inns&nbsp;&&nbsp;Suites&nbsp;By&nbsp;Carlson&nbsp;and&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Missoni.<br>With&nbsp;our&nbsp;long,&nbsp;successful&nbsp;history&nbsp;in&nbsp;global&nbsp;hospitality,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Carlson&nbsp;Rezidor&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Group&nbsp;has&nbsp;a&nbsp;rich&nbsp;expertise&nbsp;across&nbsp;all&nbsp;key&nbsp;segments,&nbsp;all&nbsp;business&nbsp;models,&nbsp;plus&nbsp;a&nbsp;strong&nbsp;and&nbsp;expanding&nbsp;revenue&nbsp;generation&nbsp;capability.<br>Our&nbsp;80,000&nbsp;inspiring&nbsp;people&nbsp;collectively&nbsp;deliver&nbsp;system-wide&nbsp;revenues&nbsp;of&nbsp;USD&nbsp;7&nbsp;billion.We&nbsp;aspire&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;the&nbsp;number&nbsp;one&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;company&nbsp;to&nbsp;work&nbsp;for&nbsp;and&nbsp;invest&nbsp;with.&nbsp;Additionally,&nbsp;we&nbsp;intend&nbsp;to&nbsp;grow&nbsp;the&nbsp;number&nbsp;of&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;in&nbsp;operation&nbsp;by&nbsp;at&nbsp;least&nbsp;50&nbsp;percent&nbsp;–&nbsp;reaching&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;1,500&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;in&nbsp;operation&nbsp;by&nbsp;2015.<br>'),(51,NULL,34.1,'西藏金查尔顿度假酒店','G Charlton Hotels & Resorts Linzhi, Tibet','public/2013/08/FSC.png','藏式宫殿<br>这座230间客房的五星级酒店如藏式宫殿般座落于雄伟的雪峰山景以及壮丽的雅鲁藏布江景环绕中。这座标志性的建筑容纳着公共设施如两座餐厅和雅座，小型会议设施、水疗、室内泳池、健身中心、游戏室、文化中心、以及观星阁。建筑沿着景观展开，既舒展着宫殿般的伟岸，又分隔出庭院空间的精致。为保留古树，建筑结构优雅地交织其间。<br>设计：<br>FSC&nbsp;建筑师事务所<br>1-808-352-5299<br>www.fscarchitects.com<br>','Tibetan&nbsp;Palace<br>Surrounded&nbsp;by&nbsp;majestic&nbsp;views&nbsp;of&nbsp;snowcapped&nbsp;mountains&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;Brahmaputra&nbsp;River,&nbsp;this&nbsp;230&nbsp;room,&nbsp;five-star&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;sits&nbsp;on&nbsp;a&nbsp;hill&nbsp;like&nbsp;a&nbsp;Tibetan&nbsp;palace.&nbsp;&nbsp;This&nbsp;iconic&nbsp;structure&nbsp;is&nbsp;loaded&nbsp;with&nbsp;public&nbsp;amenities&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;two&nbsp;restaurants&nbsp;and&nbsp;private&nbsp;dining&nbsp;rooms,&nbsp;modest&nbsp;conference&nbsp;facilities,&nbsp;spa,&nbsp;indoor&nbsp;pool,&nbsp;fitness&nbsp;center,&nbsp;games&nbsp;room,&nbsp;cultural&nbsp;center,&nbsp;and&nbsp;stargazing&nbsp;tower.&nbsp;It&nbsp;stretches&nbsp;across&nbsp;the&nbsp;landscape&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;palace-resembling&nbsp;expansiveness&nbsp;but&nbsp;is&nbsp;segmented&nbsp;into&nbsp;intimate&nbsp;courtyards.&nbsp;&nbsp;Existing&nbsp;ancient&nbsp;trees&nbsp;were&nbsp;purposely&nbsp;preserved&nbsp;by&nbsp;weaving&nbsp;the&nbsp;structures&nbsp;elegantly&nbsp;around&nbsp;them.&nbsp;<br>Designed&nbsp;by:<br>FSC&nbsp;Architects<br>1-808-352-5299<br>www.fscarchitectsc.com<br>'),(52,NULL,35.1,'IDeaS软件、服务及咨询业务助您创收有道','Driving Better Revenue with Software, Services and Consulting.','public/2013/08/Ideas.png','IDeaS&nbsp;Revenue&nbsp;Solutions成立于1989年。作为SAS子公司，IDeaS为酒店与旅游行业提供业界领先的定价及收入管理系统、服务和咨询业务。<br>IDeaS为酒店业服务了超过20年，目前在全球拥有2,500多家客户，其中95%以上始终如一地与我们保持着合作。每天遍布6大洲的94个国家多达54.1万间的酒店客房采用IDeaS软件进行定价。我们还应邀为其他多个行业提供服务，包括停车场、航空、运输和活动票务。<br>在中国，IDeaS已成功为众多领先的单体酒店及酒店管理集团提供了前沿的收益管理技术及服务支持，包括北京首都旅游股份有限公司、港中旅酒店有限公司、锦江国际酒店管理有限公司以及金陵连锁酒店等不胜枚举。<br>无论进行着何种努力，我们的目标始终如一，即帮助收益管理人士摆脱陈旧的工作方式，打造贴近用户、分析深入及创造更多价值的收益管理方案。<br>','Founded&nbsp;in&nbsp;1989,&nbsp;IDeaS&nbsp;Revenue&nbsp;Solutions&nbsp;-&nbsp;a&nbsp;SAS&nbsp;Company,&nbsp;offers&nbsp;industry-leading&nbsp;pricing&nbsp;and&nbsp;revenue&nbsp;management&nbsp;software,&nbsp;services,&nbsp;and&nbsp;consulting&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;and&nbsp;travel&nbsp;industries.<br>We’ve&nbsp;been&nbsp;serving&nbsp;the&nbsp;hospitality&nbsp;industry&nbsp;for&nbsp;over&nbsp;20&nbsp;years&nbsp;and&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;2,500&nbsp;clients&nbsp;and&nbsp;95%&nbsp;of&nbsp;them&nbsp;are&nbsp;still&nbsp;working&nbsp;with&nbsp;us.&nbsp;541,000&nbsp;rooms&nbsp;from&nbsp;94&nbsp;countries&nbsp;on&nbsp;6&nbsp;continents&nbsp;are&nbsp;priced&nbsp;every&nbsp;single&nbsp;day&nbsp;using&nbsp;IDeaS.&nbsp;IDeaS&nbsp;has&nbsp;also&nbsp;been&nbsp;called&nbsp;on&nbsp;by&nbsp;industries&nbsp;as&nbsp;far-ranging&nbsp;as&nbsp;parking,&nbsp;airlines,&nbsp;transportation&nbsp;and&nbsp;event&nbsp;ticketing.<br>In&nbsp;China,&nbsp;IDeaS&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;successfully&nbsp;offering&nbsp;state-of-of-the-art&nbsp;technologies&nbsp;and&nbsp;services&nbsp;of&nbsp;revenue&nbsp;management&nbsp;to&nbsp;leading&nbsp;individual&nbsp;hotels&nbsp;and&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;groups&nbsp;in&nbsp;China,&nbsp;including&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;Capital&nbsp;Tourism&nbsp;Co.&nbsp;Ltd.,&nbsp;HK&nbsp;CTS&nbsp;Co.,&nbsp;Ltd.,&nbsp;Jin&nbsp;Jiang&nbsp;Hotel&nbsp;Management&nbsp;Group&nbsp;and&nbsp;Jinling&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts,&nbsp;just&nbsp;name&nbsp;a&nbsp;few.<br>No&nbsp;matter&nbsp;what&nbsp;we’re&nbsp;working&nbsp;on,&nbsp;our&nbsp;goal&nbsp;is&nbsp;to&nbsp;make&nbsp;revenue&nbsp;management&nbsp;so&nbsp;user-friendly,&nbsp;insightful,&nbsp;and&nbsp;profitable&nbsp;that&nbsp;revenue&nbsp;management&nbsp;professionals&nbsp;wouldn’t&nbsp;think&nbsp;of&nbsp;going&nbsp;back&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;old&nbsp;way&nbsp;of&nbsp;doing&nbsp;things.&nbsp;<br>'),(53,NULL,36.1,'州逸','Interstate Hotels & Resorts','public/2013/08/Interstate_China.png','州逸（Interstate&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts）是全球最大的第三方酒店管理集团，在全球拥有超过50年的管理经验。其子公司--上海州逸酒店与度假村管理有限公司，成立于2010年。他的诞生，为中国的业主带来了具有重大创新意义的管理解决方案--第三方管理。公司的酒店管理平台遍及世界各地，包括美国、欧洲、俄罗斯以及印度，为酒店业主与开发商提供了管理及运营世界顶级酒店品牌特许经营的酒店以及地标级独立酒店所具备的世界级经营管理水准。在中国，倚靠州逸在国际酒店业的知名度和锦江集团在中国及亚洲地区的影响力，使得州逸中国（IHR&nbsp;China）有能力在中国市场为中国业主提供更加切合地方情况，更加符合业主需求，以及更加人性化的国际级的酒店管理政策、流程和系统。','Interstate&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;largest&nbsp;U.S.-based&nbsp;global&nbsp;third-party&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;management&nbsp;company&nbsp;with&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;50&nbsp;years’&nbsp;experience&nbsp;all&nbsp;over&nbsp;the&nbsp;world.&nbsp;Its&nbsp;subsidiary,&nbsp;Shanghai-based&nbsp;Interstate&nbsp;China&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;&&nbsp;Resorts,&nbsp;was&nbsp;established&nbsp;in&nbsp;2010.&nbsp;Its&nbsp;establishment&nbsp;has&nbsp;brought&nbsp;to&nbsp;our&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;owners&nbsp;a&nbsp;brand&nbsp;new&nbsp;management&nbsp;solution&nbsp;of&nbsp;revolutionary&nbsp;significance,&nbsp;i.e.&nbsp;third-party&nbsp;management.&nbsp;The&nbsp;Company’s&nbsp;management&nbsp;platform,&nbsp;with&nbsp;offices&nbsp;around&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;including&nbsp;the&nbsp;US,&nbsp;Europe,&nbsp;Russia&nbsp;and&nbsp;India,&nbsp;provides&nbsp;hotel&nbsp;owners&nbsp;and&nbsp;developers&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;resources&nbsp;and&nbsp;economies&nbsp;of&nbsp;scale&nbsp;necessary&