e&nbsp;growing&nbsp;awareness&nbsp;and&nbsp;increasing&nbsp;demands&nbsp;for&nbsp;buildings&nbsp;to&nbsp;respond&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;natural&nbsp;environment,&nbsp;URBANPROJECTS&nbsp;derives&nbsp;it\'s&nbsp;philosophy&nbsp;from&nbsp;an&nbsp;understanding&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;role&nbsp;that&nbsp;climate&nbsp;can&nbsp;play&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;built&nbsp;environment.&nbsp;<br>Building&nbsp;form,&nbsp;texture&nbsp;and&nbsp;technology&nbsp;can&nbsp;(and&nbsp;should)&nbsp;enhance&nbsp;the&nbsp;lives&nbsp;of&nbsp;building&nbsp;occupants&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;general&nbsp;public.&nbsp;URBANPROJECTS&nbsp;believes&nbsp;that&nbsp;the&nbsp;above&nbsp;must&nbsp;be&nbsp;balanced&nbsp;with&nbsp;commercial&nbsp;realities.&nbsp;Speed&nbsp;of&nbsp;construction,&nbsp;flexibility,&nbsp;life-cycle&nbsp;cost/capital&nbsp;cost&nbsp;often&nbsp;contradict&nbsp;the&nbsp;ideal&nbsp;sustainable&nbsp;solutions.&nbsp;URBANPROJECTS&nbsp;has&nbsp;a&nbsp;pragmatic&nbsp;approach&nbsp;to&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;will&nbsp;develop&nbsp;the&nbsp;highest&nbsp;quality&nbsp;product&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;our&nbsp;client\'s&nbsp;priorities.&nbsp;<br>URBANPROJECTS&nbsp;believes&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;highest&nbsp;quality&nbsp;urban&nbsp;design&nbsp;and&nbsp;master&nbsp;planning&nbsp;solutions.&nbsp;Without&nbsp;strong&nbsp;infrastructure&nbsp;there&nbsp;can&nbsp;be&nbsp;no&nbsp;quality&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;environment.&nbsp;In&nbsp;21st&nbsp;Century&nbsp;Asia,&nbsp;with&nbsp;urbanization&nbsp;on&nbsp;an&nbsp;unprecedented&nbsp;scale,&nbsp;good&nbsp;strategic&nbsp;planning,&nbsp;integrated&nbsp;Landscape,&nbsp;transport&nbsp;and&nbsp;amenities&nbsp;have&nbsp;never&nbsp;been&nbsp;more&nbsp;important.&nbsp;<br>');

